\id PSA
\h La Bu
\toc1 La Bu
\toc2 La Bu
\toc3 Labu
\mt1 PSALMS
\mt2 LABU
\mt3 Labu Sung Thu Umdan
\ip Hiche lekhabu hin na lungthim sunga giltah a thu asei ding ahi. Ajeh chu kipana, lunghemna, chamna, lunggimna chule kinepna hihen kinepnabei hijongleh hiche Labu'a kon hi, kitilkhouna le lung kipana thei namudoh tei ding ahi. Khang masa laija Labu'a thucheng kijih ho hi, tukhang kipana le dinmun ho toh jong akitoh in ahi. Labu'a um thucheng phabep hi, taona thutoh akilhonin, vahchoi tothoa kipana'a dim, chule kisihna neija chonset phondohna le khat le khat Pathen Pathen henga kitaopeh tona thudol ho aseijin ahi.
\ip Phat phatah napeh a nasim'a ahileh hiche lekhabu hin bukimsel'a aman aleding ahi. Labu hi avel vel-a nasim'a ahileh athah beh-a houlim pina nachan ding, hichu tule phatsot tah a ding ahi. Lunglut tah in sim in, ajeh chu Hebrew La toh kisai ho hi, La dang hotoh akikhehna um ahi.
\ip Chule hetdinga pha chu, Labu hi la-lam toh kisai ahin, houlam tahsan-dan toh kisai lou ahi. Labu jih ho hin, alhangpia amaho lungthim sunga kon ho hilchetna apeh-u ahin, Tahsan thudol'a Pathen Pathen thu adihtah ahilchet-u ahipoi. Labu sung thu umdan ho phatah in vele chun—Pathen Pathen le mihemte kiguijopna thudol jeng ahi. Hijeh chun La toh kisaija thucheng kijih ho hin, lunglut tah le na hinkho sunga taona tothoa sim jing dingin nakouve.
\is1 Lekhabu Jih Ho Chule Akijina Lo
\ip Israel Leng David chun Labu som sagi le thum ajih in ahi. Chule Labu som nga hi koipen in anajih ham, ti hetdoh ahahsan; ahinlah Labu adangse hi Asaph, Korah chihlhah te, Solomon, Mose le Ethan kiti Ezrahite amaho cheng hin anajih-u ahi.
\ip Chule phabep chun, Pathen Pathen henga taona le Ama vahchoina thudol'a Labu hi anajih-u ahi. Hinlah adang phabepma chun, kipun khom'a Pathen Pathen hou toh kisaijin anajih un, ama ama cheh thiljih-a kon hin, lhagao lam kitilkhouna ahiti, aki muchen in chule Labu ho hi aboncha Thangvahna, Taona chule Pathen Pathen kilam hilsahna jeng ahi.
\c 1
\s1 BU KHATNA
\s1 Pathen Pathen Adia Mipha Leh Migilou
\p 
\v 1 Migiloute thuhil jom louva, michonse ho lamlhah dunga jong ding leh lou; chule Pathen Pathen ginglou ho kikhop na dunga jong tou khompi lou mi chu anunnom ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Hitobang miho chun Yahweh Pakai Dan thu a bou lunglhai na aneiyun, Yahweh Pakai Dan thu chu sun le jan in angaito jing jeng ui.
\p 
\v 3 Hitobang mi ho chu twi lonna luipanga kiphut, aphat cha hung gaji adojong gopjilou thingphung tobang ahi; hitobang miho jong chu atohna lam lam'uva alolhing jiuve.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai ginglouho vang chutobang ahipoi: huilhoh mangle changvai tobangbep ahiuve.
\p 
\v 5 Hijeh a chu Yahweh Pakai gingloute chu thutan nikho tengleh themmo changdiu, michonse hon jong mikitah ho lah a mun aneiloudiu ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin michonpha ho lamlhah ahetpeh jingin, Yahweh Pakai ginglou ho lampi vang manthahna'a lut diu ahi.
\c 2
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Thaonupan Lengvai Apoh
\p 
\v 1 Ipi dinga chitin namtin kitohmoa, thilphachomlou ngaito na a aphat'u amoh man chatvai u hitam?
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakaiyin lengdinga athaonupa dounan leiset lengte akikhom un, chule vaihom thunei hon jong thulhuh asem un, hitin asei ui.
\p 
\v 3 “Ei-kihennauva kon ahin kilhamlhao hitin, Pathen Pathen thaneina'a kon'in kilha ong-u hite” atiuve.
\p 
\v 4 Hinlah Yahweh Pakaiyin avan laltouna'a kon'in amaho chu ahin nuisat in, Yahweh Pakai a din nuijat umtah ahi tauve.
\p 
\v 5 Chuin Yahweh Pakaiyin amaho chu lunghang tah in aphoh in, alunghan jah jeng chun amaho atijatsah tai.
\p 
\v 6 Chutah in “Keiman kalhendoh lengchu kalhang theng Zion molvum a katousah'e,” ati.
\p 
\v 7 Keiman thugahna chu phongdoh inge; Yahweh Pakaiyin kahengah hitin asei e, “Nangma hi kachapa nahi, Keiman tunia nangma hi kahin nahitai.”
\p 
\v 8 Kahenga nathum pouleh chitin namtin hi nagoulo dinga kapeh ding, vannoi leiset pumpi geija nagou kahisahding ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Nangman amaho hi thihjolla najep boh'a; belkhengpa bel kivoh chip banga ahal hal a nakoi ding ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Hijeh chun Vo leiset lengte kichih theiyun; Chule leiset thutan ho nang hon thuhil ngaiphaovin.
\p 
\v 11 Yahweh Pakai chu ging tah in akin bol un, chule kithing pum in Ama chu houvun.
\p 
\v 12 Yahweh Pakai lungsatna nachung uva achuh a namanthah masangun akengphang kolchah in chop un, ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai lungsat na neocha jong eihodia deojah ahi. Atahsan nau Yahweh Pakai a koi jing ho chu anunnom ahiuve.
\c 3
\s1 Pathen Pathen'a Kingaina Le Bitna
\s1 David lengpa'n achapa Absolom'a konna ajammanga alasem
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, idia eisulam vaiding mi pung jing hitam! eidou din mi tamtah akipandoh taove.
\p 
\v 2 Ama kihuhdoh na hi Pathen Pathen a aumpoi tin kalungthim in mi tamtah in aseijui. Selah.
\p 
\v 3 Ahinlah Yahweh Pakai, nang hi eiveng tup, kalum'a kisoung nahi; Ka loupina le khodah ngam-a, gal jona eipeh jing nahi.
\p 
\v 4 Keima O sangtah in Yahweh Pakai henga kataovin, Aman alhang thenga kon'in eihin donbut tai. Selah.
\p 
\v 5 Keima kalum'in ka-imu jin; Yahweh Pakaiyin eichin tup'a eihoidam jeh'in, kajing-thou kit tai.
\p 
\v 6 Keima doudin mihem sangsom sangjan ei umkimvel jongleh kichakit taponge.
\p 
\v 7 Hung thoudoh in O Yahweh Pakai; neihuhdoh'in, Pathen ka Pathen: Eidou hojouse khagu eivohchipeh in; nangma migilou ho hahemtah jong vopul soh ji nahi.
\p 
\v 8 Huh hingna hi Yahweh Pakai a kon bou ahi: Na phattheina jong namite chunga aum'e.
\c 4
\s1 Pathen Pathen In Asanpehna Dinga David Taona
\s1 Lalamkai pan semjangle selangdah ho to atho dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 Kakou teng neidon but'in, them eichan sah a O Yahweh Pakai; ka lhahsam nikho teng jong le nangman lunglet neipe ji; neikhoton lang kataona neingai peh tei in.
\p 
\v 2 Vo mihem chapa te, nangho hin itihchanpi neisuh jum diu hitam? Itihchan ajehbei a nei thepmosah uva, itihchan pihi jouthu nachepi diu hitam?
\p 
\v 3 Ahin nang hon heuvin, Yahweh Pakaiyin ama gingho Ama dingin atum'in alhengdoh'e. Yahweh Pakai kakou tengleh Aman ei-donbut teijin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Ki sonlelnan kithing pumin umun, ahin chonset boldaovin; hichu nalupnao mun'a jong nalungthimu toh gelkhom jing uvin lang umdet jingun.
\p 
\v 5 Lungthengsel a kilhai naho boljingun chule na tahsan nao Yahweh Pakai a koi jingun.
\p 
\v 6 Hiho sanga phajo eimusah thei diu koi ham? tin mi tamtah in seiunte, Yahweh Pakai namaivah achun keiho neihinsu emsel un.
\p 
\v 7 Nangman lengpitwi leh changle mim nengchet a kilamdoh ho kipani sangin, kalungthim nakipasah tai.
\p 
\v 8 Keima Nanga dia lungmonga kalup a ka-ihmut ding ahi, Yahweh Pakai nei hoidoh inlang neivengtup in.
\c 5
\s1 Pathen Pathen In Avenbitna Dinga David Taona
\s1 La lamkai pan pengkol to tho a sah ding David lasem
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, ka ocheng ho neingaipeh'in, Kalungthim a kataona jong neigelkhoh peh'in.
\p 
\v 2 Panpi ngaija kakana neigelkhohpeh'in, ka lengpa le Pathen ka Pathen; ajeh chu nangma kom'a bou taovakahi.
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai, jingkah teng kataona nei ngaipeh'in, jingkah seh leh nangma lam sang'ingting kangai chat jouse nakom kahin lhut a kinemtah a ngah jingding kahi.
\p 
\v 4 Nangma thil phalou ho chunga kipah ji pathen nahipon, migilou ho jong na angsuna aum thei ji pouve.
\p 
\v 5 Nangma angsunga mikiletsah ho a dingjou jipon; Yahweh Pakai nangman gitlou na le chonset bol jouse nathet soh hel e.
\p 
\v 6 Nangin jouthu sei ho na suhmang ding ahi; Yahweh Pakaiyin mijoulhep ho leh tolthat ho athet ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Keima din vang, Nangailutna bulhingsetjal chun na hongsung hunglut nange; Chule nangma ginle jana a naHou-In theng mai a bohkhup a chibai kabohding nahi.
\p 
\v 8 O Yahweh Pakai, kamelma ten eijo lounadin nalamdih a neipui in. Kamasanga um lampi hi kajuidih nadin neihin lhun jang peh in.
\p 
\v 9 Ajeh chu kamelma te kamsunga thutah apotthei tapon, asunglam'u jong setnajeng ahitai; Alol sung ujong lhankhuh abangin, alei ujong chuchi a kilhunglut kalbi abang e.
\p 
\v 10 O Yahweh Pakai amaho khu gotna petan. Aduhabol nauhi amaho lhuh na hihen! Achonset nau ho jeh'in delmang jengin, ajeh chu amaho hin nangma dounan na atong'un ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Ahin koi hileh nangma lhalim noi'a umho chu thanom'u hen! Nangma thangvahna lachu kipah tah in sajingu hen! Amaho chunga nalhajah in hoidoh jingin lang, Nangma min ngailu jing ho jong kipa na lodim jing'u hen.
\p 
\v 12 O Yahweh Pakai, nang'in michonpha ho phatthei naboh tei in. Nalungtoh te ngailutna ompho phatah achun nahoibit jing e.
\c 6
\s1 Pathen Pathen Hepina Ngaiya David Taona
\s1 David in Sheminith lakai a semjang jangget toh thodia lalamkaipa sah dia asem
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, nei lung han san loujen in! Lungsat namoljol a chun neikhoukhah hih helin.
\p 
\v 2 Neikhoto teijin lhasam le hatlou kahi Yahweh Pakai, neidam sah in kagu kachang jousen eichip ui.
\p 
\v 3 Kalhagao alengvai lheh jeng tai, O Yahweh Pakai itihchan pi hitia hi kaum ding hitam?
\p 
\v 4 Hungkilen O Yahweh Pakai, kalhagao huhdoh in. Nami ngailutna longlou jeh chun neihin huhdoh tei in.
\p 
\v 5 Ajeh chu thina ahin nangma geldoh na aumpoi: lhankhuh a konna jong koiham nahin thangvah ding?
\p 
\v 6 Ka ka kamao nan kachao lhatai; janseh a kakanan kajalkhun achin in, kaka na mitlhi hon kalupna jalkhun akotsah sohtai.
\p 
\v 7 Genthei a kaka nan kamit athimtan; kagalmiten eisuh genthei jeh uvin apomhel jengtai.
\p 
\v 8 Gitlouna bol ho jouse kakom'a kon'in potdoh tauvin; Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin kakana eijahpeh tai.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakaiyin kangaichat a kathum na ho eihetpeh tan; kataona hi eidonbut ding ahitai.
\p 
\v 10 Kagalmite jouse kijumsou henlang kithing pumin um uhen: Jum le ja pumin gangtah in kinungle taohen.
\c 7
\s1 Thudih Kiphkonna Dinga David Taona
\s1 Cush kiti Benjamin mipa chung chang a David in tumging jatchom chom ho to thoa Yahweh Pakai anga anasahdoh la
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, Pathen ka Pathen eihoidam din nangma kahin belle. Eipedoh a pang hoa kon'in neihoidohsah'in, neihuhdoh'in.
\p 
\v 2 Achuti loule panpi ding bei a kaum a, keipi bahkai-jin mi abolset banga eiboset uva, ahal halla eibotel diu ahi.
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai, k a Pathen keiman thil suhkhel kaneija, thil dihlou kana tohdoh khah a,
\p 
\v 4 Lungmonga kachenkhom pi khat chonphatlouna kalethuh a, ajeh beija kagalmi kanchom khah a ahileh,
\p 
\v 5 Kagal mite khut-ah neipedoh jengin lang kahin na lajengu hen, ama hon tolla eichotpha jeng uhen chule kaloupi najouse bon lah a kaithang jeng-u hen. Selah
\p 
\v 6 O Yahweh Pakai, lunghan in hungthoudoh'in, Doumit melpu kagalmite jeh in nang hung kichoisang'in; Chule hung kipatdoh'in Pathen ka Pathen nathutan dihtah chu hinpolut in.
\p 
\v 7 Namasangah chitin namtin kikhom soh hen: Ama ho chunga namun dihtah chu hin kimusah kit in.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai chu chitin namtin ho thu atan ahi: Kachondih naho nei phondoh peh tan, O Yahweh Pakai, ajeh chu keiman them mo na kanei poi O hatchungnung.
\p 
\v 9 Mi phalouho thil dihlou bolna kichai sah tan, chule michonpha ho chu domsangin. Ajeh chu nangman mihem lungthim gilsung ve Pathen dihtah chu nahi.
\p 
\v 10 Pathen ka Pathen hi kalum'a pang ahin, alungthim dih le akitah ho chu ahuhhing jin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Pathen ka Pathen hi thutan dihtah ahin, niseh'in miphalou chunga alunghangjingin ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Mihemkhat chu akisih louva ahileh, Pathen ka Pathen'in achemjam kinol hem intin, athalpi kaosa akoijing ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Aman thina manchah gimneitah chu kigot intin athalpi meikou chu akapding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Miphalou hon setna avop un, umhelna le thil phalou va agaiun, jouthu ho ahinpen doh sah jiu ve.
\p 
\v 15 ama hon mi lhahlutna dingin kotong thuhtah alaijiuvin, ahinlah amaho joh alhalut jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Midia set na abol hou chu amaho angsung joh in achuhjin ahi. Michunga chudinga thilse agon houchu amaho luchunga joh achujin ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Keiman Yahweh Pakai chu akitahna jeh'in thangvah ing-ting, keiman Yahweh Pakai hatchungnung min chu ka thangvah ding ahi.
\c 8
\s1 Pathen Pathen Loupina Mihem In Ajabolna
\s1 David in Gittith lakai a sah dia lallamkai pa apeh lacheng
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, ka-Pakai u, leiset chunga hi itilom loma naming loupi hitam! naloupi nahi vanho sangin asangjon ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Nangin chapang ho leh naosen ho kamsunga nathahat naho nahil in, hiti chun nagalmi ho leh nangma douho nasuthipjin ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Keiman janteng vanthamjol kavet akangaito jiteng, nakhut jung ho natoh in lhathah le ahsi ho agongtoh sel ui.
\p 
\v 4 Mihem hi ipi hija hibanga nagelkhoh'a, Mihem Chapa hi ipi dinga hibanga hi nakhohsah ham?
\p 
\v 5 Nang'in amaho hi Vantil sanga themchabou nemjep in nakoi jin, loupina le jana dimset in lallukhuh nakhuhpeh e.
\p 
\v 6 Nangin nathilsemsaho jouse chunga vaihop na napen, thiljouse akhutnoija nakoitan ahi:
\p 
\v 7 Kelngoiho le bong ho chule gamsahang ho jouse,
\p 
\v 8 Vantham jol'a vachate, twikhanglen'a nga-ho chule twikhanglen'a kijap jouse ahiuve.
\p 
\v 9 O Yahweh Pakai, ka-Pakai u, leiset chunga hi itilom loma naming loupi hitam!
\c 9
\s1 Pathen Pathen'in thu adih a atanjeh a David in athangvah
\s1 Lalamkai pan Alumoth-labben lakaiya sah dia David lasem
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai kalungthim pumpin nangma thangvah ing-kate. Thil loupi nabol ho hi seiphongle-inge.
\p 
\v 2 Nangma jal a kipana a kadimset ding ahi. Namin'in vahchoi la sang e, O Yahweh Pakai Hatchungnung.
\p 
\v 3 Nang nahung dindoh teng kagal mite anungjam jiuvin, akiseplhu vin na angsunga athiden jitaove.
\p 
\v 4 Ajeh chu nangin kadih nalam a thu neitan pehin, navan laltouna'a kon'in thu adih'in nahin tan e.
\p 
\v 5 Nangman namtin vaipi na lethuh in migiloute nasu-mang'in, amin'u tonsot a din nathai mangtai.
\p 
\v 6 Melmate chu nangin a-itih'a dingin nasumang in, khopi na suhmang ho jong tun suhmil'in aumgam-tauve.
\p 
\v 7 Ahinlah Yahweh Pakai hi tonsot leng ahin, thutanna dingin alaltouna atungdoh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Aman leiset hi thudih a achungthu atan a, namtin vaipi chunga hi dihtah a vai ahop ding ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakaihi bolgentheija umho dinga hoidohna ahin, hahsatna nikho hoa dinga kicholdona kulpi ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Namin heho jousen nahin tahsan ui, ajeh chu, O Yahweh Pakai nangin nangma holte chu nadalha ngaipoi.
\p 
\v 11 Jerusalem'a vaihom Yahweh Pakai vahchoinan lasauvin. Suhmil theilou atohdoh ho namtin jah a seiphongun.
\p 
\v 12 Ajeh chu aman tolthat ho aphu alahjin, panpi beiho apanpin ji. Aman migentheiho kana jong nahsah mon akoijipoi.
\p 
\v 13 Neikho to teijin O Yahweh Pakai; eibose teuvin ichan a eisuh genthei u hitam, thina kokhuh a kon'in neiloidoh'in.
\p 
\v 14 Zion chanu kelkot phunghoa lhangphong tah a ka thangvah theina dingin neihuhdoh'in, chutengleh neihuhdoh jal a kakipa thanom ding ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Midang ho lhahlut nadia asem u kokhuh a chun Namtin vaipi alhalut un, athang kam uva chun amaho keng joh a ohtai.
\p 
\v 16 Yahweh Pakai hi athutan dihna'a kon'in akilangdoh jin: Migilouho vang amaho thang-kamna'a a-ohden jiuvin ahi. Selah
\p 
\v 17 Migilouho vang lhankhuh a lhalut untin, hichu Pathen Pathen nahsah lou namtin vaipiho chunga got na jong ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Ahinlah panpi ngaichaho chu nahsahmoa umjom jing loudiu: chule migenthei te kinepna jong tonsot a suhmil-a um louding ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Hungthou vin, O Yahweh Pakai! Mihemho kinoise sah-hihbeh'in! Nangma ginglou namtin vaipi ho chungthu hi tanin!
\p 
\v 20 amaho hi tijatnan lungkhamsah'in, O Yahweh Pakai. Namtin vaipi hi mihem maimai ahiu kihetdoh sah'in.
\c 10
\s1 Migilou Lekhupna Dinga Pathen Pathen Henga David Atao
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, idia gam lhatah a ding nahim? Genthei kathoh jiteng ibol'a kisel jia nahim?
\p 
\v 2 Migilouten noise tah in migentheite adel mangjiu vin, mi-o nadinga asem'u thang a chun amahojoh hin-o sah'in.
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu amhon thilselam a alung ngaichat hou akiletsah piuvin, mikilose ho apah chauvin, Yahweh Pakai chu ataitom-un ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Migilou te vang Pathen Pathen holdin akiletsah val un, alungthim pumpiu vin jong Pathen Pathen aumpoi atiuve.
\p 
\v 5 Ahinlah amaho hi abol-lam lam uvah alolhing'un ahi. Achung uva hunglhung ding eng-bolna ho jonghi amupha jipouve. Ama hon agal-mihou jouse chu ataitom-un ahi.
\p 
\v 6 ama hon, kachung uva thilse kiti chulouding ahi tin atahsan un; boina hoa konna a-itih a ongthol ding kahitaove atiuve.
\p 
\v 7 Akam-uvah sapsetna, joule nal, chule gihsalna adimset ui. Alei muh uva jong thilse le thil phalou jeng aum'e.
\p 
\v 8 ama hon khopam lam gamthip lah hoa mi achanglhi jiuvin, them-mona neilouho thading agojiuve. Amit un alhasam te umna aching lhi jingun ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Keipi bahkaiho bangin akisel'un lhasam le hatloute mat jeng dingin angahun ahi. Sachangho bangin tah-lelte chu len akhu khum un amandoh jitaove.
\p 
\v 10 Lhasam a bolsetna toh te chu asugep jiuvin; miphalouho thahatna noi a chun alhalut jitaove.
\p 
\v 11 Migilou ten Pathen Pathen'in eimupha pouve atiuve! Aman amit sing intin, “Eihon ibol uhi mu hihbeh inte” atiuve!
\p 
\v 12 Hung kipat tan O Yahweh Pakai, migiloute hi gotna petan, O Pathen Pathen! Hatlou lhasam te hin sumil hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 13 Migiloute Pathen Pathen sam se pum puma iti ongthol diu ham? ama hon Pathen Pathen'in eithemmosah pouvinte tin angai touve.
\p 
\v 14 Ahinlah Yahweh Pakai nangin athilse bol-houhi namusohkeije. Nangin hiche ho hi melchih inlang amaho hi gotna pen. Hatlou lhasam ten atahsan nao nanga akoi un, nulou palou te jong nangin vengbit in.
\p 
\v 15 Hiche migilou mi-engseho hi abanjang-u heh bongin! abon-uva na suhmang kahsen anung u deljingin.
\p 
\v 16 Yahweh Pakaihi atonsot tonsot leng ahi! Pathen Pathen neilou nam mite chu gamsung akon a mangthah ding ahiuve.
\p 
\v 17 Yahweh Pakai nangin tah-lelte kinepna hi nahetsa ahi, nangin thon louva akana-u najahpeh a nahin lhamon ding ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Nangin nulou palou te leh bolgentheija umho chungthu adih a natanpeh ding, chuteng athi thei mihem in amaho hi asuh lengvai theilou diu ahitai.
\c 11
\s1 Mikitah Kiselna Mun
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 Keiman eiveng tup din Yahweh Pakai katahsan e. Hijeh achu, nangin ipi dia, “vacha bangin nahoibitna dingin hiche molchunga khun galeng tan” natiham!
\p 
\v 2 Migilouhon athalchangu akhaoto suhtoh san akoi un aloisal tauvin ahi. Ama hon munthip a kon-in milungdih ho ahinkap'un ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Dan leh thupehho akisuhset teng, michonphapa chun ipi abolthei nahlai dingham?
\p 
\v 4 Ahinlah Yahweh Pakai chu a-Hou-In munthenga chun aum'e; Yahweh Pakai chun vanna kon'in vai ahinhom nalaije. Aman mijouse ahin vechilsohkeijin, leiset chunga mitin ahinkholtoh e.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakaiyin michonpha le migilou anigelin ahinkhol toh e. Aman thunoh baotam bol ho athen ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Aman migiloute chunga mei-am lenglung leh katsong meikong gojuh'a ajuhsah ding hui savetvut pumma gotna apeh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai dihnahin thu adih a kitan achepin, hijeh a chu thudih chepi ho chun Yahweh Pakai mai amudiu ahi.
\c 12
\s1 Migilou Ho Kidou Teng Panpi Ngehna David Atao
\s1 Sheminith lakai a Lalamkai pa sah dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 Huhhing in, O Yahweh Pakai, michonpha mangthah ding ahitai! Leiset mihem te lah a mikitah jong abeitai!
\p 
\v 2 Heng le kom jeng jong jouthu jengin akilhemtouvin, muhnal a lungthima kilhep lhahding jeng thu asei ui.
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakaiyin dangnal tah a thukisei ho hi asuh bei ding, kiletsahna thuchengho jonghi asuthip ding ahitai.
\p 
\v 4 ama hon aseijun, eihon lungna chim set'in jouthu seiju hite, ajeh chu i-lei ikam'u eihoa hilouham, kon eisuh tang jou diuham? atiuve.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakaiyin adonbut in, “Keiman hatlou lhasamte chunga bolgenthei naho kamudohtai chule migenthei ho ka lemao jong kajatai. Tun keima kipan inting huhdoh dia eingaichat bangu va kahuhdoh diu ahitai.”
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakai kitepna hi thengsel'a ahin, dangka mei chunga sagivei kilhit theng tobang ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Hijeh chun, Yahweh Pakai nangin bol-hesoh a umho nahuhdoh ding ahi, ti kaheuve, chule hiche kitahlou khang mitea kon'a tonsot geija dinga nahoidoh ding ahi,
\p 
\v 8 migilou te muntin'a vahle henlang migilou pen ho jong gamsung a kidomsang u jong le.
\c 13
\s1 Gim Le Hesoh Pet'a Panpi Ngaiya David Taona
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, phat itihchan geihi neisuhmil ding hitam? Itih chan keija kon'a nakiselmang ding nahim?
\p 
\v 2 Itihchan gei hiche hahsatna hi kathoh ding ham? Itih chan asun ajan'a lungkhamna dimset'a kaum ding ham? Itih chan kagalmiten hanla eisap khum diu hitam?
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai, Pathen ka Pathen hung kiheiyin, neihin donbut tan! Katha kile dohsah'in, neithisah hih'in.
\p 
\v 4 “Ama hi kajou tai!” tin kamelma te hi ka lhuh nin kipasah hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 5 Amavang nami ngailutna longlouvachu kingai jing kahi. Neihuhdoh jeh a keima kipa jing ding kahi.
\p 
\v 6 Keiman Yahweh Pakai vahchoi lan sang e ajeh chu Ama keidin thilpha tah eibol peh ati.
\c 14
\s1 Mihem Ngolna David In Ahilchet
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia David Labol
\p 
\v 1 Mingol'in bou alungthim in “Pathen aumpoi” ati. Amaho hi lepche ngen ahiuvin, chule athilbol ujong adihlou jeng ahin, khatcha jong thilpha bol aum pouve.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakaiyin vanna kon'in lei mihemte jouse ahinven, mikhattou aching tahbeh um-em, chule Pathen Pathen ngaicha'a hol-a um-em atin ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Hinlah aumpoi, abon'un aki-heimang gam tauve, abonchauva lepche ngen ahiuvin, koimacha apha aumpoi khatcha jong aumpoi.
\p 
\v 4 Setna bolten hetna anei lou u hintem? Amaho hin kamite changlhah bangin aneuvin, Yahweh Pakai komin la taoding agelpouve.
\p 
\v 5 Amaho hi tijatnan alodim diuahi, ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin athua nung ho aumpin ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Migilou ten bolgentheija umho tohgon asuhsetpeh jiuvin, ahin Yahweh Pakaiyin amite ahuhdoh jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Zion molsang a kon a Israel huhdoh dinga koi hung ding ham? Yahweh Pakaiyin amite aki-ledohsah kit teng, Jacob in kipana asap phon a, Israel in Pathen Pathen athangvah ding ahi.
\c 15
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai na intheng sunga, kon nangma nahou ding hitam? Koiham nalhang thenga na angsunga hunglut ding?
\p 
\v 2 Hitobang mi themmona bei, thil dihjeng bol, lungthim theng pumma thudih jeng seiho.
\p 
\v 3 Akam a miseiset ding nomlou chule aheng akom chunga thilse bollou, ahilou le aloi agol chunga thilse seinomlou.
\p 
\v 4 Chonset kithang-atpiho theinomlou va, Yahweh Pakai dihtah a juiho ngaisanga, chuleh itobangin hahsa jongleh akitepna nitjingho.
\p 
\v 5 Athoi lalouva sumpa homho chuleh setna neilouho, ahethemlou ho lhemlha a phatchomna sum hol lou. Hitobang miho chu ahinkhouva dingdet jingding ahiuve.
\c 16
\s1 Hoidohna Dinga Pathen Pathen Henga David Ajam
\s1 David Michtam (Lakai jatkhat)
\p 
\v 1 Neihoibitnin O Pathen Pathen: ajeh chu nangahi kinem jing kahi.
\p 
\v 2 O Kalhagao, nangman Yahweh Pakai kom'a Nanghi ka Pakai nahi nati, thilpha kaneijouse hi nanga kon bou ahi;
\p 
\v 3 Leiset a Pathen Pathen lhentumte hi pachat umtah ahiuvin, amaho hi keidinga kagal lamkai le kakipa thanop napen ahiuve.
\p 
\v 4 Pathen dang ho nung jui a delle ho chu alung khamnao kibejing ding ahi. Amaho thisan a kilhaina ganthat a pang ka hilou ding, a pathen nu jong kahoupeh loudiu ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai hi ka chan ding gou le ka phatthei channa khon chu ahi. Yahweh Pakaiyin ka ijakai eichintup peh e.
\p 
\v 6 Nangin neipeh gam jonghi gamphapen ahi, itobanga goupha kidang neipeh hitam!
\p 
\v 7 Ijakai eihilla ka Yahweh Pakai chu keiman thangvah inge; janteng jong le avel in eigeldoh sah jin eihil jie.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaiyin eiumpi danhi keiman hetna kanei jinge. Ama hi kakom'a naichakhatna um ahi ti kahen hijeh chun keima lungthomhao ponge.
\p 
\v 9 Hijeh hin keima kalung amongsellin chuleh kipanan kadimmin Pathen Pathen ka thangvah e.
\p 
\v 10 Ajeh chu nangin thina mun a neidalha pon natin namitheng te jong lhankhuh a lhahlutsah pon nate.
\p 
\v 11 Nangin hinnalampi chu neimusah'in natin, neiumpi jal a kipana le nei umpina tonsot nopna chu nei pen nate.
\c 17
\s1 Mi-Sugentheitea Kon Gimna Aum Teng Hoidohna Dia David Taona
\s1 David Taona
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai adih thumna a kaka ogin hi nei jahpeh in, katao nahi nei ngaipeh in, lungthengsel le dihtah katao ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Kathem chan na neiphondoh peh'in, ajeh chu nangin thudih a natong namuchet ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Nangin kalunggel ho napatep jin, janteng jongleh ka lungsung navelhaji. Nangin kapum changin neivechillin kathepmo na namupoi; ka kamsung jenga jong set na potlou ding ahitai.
\p 
\v 4 Keiman nathupeh Dan dungjuiin, migilou ho le mi-engseho ho khonung kajui ji poi.
\p 
\v 5 Kakalson dan hin nalampi kajui jingin nangma lampia kon'in kapotdoh pon ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Keima nangma kom'a taova kahi ajeh chu O Pathen Pathen nangin neisanpeh tei ding kahei. Kataona hi lunglut tah in neingaipeh in.
\p 
\v 7 Nami ngailutna longlou chu kidangtah in neimusah'in, agalmitea konna hoidohna ngaichaho chu nathahatna gimneitah chun nahuhdoh ji e.
\p 
\v 8 Nangman namit teni na chintup jing bangin keima jong nei vesuijin. Nalhaving limnoija chun neisellin.
\p 
\v 9 Kavel a eidoujing migilouho a kon'in eivengtup in, eithatgo kamelma hoa kon'in nei huhdoh in.
\p 
\v 10 Amaho hi mi khotona bei ahiuvin akiletsah nao thucheng chu ngaitan!
\p 
\v 11 ama hon eihin juilutnun eiumkimvel uvin tola selhuh dingin agomkom'ahol un ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Aneh ding changlhih le keipi bahkai hangtah bang le keipinou vin gamthip lai matding avetlhih le tobang ahiuve.
\p 
\v 13 Hung kipat tan O Yahweh Pakai kidintepin lang seplhu jengin! Na chemjammin migilouhoa kon'in neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 14 O Yahweh Pakai naban thathatnin vannoia ama phatchomna ngaito ho hi sumangin. Amavang nangma goulu ho hi nangman vah va jingin. Achateu neijong suhnengpeh inlang ason apahteu goulo ding geija adalhah peh theina diuvin gontoh peh'in.
\p 
\v 15 Monabeija hinkho Kaman jeh a namel kamu tei ding ahi. Kathodoh tengleh nangma toh kimaitoa ikimuto ding chule kalungnachim tante.
\c 18
\s1 Pathen Pathen Phattheina Jal'a David Thangvahna
\s1 Pathen Pathen lhacha David la. Yahweh Pakaiyin agalmijouse le Saul a konna ahuhdoh nikhoa asah;
\p 
\v 1 Keiman nangma kangailui Yahweh Pakai; Nangma hi kathahatna nahi.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakai hi kasongpi, kakulpi, chuleh eihuhhingpu ahin, Pathen ka Pathen hi kasongpi ahin eiveng tup jing ahi. Ama hi kalumdal, eihuhhinga thahat chu ahin, chuleh kahoidohna munpi chu ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Keiman thangvah dinga lomtah Yahweh Pakai chu kakouvin, aman kamelma tea kon'in eihuhdoh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Thina khoisatna chun eiumkimvel tan, manthahna twipi chun eichup tan ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Damun lungkhamna chun eiumkimvelin, kalampi a thinan thang akam e.
\p 
\v 6 Ka lungkham val phatnin Yahweh Pakai chu kakouvin, Pathen ka Pathen kom'a chun panpi ngaichan kataovin Aman aHou-In thenga kon'in kataona asangin ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Hi jouchun leiset akilingin akihot e. Molbul ho jeng jong kihot e ajeh chu Pathen Pathen lunghang a ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai nah hom a meikhu ahung potdoh in, meikou gimneitah akam a kon'in ahungkoudoh'in chuleh Mei-am al lenglung Ama-a kon'in ahung koudoh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Aman vanho chu ahongdoh'in meilom thimletlut chu ahin chotphan ahung kumsuh in,
\p 
\v 10 Yahweh Pakai chu vantil pipui khat chunga atouvin, huipi chu alhavingin amangin alengin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Yahweh Pakai chu muthim in ahung kitom in, meilom twi jingletlut pumin ahunglhungin ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Yahweh Pakai vah'in ahintom chu meilom satah in ahinkhu khum in gelchang le mei-am chu gojuh'in ahung julhan ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Yahweh Pakai chu vanna kon'in ahung kisen in hatchungnung ogin chu gelchang leh mei-am koulah achun akithongin ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Aman athalpi ahin kapmin agalmiho chu athe cheh in, avah em lahlah chun amaho chu asuboi gamtan ahi.
\p 
\v 15 O Yahweh Pakai nangin nagalmi ho napho a lunghangtah a nakisen chun twikhanglen ato geijin akikangin, leiset bulpi jouse jong akeuvin aumjie.
\p 
\v 16 Aman vanna kon'in akhut ahin lhangin eihin kaidoh'in, twipi thuh lah a kon'in jong eikaidoh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Aman kagalmi hattah tah ho a kon'in eihuhdoh in, kasang a hatjo ka dougal hoa kon'in eihuhdoh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Hahsatna kato pettah in ama hon eihin delkhum un ahinlah Yahweh Pakaiyin eipanpin ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Aman kahoidohna mun nah eipuilut in eihuhdoh tai ajeh chu ama kipana kahi.
\p 
\v 20 Yahweh Pakaiyin thildih kaboljeh in kipaman eipen mona kaneilou jeh'in eikiledohsah tai.
\p 
\v 21 Keiman Yahweh Pakai lampi kajui in, thilse lam jon'in Pathen Pathen'a kon'in kakiheimang poi.
\p 
\v 22 Keiman Yahweh Pakai chonphatna lampi kajui jingin, a Dan thupeh ho kapaidoh khapoi.
\p 
\v 23 Pathen Pathen masangah nolnabei kahin, chonsetna kon'in kaki kangse jing e.
\p 
\v 24 Yahweh Pakaiyin thildih kaboljeh in Aman kipaman eipejin ahi. Aman themmonabei kahi amui.
\p 
\v 25 Mikitah kom'ah nangmatah jong nakitah in, monabei ho kom'ah monabei nahi.
\p 
\v 26 Milungtheng ho kom'ah nalungtheng in ahinlah miphalouho kom'ah nakhohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 27 Nangin mikineosah ho nahuhdohjin ahinla mikiletsah ho nasujumjin ahi.
\p 
\v 28 Nangin thaomei neidetpeh'in, Yahweh Pakai, Pathen ka Pathen'in kamuthim jong neisalvah peh e.
\p 
\v 29 Nangma hatna chun kagalmi hi neisuhchip peh'in Pathen ka Pathen toh kapankhom poupou leh itobang bang sang hijongleh kakal ngapchan ahi.
\p 
\v 30 Pathen Pathen lampi chu nolnabei ahi! Yahweh Pakai kitepna jouse alolhing jinge. Ama hi ahuhdoh ding ngaicha jouse dinga lum le pho ahi.
\p 
\v 31 Yahweh Pakai tailou pathen dang um'am? Pathen Pathen tailou songpi det dang um'am?
\p 
\v 32 Hiche Pathen Pathen hin eihatdoh sah'in kalampi jong hoibitnapen ahisah ahi.
\p 
\v 33 Aman molsang hahsa chung dunga kadindet theina din kakeng jong sakhi keng bangin atah sah e.
\p 
\v 34 Aman kakhut teni jong galsatna a manthei dingin agongin, kabanjang jong sum-eng thalpi loithei dingin ahatsah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 35 Nangman nagaljona lum chu neipetan nabanjetnin neipanhun ahi. Neikithopina hin eithupi sah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 36 Nangman kakeng phang tenin alhonal louna dingin kalampi neikehlet peh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 37 Keiman kagalmite kadel'in kaman'in ahi; amaho hi kajo kahsen katangpon ahi.
\p 
\v 38 Amaho hi ahung ki thodoh jou louna diuvin kasat lhun kakeng noijah akijammun ahi.
\p 
\v 39 Nangin kagalsatna dingin thahatnan neivon in; Nangman kagalmite chu kakengphang noi a neikoipeh e.
\p 
\v 40 Nangin angongchang'u neichotpha sah'in eivetda ho jouse chu kasumang sohtan ahi.
\p 
\v 41 ama hon panpi athummun koiman ahung huhdoh pouve. Ama hon Yahweh Pakai akouvun ahinla Aman adonbut pon ahi.
\p 
\v 42 Keiman amaho chu huilah a vutvai kithethang bangin tol ah kagoibong sel'in, bonlhoh lah a kasunat gamatai.
\p 
\v 43 Nangin eihouse jing ho chungah galjona neipetan ahi. Nangin namtin vaipi chungah vaihom'in neipansah tan ahi. Kanahet phahlou miho jeng jong kalhachan ahungpang tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 44 Kamin ajah jah'un kanoijah alut un gamchommi hojeng jong ka-anga akisunem gamtauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 45 Hansanna aneijou tapouvin kithing pumpum'in ka-ang ahinbel tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 46 Yahweh Pakai ahing jinge, kasongpia apanjeh'in ka thangvah e! Ka sochatna Pathen ka Pathen chu loupi jing tahen!
\p 
\v 47 Ama hi eibolse ho lethuh jinga Pathen ka Pathen chu ahin, aman namtin vaipi hi eisuhnem peh'in kanoijah eikoipeh tai.
\p 
\v 48 Chuleh kagalmitea kon'in eihuhdoh'in nangman kagalmiten aphah joulouna munnah neikoijin, eidouva mi-engse hoa kon'in neihoidohsah tan ahi.
\p 
\v 49 Hiche jeh hin O Yahweh Pakai namtin vaipi lah a nathangvah ingkate, na min vahchoinan la sang nge.
\p 
\v 50 Nangin leng a natun pa din goljona loupitah chu napetai; Chuleh nathaonupa David leh achilhah te chunga nalungset longlou namusah e.
\c 19
\s1 Pathen Pathen Natoh Ho Leh Athu Hing In Aloupina Phong
\s1 David labol
\p 
\v 1 Vanho'n Pathen Pathen loupina aphongdoh un ahi. Vanthamjol hon jong akhut thepna atahlangui.
\p 
\v 2 Anitin in aphongdoh jing jengun; jansim janseh le ama chu aseiphong jingui.
\p 
\v 3 Ocheng soh lou vin thu aseiyun; a ocheng'u hi akijakha ngaipoi.
\p 
\v 4 Ahinlah athu chun vainoi alodim in, thucheng jong chun vannoi leiset athechansoh in ahi. Vanthamjol hoa Pathen Pathen'in nisa chenna ding asem peh e.
\p 
\v 5 Hihchu kichen jouva moulang emsel a ahung potdoh bangin avahchan jengin ahi. Kisongtah a lhaitet golseh a pango banginhaltah le kipah tah in aum'e.
\p 
\v 6 Vanmong langkhatna kon'in nisa ahung sohdoh jin ajotna ding vanmong lang khat gei in ajui peh jie. Hiche asat a kon chun imacha ahoidoh ji poi.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai thuhil ho hi achamkim in, lhagaova asuhhal jingin ahi. Yahweh Pakai Dan thu ho hi tahsanthei tah ahin milham jong chihsah jengthei ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai thupeh ho hi adih'in, lungthim kipasah ji e. Yahweh Pakai thupeh ho hi akicheh in lungsunga hetthem theina eipeuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai ginle jana neihi athengin ahi, hiche hi tonsotna ding ahitai. Yahweh Pakai thutan hi adih'e; a etih a dih jing jeng ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Hiche ho chu sana sanga deiumjo ahin, sana thengpen sanga jong deiumjo ahi. Khoiju sangin jong alhumjon, akhoiphang dunga kilhoh lhatil sangin jong alhumjoi.
\p 
\v 11 Hiche ho hi nasohpa dinga gihsal na ahin, nathu nung hoa dia kipana chanvou lentah ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Kalungsunga chonset kisel guh jouse hi itikahetdoh jouding ham? Hitobanga kiselgua setna hoa konhin neisilthengin.
\p 
\v 13 Nasoh hi henasasa chonset bolna a kon'in neihuhdoh'in! Hiche ho hi kachunga vaihomsah hihbeh'in, chuteng keima chonsetna a konna kahoidoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Kakam a kon'a hung potdoh thucheng ho leh ka lungsunga kalunggel ho nalunglhaina hihen, O Yahweh Pakai kasongpi leh eihuhhingpu.
\c 20
\s1 Galjona Dinga David Taona
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia David Labol
\p 
\v 1 Na hahsat nikhon Yahweh Pakaiyin nakana taona nadonbut hen. Jacob Pathen Pathen min chun thilse jousea kon'in nahoidoh hen.
\p 
\v 2 Aman aHou-Intheng a kon'in kithopina nahin pejing henlang Jerusalem a kon'in nahin hatsah jinghen.
\p 
\v 3 Pathen Pathen'in namaicham thilto ho hingeldoh jinghen lang chuleh napumgo thiltoho jong khotona in nahin vetpeh jinghen.
\p 
\v 4 Pathen Pathen'in nalunga nangaichat nape henlang nathilgon jouse nalolhinsah sohkeihen.
\p 
\v 5 Nagaljona thu kajah tengu leh kipah'a kasapdiu ahi, chuleh Pathen ka Pathen u minna galjona ponlop kadopsangdiu ahi. Yahweh Pakaiyin natao na jouse donbut jing hen.
\p 
\v 6 Tun keiman athaonu lengpa chu Yahweh Pakaiyin ahuhdohji ti ka hetai. Aman avan mun thenga kon a ahin donbut ding, chuleh athahatna nasatah a chu ahuhdoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Namtin vaipi abankhat chun a sakol u leh sakol kangtalai hou akiletsah piuvin, ahin eihonvang Yahweh Pakai, eihon Pathen Pathen u minbou ikiletsahpi diu ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Namtin vaipi ho hi hunglhu'u vintin chip lhadiu ahi, ahinla eihovang idindoh diu chule dehtah a idin diu ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Kalengpau chu galjona pe'n, O Yahweh Pakai! Panpi ngai a kakana neidonbut tei in.
\c 21
\s1 Melma Khutna Huhdohna Jal'a David In Pathen Pathen Athangvah
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 Nathahatna ahi lengpa iti kipah hitam O Yahweh Pakai! Galjona napehjeh'in aman kipah'in kho asam e.
\p 
\v 2 Ajeh chu nangin alungthim'a angaichan napen aman athumho khatcha jong nadapeh poi.
\p 
\v 3 Nangin lolhin na leh houtheinan nalamto jin, aluchungah sana hoipen lallukhuh nakhuhsah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Aman ahinkho nahoitup peh din athumjin, chule nangin ataona nasanpeh jie. Ahin nikho jong tonsot a din nasuh saopeh ji e.
\p 
\v 5 Nagaljona chun jabolna lentah achansah in, thupina le loupinan najemhoijin ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Nangin tonsot malsomnan naphungvuh in chuleh nang toh umkhom a nopna kipana achun naphung vuh e.
\p 
\v 7 Ajeh chu lengpa'n Yahweh Pakai atahsan e. hatchungnung ngailutna longlou chun alhuhna dinga kon'in na hoidoh sah jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Nangin nagalmiho chu namattup sohkei ding, nangma nadouho jouse chu thahat tah na banjetna chu na mattup ding ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Nangma nahung teng amaho chu meikong lah a naselut ding ahi. Yahweh Pakaiyin alunghanna a asuhgam ding meikonga ahalgam ding ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Achateu leiset chunga kon a nathaimang ding; ama hon sonlepah aneikitlou diu ahi.
\p 
\v 11 ama hon nangdounan thil gong jonglehu, athilse gonhou chu lolhing louding ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Ajeh chu ama hon nathalchang amaho kapna dinga nadoi chu amutengu leh kiheimang untin jammang diu ahitai.
\p 
\v 13 O Yahweh Pakai na thahat na nasatah a chun hungthou doh tan. Tumgin le lasah to thoa nahat na natoh chu kakipa pi diu ahi.
\c 22
\s1 Gentheina Pum'a David Thangvahna
\s1 La lamkaipa henga jingkah khovah konna sakhi laina pen banga peng liuva sah dinga david labol
\p 
\v 1 Ka Pathen Pathen, ka Pathen idia neidalhah hitam? Panpi ngai a kamao teng idia gamla tah a um ji nahim?
\p 
\v 2 Niseh in nangma kakoujie, Pathen ka Pathen, hinlah nangin nei donbut poi. Janseh jongleh kakou ogin naja jin, hinlah lungmon na kanei jipoi.
\p 
\v 3 Israel'in athangvah jing laltouna-a tou nangmahi Atheng nahi.
\p 
\v 4 Kapu kapa teuvin nangma na tahsan un, nangman amaho nahuh hing tai.
\p 
\v 5 Naheng a akap un huhhing in a umtaove. Ama hon nangma na tahsan un nangman amaho nasujum poi.
\p 
\v 6 Hinlah keima hi mihem a dia lhing joulou lungtol bang bep kahi. Mijouse dia thet umle musit umchu kahitai!
\p 
\v 7 Eimu jousen eihouseovin, aleiju adosah un, alu apeijun asei uve,
\p 
\v 8 “Ama pa hi Pathen Pathen a ki ngai pa chu hilou ham? Achuti le a Pathen Pathen chu kihuhdoh sah hen! Yahweh Pakaiyin ama hi angailut a ahileh aYahweh Pakaiyin huhdoh hen!”
\p 
\v 9 Nangin kanu naobusunga kon'in neina hoidamin nei pui galkai in, kanu a-anglum laija patna nangma tahsanje neina hil ahitai.
\p 
\v 10 Kahung pen a patna nangma ban thahatna a eikipelut a ahitai. Kahung penlhah a patna ka Pathen chu nangma nahi jing e.
\p 
\v 11 Keija kon'in gamla loujen in ajeh chu boina ahungnai in, koima dang eikithopi thei aumpoi.
\p 
\v 12 Bongchal ho'n aum kimvel bangin kagal miten eihin um kimvel tauvin, Bashan bongchal khohlai hon eium kimvel taove!
\p 
\v 13 Hang tah le kisong tah Keipi bahkai in aneh ding aboltel bangin keima val lhum dingin akamkau ve.
\p 
\v 14 Kahinkho hi twi banga kisunglha ahitai, kagu kachang ho jong akilhep gamtan, kalungchang jong khoilu bangin ajunlha gamtai.
\p 
\v 15 Nisan asah gep leilhang bangin katha akanghel jengtai. Kaleijong kadang chungah akikamat tai. Nangin vutvai lah a neijam in athidin nei dalhatan ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Kagalmiten uichahon bangin eium kimvel tauvin. Migilou honkhat in eium kimvel tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Kagu kachang ho jong simthei ahisoh tan. Kagal miten eiveovin eivesalteh jengun ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Kavon ho jong vang asan un akihom gamtauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 19 O Yahweh Pakai keija kon'in umgamla hihbehin! Nangma kathahatna nahi neihung kithopi loijin.
\p 
\v 20 Na chemjam chun neihuhdoh in, kahinkho manlutah hi hiche uicha hoa kon'in neihuhdoh peh in.
\p 
\v 21 Keipi bahkai kam a kon'in neiloidoh peh in lang hiche gambongchal hang kiteni ki a kon'in neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 22 Kasopi pasal ho leh numeiho kom'a naminhi phongjal leng katin, Houbung kikhom holah a nangma ka thangvah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Ama gingho jousen Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah hen! Jacob chilhah te jousen ama chu ging uvin! Israel chate jousen ama chu jana peohen!
\p 
\v 24 Ajeh chu aman migentheite thohgimna jouse chu anungsun pon, panpi ngaichatna a taona neiho angaipeh in ahi.
\p 
\v 25 Keiman Houbung kikhopna lah a nangma kathang vah ding ahi. Nangma chibai boh ho angsunga kakitepna kasuh bulhit ding ahi.
\p 
\v 26 Mivaichaten neovintin vaset diu ahi. Yahweh Pakai holte jousen ama chu athangvah diu ahi. Alung thim u tonsotna kipah jingding ahiuve.
\p 
\v 27 Vannoi leiset miten Yahweh Pakai chu ahin hetdoh diu chuleh akom'a hung kilediu ahi. Chutengleh namtin vaipi insung jousen a anga hungkun cheh diu ahi.
\p 
\v 28 Ajeh chu leng thaneina chu Yahweh Pakai ama a bou ahi. Aman namtin vaipi chunga vai ahom ahi.
\p 
\v 29 Leiset chunga mihaohon ankong sem untin chibai aboh diu ahi. Ahinkho kichai a leivui soh ding athi thei mihem jouse a anga kun cheh hen.
\p 
\v 30 Ichate jouseuvin jong Ama kin ahinbol diu ahi. Ahunglhung ding khang miten jong Yahweh Pakai kidanje chu ahin jahpeh diu ahi.
\p 
\v 31 Tua penglou laiho kom'a jong thudih a anatohnaho jouse hung kiseipeh ding ahi. Ama hon athilbol natoh naho jouse ahin jahdiu ahi.
\c 23
\s1 David in Yahweh Pakaiyin a kelngoi bangtah a eichin ahi ti
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu akelngoi keima eiching pa ahi, keiman lhah samna neiponge.
\p 
\v 2 Aman hamhing dumlah lah a kelngoi bangin eikicholdo sahjin, kilinglouhel twiveina pang dungah eipuilei.
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakaiyin katha akiledoh ji. Amintheng khohsahna jalin lamdih lang jenga eipuilen ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Thim jin napen phaicham palgalkai jonglehng keima kichaponge, ajeh chu nangman naum jingin nateng gol le namoljol chun neihongin neilhamon jinge.
\p 
\v 5 Ka melmate masangtah jenga jong nangin kaneh ding ankong neiluipeh in, naphat theina thao ka lujangah neinupeh in kadon ding khonjong phatthei na aletset in ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Tahbeh in phatna le hepinan kahinkho lhung keiya eijui jingding ahi, chuleh keijong tonsot na Yahweh Pakaiyinn sunga kachenjing ding ahi.
\c 24
\s1 Loupina Lengpa
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 vannoi leiset le asunga um jouse hi Yahweh Pakai a ahi. Vannoi pumpi le asunga cheng mihemte jousehi Ama a jeng ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Ajeh chu Aman leiset khombul hi twikhanglen chunga atun ahin, twipi thuhlah a aphudet ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Koiham Yahweh Pakai moul chunga kaldoh jouding? Koiham amunthenga dingthei ding?
\p 
\v 4 Akhut le Alungthim thengho bou, chuleh milimsemthu houlou le jou seilouho bou hidiu ahi.
\p 
\v 5 ama hon bou Yahweh Pakai malsomna amudiu ahin, chuleh ahuh hingpao Pathen Pathen toh ki guijop na dihtah anei theidiu ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Hitobang miho hinbou nangma naholthei diu chuleh Jacob Pathen Pathen nangma nachibai theidiu ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Khanglui kelkot ho kihonglen un! Khanglui kotpiho kihong len un lang leng loupi chu lutsah un.
\p 
\v 8 Koiham lengloupi chu? Yahweh Pakai hattah leh thupi tah, Yahweh Pakai koiman ajojou lou galhattah chu ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Khanglui kelkot ho kihong lennun, khanglui kotpiho kihong lennun, loupina leng chu lutsah un
\p 
\v 10 Koiham lengloupi chu? Van Pathen Pathen sepai, Ama hi leng loupi chu ahi.
\c 25
\s1 David Tahsandet Tah'a Atao
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, kahinkho hi nang kapetai.
\p 
\v 2 Nang katahsan e Pathen ka Pathen! Nei jumso hihbeh in, chule kalel na a hin ka melmate kichoisang sah hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 3 Nangma tahsan koima chan jumna ato loudiu ahi, amavang mijoulhep gojing honvang jumna ato diu ahi.
\p 
\v 4 O Yahweh Pakai lamdih chu neihil in; kajui ding lampi chu neiko peh in.
\p 
\v 5 Nathutah chu neihil in hichea chun neipui in ajeh chu nangmahi eihuh hinga Pathen ka Pathen chu nahi. Nilhum kei keijin nanga hin kinepna kanei jinge.
\p 
\v 6 O Yahweh Pakai gol lui a patna neihin puinao nami khoto na le na mi ngailutna longlou hingeldoh in.
\p 
\v 7 Ka khangdon lai a kachonset gitlou naho neigeldoh peh hih inlang nami ngailutna longlouva neipuina johchu galdoh in, ajeh chu nangma milungset them nahi, O Yahweh Pakai.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaihi apha ahin adih jengbou abol'e, aman lamdihlou vache ho jeng jong lamdih akopeh jinge.
\p 
\v 9 Aman mi kineosah ho chu lamdih a apuijin, ama dei lampi chu ahil jinge.
\p 
\v 10 Yahweh Pakai kitepna nitjing ho leh ama deipeh dungjuiya chonho chu ami ngailutna longlou leh akitahna in apuihoi jinge.
\p 
\v 11 Namin loupina dingin O Yahweh Pakai, ka chonsetna simjoulou neingai dam in.
\p 
\v 12 Yahweh Pakai ging ho chu koi ho hiuvam? Amaho che nading lampi chu Yahweh Pakaiyin avetsah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Amaho chu khangtou untin achateuvin jong gamsung alo dingu ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Yahweh Pakai hi ama gingjing tedinga golphapen ahin, Aman hitobang miho chu akitepna ahiljing e.
\p 
\v 15 Kamit tenin Yahweh Pakaichu avejingin, aman kagalmite thangkol a kon'in eihuhdoh jinging e.
\p 
\v 16 Neihin ang-ngatnin lang neikho ton, ajeh chu keima kachangseh a lungthom haotah a um a kahi.
\p 
\v 17 Kaboi na ho akhoh se cheh un. Oh hiche hoa konhin neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 18 Kalung gimnahi neihet pehin chuleh kahah satna ho hi neivet peh inlang kachonset naho ngaidam in.
\p 
\v 19 Ven galmi ijat mong kanei hitam chule amaho hin ichan geija eihotnu hitam!
\p 
\v 20 Neivengbit in! amaho a konna hin kahinkho huhdoh in! nangma a kisel kahi neijumso hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 21 Kitah na le thenna in eivengbit hen ajeh chu nanga hin kakinepna aum jinge.
\p 
\v 22 Vo Pathen Pathen Israel te hi aboi najouseu va kon'in lhatdoh tan.
\c 26
\s1 David In Thudih Le Tahsan Ahina Dol Pathen Pathen Henga Aphon
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai themmona bei kahihi phongdoh tan, ajeh chu keiman kitah na neitah in hinkho kamangin nungchonlouhel in Yahweh Pakai a tahsan na dettah kaneije.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakai neipatep inlang neikhol chil in, kachondan leh kalungthim hi vechen mongin!
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu nei ngailutna longlouhi keiman kahejing e, chuleh keiman nathudih dungjuijin hinkho kamange.
\p 
\v 4 Keima mijouho tojong kakivop khompon, miphalhem ho deilam jong kachepipon ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Keiman migiloute kikhop na kathet in thil phalou ho jong kanuse ji e.
\p 
\v 6 Themmona kaneilou vetsahna in kakhut kasil in namaicham kahin jon e O Yahweh Pakai,
\p 
\v 7 Thangvah la sapum in nakidan na ho kaphong doh e.
\p 
\v 8 Na Hou-In theng kangailui, Yahweh Pakai, naum pi na loipi tah kilan doh na mun chu.
\p 
\v 9 Michonse ho thoh ding neithoh sah hih in, tolthat hoto kibanginneithep mo sah hih in.
\p 
\v 10 Set bolnom nan akhutnu asuboh un, chuleh ama hon phatseh in nehguh akilah un ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Keiman hitobang hinkho chu kamangpon, kitahna hinkhoa kading jinge. Hijeh chun neilhat doh inlang nami hepina chun neipuijin.
\p 
\v 12 Tun keima tolgo lai a dettah in kadinge chuleh keiman lhangphong tah a Yahweh Pakai kathang vah ding ahi.
\c 27
\s1 Pathen Pathen Thaneina Dol'a David Tahsan Detna
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakaihi keidin vah leh huhhingna ahi. Chuti ahileh idia kakichat ding ham? Yahweh Pakaihi kakulpi, hahsatna a eihuhdoh pa ahi. Chuti ahileh ken idia kakithin ding ham?
\p 
\v 2 Migilou ten suhgamdia eihindel khum uva, kagalmite leh eidou teuvin eihin nokhumtengu leh kipal lhuvin tin chuleh lhugam diu ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Galmi tamtah in eium kimvel jeng jongleh kalung linglao ponte, ijemtin thagam dingin eihin delkhum jongleho Pathen ka Pathen a lung mongtah a kaum ding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Hiche thil khat Yahweh Pakai henga kathum kadei pipen chu kahinkho lhumkeija Yahweh Pakaiyin na um ding, Yahweh Pakai lolhinna a chu lunglhaisel a um a aHou-In na aphatnaho geljinga hinkho man ding hi ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Ajeh chu aman hahsatna a konna eihoidoh sahding a Hou-In thenga chu eihoibit ding Aman mi maiphah louva songpi chunga eiselding ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Ajeh chu boina hon eihin lonkhum jong le Aman eihoi dam ding ahi. Ama Hou-Intheng sunga kipah le thanom tah a pumgo thilto kabolding semjang saipum a Yahweh Pakai thangvah la kasah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Kahung taove neingai peh in O Yahweh Pakai. Namikhoto na pum in neidonbut in.
\p 
\v 8 “Hungin lang neihoulim pin” nati chu kalungthim in ajan hitin adonbutne, “Yahweh Pakai kahunge”
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai neinung ngat hihbeh in. Na lunghan nan nasoh hi paidoh hihbeh in. Nangmahi eikithopi phapen chu nahijenge. Tun neipaidoh hih in; neidalha hih in, O Pathen Pathen ka huhing pu.
\p 
\v 10 Kanu le kapan eipaidoh jeng jongleh Yahweh Pakaiyin eikolchah jing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 11 O Yahweh Pakai kahinkho man ding Dan neihil in lamdih jenga neipuiin, ajeh chu kagal miten eichang lhijingun ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Amaho khut a neilhah lutsah hih in, ajeh chu ama hon kabol louhel thil a themo eichan un, phatin in kachungah thilse abolgo jingun ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Ahijeng vangin, hiche mihing gam a kaum laisen Yahweh Pakai phatna kamu jing jeng ding kakinem e.
\p 
\v 14 Yahweh Pakai chu lungneng tah in ngah jingin, Hanginlang hatnin, Henge, Yahweh Pakai chu lungneng tah in ngah jingin.
\c 28
\s1 David Dinga Pathen Pathen Hi Panpi Le Hoidohna
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai kasongpi nakom'a kataove, Ngaipeh lou in neikoi hihbeh in. Ajeh chu nangin neithip sanleh keijong lhadah ing kating kathi ding ahitai.
\p 
\v 2 Hepina ngeh a neipanpi dia katao teng nei ngaipeh tei in, kakhut kahin domsang'in namun theng lam kahinsan e.
\p 
\v 3 Thilse bolnom jing a, akam uva thungei ngei seija alung sung uva thilse jeng gonle ho to nei sumang tha hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 4 ama hon achan ding dol u athilse bolu toh kitoh in got na pejengin! Athilse bolu dungjui chetnin lethuh jengin! Michunga athilse bol gu'utoh kitoh in amaho chungah chuhsah in.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakaiyin ipi abolham ti ama hon anahsah pouve, Pathen Pathen khut sem ipi jeh a umham agel pouve, hijeh a chu aman abotel a tonsot gei a kitung doh lou diu ahitai.
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah in umhen! Ajeh chu khotona kangaicha a kataona chu eijah pehtai.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai hi kahat na le kalum ahi. Kalungthim pumpin ama chu katah san e. Aman eikithopin kalungthim kipanan adim e. Thangvahna la'n keiman kasam phonge.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaiyin amite thahat apei, ama hi athaonu lengpa dinga ahoidohna kulpi ahi
\p 
\v 9 Namite huhhing in! Kelngoi chingpha bangin nagoulu Israel chu phatthei bohtan, chule tonsot in amaho hi nabanjetnin puitan.
\c 29
\s1 David In Ijakai Pathen Pathen Loupina Jeng Ahi Ti
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 Nangho vanmi hon Yahweh Pakaichu jana peuvin; Aloupi na le athahatna jeh in Yahweh Pakaichu jana pecheh un.
\p 
\v 2 Amin loupinajeh in Yahweh Pakai chu jabolcheh un. Athenna thupitah jehchun Yahweh Pakaichu chibai bohun.
\p 
\v 3 Twipi chungah Yahweh Pakai ogin athong doh e. Vanthamjol ginbanginPathen Pathen loupina akithonge. Yahweh Pakaihi twikhanglen chungah akithonge.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai ogin hi thaneitah ahi, Yahweh Pakai ogin hi thupitah ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai Ogin hin Cedar thing thupitah ho jong aban tumboh gam e; Yahweh Pakai thupinan Lebanon Cedar thingho jong asubong soh gamtai.
\p 
\v 6 Aman Lebanon moljeng jong bongnou bangin akichop sah e, Aman Hermon moljeng jong gambong bangin akichop sah e.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai oginhi kolphe meivah gimneitah banga ginga ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai Ogin chun gamthip gamgolai jeng jong akilinsah e; Kadesh gamgolai jong Pathen Pathen'in akilin sah e.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai Ogin hin gangpi phung phatah ho jong ahot ling in, gammang jong asuchai hel e. AHou-In theng sungah mijousen “Aloupi” tin asam uve.
\p 
\v 10 Yahweh Pakai chu twipi chunga chun atouvin vai ahom e.
\p 
\v 11 Yahweh Pakaiyin amite thahat apen, Yahweh Pakaiyin amite chamna apen phatthei aboh'e.
\c 30
\s1 Huhdohna Jal'a David In Pathen Pathen Athangvah
\s1 Hou-In kilhangdoh nia sah dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai nangin neihuhdoh tahjeh in kahin thangvah e. Nangin kagalmite kachunga nakithang-at sahpon ahi.
\p 
\v 2 O Yahweh Pakai, Pathen ka Pathen panpi ngaichan kahin kouvin nangman ka tahsa nakiledoh sah tai.
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai nangin lhankhuh a kon'in neihin puidoh in, thina kokhuh a ka lhahlut na dinga kon'in jong neihoidoh sah e.
\p 
\v 4 Nangho Pathen Pathen mite jousen Yahweh Pakai thangvahna lasaovin! Amintheng chu choi an'un.
\p 
\v 5 Ajeh chu alunghan hi phat chomcha bou ahijin, ami hepina vang hinkhoa ding ahi. Ka na nikho ho jong kipanin ajui pai jitai.
\p 
\v 6 Keiman ka phatthei nikhon, “Imachan eisutang jouponte!” kanati.
\p 
\v 7 O Yahweh Pakai nami hepinahin muol bangin eisudettai. Keija kon a nakiheimang jitengleh keima kading jou jipoi.
\p 
\v 8 O Yahweh Pakai nahenga kahung tao ahi. Nami hepina chu kathum in hitin kaseije,
\p 
\v 9 “Keima kathi alhankhuh a ka lhalut teng nangdinga ipi phachom dingham? Katahsa leivui in nang navah choi thei dingham? Nakitah na thu chu hiche hin aphondoh thei ding ham?
\p 
\v 10 Neihin ngaipeh in Yahweh Pakai neihin khoto in. O Yahweh Pakai neihin kithopin”
\p 
\v 11 Nangin kalung khamnahi kipah tah a lam nan neiheidoh pehtai. Nangin kalung khamna silpon neilahdoh pehin kipana silpon joh neisilpehtan ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Hitiachu thipsan louva thangvahna la kasah jing theina dingin. O Yahweh Pakai Pathen ka Pathen, keiman nangma tonsot in thangvah jing tange.
\c 31
\s1 David In Kicha Le Tija Pum'a Pathen Pathen Akou
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia David Labol
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai neihuhdoh ding ngaichan nakom kahin bel e; Jumna neimusah hihbehin. Neihuhdohin ajeh chu nangma chondihtah Pathen Pathen nahi.
\p 
\v 2 Kataona najah nadin neingai peh tei in; neihung huhdoh loi in. Kakiselna songpin pang jinginlang, kahoidohna kulpi hijingin.
\p 
\v 3 Nangmahi kasongpile kakulpi nahi namin loupina dingin kahahsatna a kon'in neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 4 Kadougal hon kalhuhna dinga thang eikampeh naova kon'in neihuhdoh in, ajeh chu kahoidoh nahi nangma a bou aum'e.
\p 
\v 5 Kalhagao nangma khut a ka pedoh tai. Neihuhdoh in Yahweh Pakai ajeh chu nangmahi kitah jing Pathen Pathen nahi.
\p 
\v 6 Phatchom nabei semthu pathen hou hokhu keiman kathet ahi. Kenvang Yahweh Pakai katahsan jing e.
\p 
\v 7 Nami ngailutna longlou jeh in keima kipah thanom jinginge, ajeh chu nangin kaboina ho neihet peh jingin chuleh kalung gimna jouse nangin neihet thempeh jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Nangin kadougal ho khutnah neipelutpon, lungmon na munjoh a neikoi jin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Neikhoton Yahweh Pakai ajeh chu keima hahsatna a um kahin kamitlhin kamit akhutan ahi. Kahinna le katahsa abeipaiding ahitai.
\p 
\v 10 Lungkham a thipaiding kahitai, gentheinan kahinkho asuhchom tai. Chonset in kajaitha anem sah in asung langa beipai ding kahitai.
\p 
\v 11 Kamelma ten eisamseovin, kaheng kakom ten eitheuvin ahi. Kagol kapaite jeng jongin eihin naingam tapouvin ahi. Lampi dunga eimu jongleh ajammang gamji taove.
\p 
\v 12 Keima mithisa bang leh bel kehsa bangin notthap in kaumtai.
\p 
\v 13 Keima chung changhi thujoungen eikisei khum in tijatnan eium kimvel tan, kadougal ten keidounan thilse agong un kahinkho hi suhmang ding agouve.
\p 
\v 14 Ahinlah Yahweh Pakai keima nanga kingai jing kahin, “Nangma Pathen ka Pathen nahi!” kati.
\p 
\v 15 Khonung kakhankho hi nangkhut a um ahin hitia tanglouva eidelle jinghoa kon'in neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 16 Nami khotona chun nasohpa hi hinsalvah in, nami ngailutna longlou chun neihin huhdoh tan.
\p 
\v 17 O Yahweh Pakai neijumso hihbeh in, ajeh chu panpi ngaichan nangma kakou jinge, miphalou ho chu jumsah jon, amaho chu alhankhuh uvah thipsan sahtan.
\p 
\v 18 Jouthu pot na alei u suthip in, ami noise nao le Pathen Pathen mite a houset nao leichu suthip jengin.
\p 
\v 19 Vo Yahweh Pakai nangma gingte dingin nangin ijakai nasuh nengpeh hi iti phat apha hitam. Panpi ngaicha a nakom'a hungte nangman naphat thei in, vannoi mite mitmu changtah in nangman phatthei nabohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Nangin amaho chu suhsetding gohoa kon'in na angsunga nahoi bitjin, chuleh ahousetnao leile danga kon'in jong na angsung'ah nahoibit jinge.
\p 
\v 21 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvahin umhen, ajeh chu Aman angailutna longlou kidangtah chu eimusah jingin, kachen na khopi gal akinokhum a kon'in jong eihoidoh sahtan ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Lunglinglao pum in keima kapengjah in, “Yahweh Pakai toh eiki sukhentai!” kati. Hinla Yahweh Pakai nangin nei kho to dia ka ka na neijahpeh in panpi ngaicha a kakouna neidonbut tai.
\p 
\v 23 Nangho Pathen Pathen mite ho Yahweh Pakai chu ngailu vin! Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin ama a kingai jingho chu ahuhdoh jingin ahi. Ahinlah mi noiseho chu engbolna nasatah apejin ahi.
\p 
\v 24 Hijeh chun Yahweh Pakaiya kinepna neiho jouse hatnunlang hangun!
\c 32
\s1 Ngaidamna'a Kon Phattheina Thudol'a David Vahchoila
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 Oh, asei ngailou nahou ki angaidam a achon set nahou kisuhmang peh ho iti thanop um hitam.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakaiyin ajihlutsa achonset nao athaimang peh a ahinkhou jongkitah tah a mangho chu iti kipa um a hitam!
\p 
\v 3 Keiman kachonset kaphon nomlou chun katahsa chu amangthah anahin, niseh in kapeng in kamao jinge.
\p 
\v 4 Sun le jan in kipui dih na nakhujol chun eidou ve. Nipilai a nichangsat in asuhkang twihu bangin katha asukang hel jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Akhon nan kachon setna nahenga kaphong in, kamo najouse selguh ding golou vin kaseitai “Kalouchal kasetna jouse Yahweh Pakai kom'a phongdoh tang e” kati. Hiti chun Yahweh Pakai nangin neingaidam e! Kachonsetna jouse abeisoh tai.
\p 
\v 6 Hijeh chun, phatpha umlai hin Pathen Pathen mite jouse naheng a taocheh uhen, hiche thutanna twilen lah a alhahlut lou nadiuvin.
\p 
\v 7 Ajeh chu nangma hi kakiselna kulpi nahin; nangin boinana a kon'in neihuhdoh e. Galjona lan neiumkimvel tai.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaiyin aseije, “Nahinkho a lampi phapen achu kapui le ding ahi. Keiman kathu mop a kavetsui jing ding nahi.
\p 
\v 9 Sakol le Sangan bangin hetna beiyin um hih in, ajo leh kamdal le thihkol bupeh a thunoiya ki koi nabah loding ahi.”
\p 
\v 10 Miphalou ho hi lungkhamna tamtah in abomjin, ahinla Yahweh Pakai tahsan hovang angailutna longlouvin aum kimvel jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Hijeh chun ama lungdei a chon ho Yahweh Pakai a kipah thanom jingun! Milung thengho jouse thanom tah in khosam un!
\c 33
\s1 Misempa Le Misudampa Pathen Pathen Vahchoina
\p 
\v 1 Pathen Pathen mite jousen Yahweh Pakai thangvahna la kipah tah in saohen; milung thenghon Ama athangvah diuhi lomtah ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Semjang gin ngaitah in Yahweh Pakai thangvah un, tumgin jangsom ngaitah saijin nguiheo vin saovin.
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakai thangvahnan lathah saovin; thepna neitah in selangdah saijun lang kipah tah in la saovin.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai thusei jouse chu atah ahin chuleh anatoh athilbol jouse chu tahsan thei cheh ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Adihleh apha kiti jouse chu Yahweh Pakai deilam ahin, Ami ngailutna longlou chun vannoi leiset hi adimin ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakai thucheng hin bou vanmun hi asem doh in, Ama thucheng haikhum chun ahsi jouse apendoh sah tai.
\p 
\v 7 Aman twikhanglen jong agamgi asempeh in chule twikhanglen jouse hi munkhat a aveikhom sah in akoidet in ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Vannoi leiset pumpin Yahweh Pakaihi jana peohen, chuleh mijouse a-angsung a kichatah in dingu hen.
\p 
\v 9 Ajeh chu ama thucheng khat in leiset khang akipatsah ahi! Ama thupeh a kitungdoh jeng ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Yahweh Pakaiyin namtin vaipi thil gon houchu asuhboi peh in, chuleh atohgon hou jouse chu asuhmo peh in ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Ahinlah Yahweh Pakai thilgon vang tonsot in adet jing e, ama tohgot ho chu itih a jong killing lou ahi.
\p 
\v 12 A Pakaiyu Pathen Pathen hikha nammite chu anunnom ahiuve, Yahweh Pakaiyin agoulo dinga alhen nammite chu anunnom ahiuve.
\p 
\v 13 Yahweh Pakaiyin vanna kon'in mihemte jouse ahin ven musohkei e.
\p 
\v 14 Alaltouna a kon'in ahin ven leiset chunga cheng jouse hindan ahesohkeijin ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Alung thim u sempa ama ahijeh in alung gellu le athilbol jouseu ahesohkei e.
\p 
\v 16 Gal manchah phapen in lengpa huhdoh jou pontin, hangta le hansan nan jong gal hat pa ahuhdoh jou poi.
\p 
\v 17 Gal satna sakol khatnin jong gal na josah jouding ahipon, thahatna jousen jong nang nahuhdoh jouponte.
\p 
\v 18 Ahinla Yahweh Pakaiyin ama gingte, angailutna longlou va ki ngaijing ho avelhi jing e.
\p 
\v 19 Yahweh Pakaiyin amaho chu athina diuva kon'in ahuhdoh jin athigam nadiuva kon'in ahuhdohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Keihon Yahweh Pakaiyah kinepna kakoi ui. Ajeh chu ama hi eiki thopiu leh eilum uva pang ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Ama a hin ilungthimu akipah in, ajeh chu eihon amin thenga tahsan na dettah inei un ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Vo Yahweh Pakai nami ngailutna longlou achun eium kimvel u hen, ajeh chu nang jenga bou ka kinepnao aum'e.
\c 34
\s1 David In Phat Jousea Pathen Pathen Avahchoi
\s1 Anomang pa Abimelech masang a mingol bang a aum nachung a David labol
\p 
\v 1 Keiman Yahweh Pakai chu phat tin in thang vah in kate. Yahweh Pakai thagvah nahi kakam sunga gingdoh jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Keima Yahweh Pakaiya bou kithang-at jing ding kahin; Panpi beite jouse lunglut cheh uhen.
\p 
\v 3 Hungun Yahweh Pakai loupi nahi seiphong khom u hitin amin hi choi-an khom u hite.
\p 
\v 4 Keima Yahweh Pakai kom'a kataovin aman kataona eisanpeh tai. Aman kakichatna jousea jong eilhat doh tai.
\p 
\v 5 Ama panpi ding ngaicha jouse vah bangin hungvah doh untin, amai uva jachatna muthim jinglouhel ding ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Kahahsat behseh phat in kataovin Yahweh Pakaiyin eingai peh e; aman kaboina jouse eisuh lhap peh tai.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai vantil chu hoidamna ahin; ama ging te aman aumkimvel in ahuhdoh jinge.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai phatje chu patepmun lang veovin, Yahweh Pakaiya kisel jing mite chu iti kipa hitaovem!
\p 
\v 9 Nangho Pathen Pathen mite ho Yahweh Pakai chu ging jingun ajeh chu ama ging jingten angai chat jouse amudiu ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Keipi bahkai gol hat laitah jong agilkel jin, ahin Yahweh Pakai tahsandet jing hovang thilpha alhasam ngaipouve.
\p 
\v 11 Kachate ho hung uvin kaseihi kingai phaovin, chuleh keiman Pathen Pathen ginje kahilding nahiu ve.
\p 
\v 12 Hinkho sottah leh phattheina lhingset a hingnom umkha em?
\p 
\v 13 Thuse seinan na lei tuhtangin lang chuleh nakam jong jouseinan mang hih in!
\p 
\v 14 Thilse a kon'in kihai mangin lang thilpha bol in, chamna hol inlang hichu chepin.
\p 
\v 15 Yahweh Pakai mitin thilpha boljingho avesui jingin; panpi ngai a koute din akol tenin jong akihong jing e.
\p 
\v 16 Hinla thilse bolte chu dou mit nin aven, aman amin u leiset akon athaimang ding ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Yahweh Pakaiyin panpi ngaichaho kouna angaipeh in. Aboi naova kon'in ahuhdoh jin ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Lungthim kisuchipte kom'a Yahweh Pakai chu anai in; Alhagao kisu gimte ahuhdoh jin ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Michonpha hon boina tampi atohjiuvin, hinla Yahweh Pakaiyin phat tinin ahung huhdoh jin ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin michonpha ho gule chang ahoibit pehjin; khatchajong abohsah pon ahi!
\p 
\v 21 Hamset nan migiloute hinkho alah tei ding, michonpha ho hotbol tejong got na chang tei diu ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Hinla Yahweh Pakaiyin ama kin bol ho vang alhatdoh ding, ama a kisel jing honjong themmo changlou diu ahi.
\c 35
\s1 Thudih Tanna Dia Pathen Pathen Henga David Taona
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai, eidou ho hi nangin kidoupin, ei kisatpi ho jong nangin kisatpin.
\p 
\v 2 Nalum leh naumpho hin kipat in. Galmun a din kigon lang neihung kithopin.
\p 
\v 3 Eihin delkhum ho dounan natengcha leh nateng muh chu hin lam tan. “Keiman gal kajopeh ding nahi!” ti neijah sah tan.
\p 
\v 4 Eithat goho chunga hin jumna le jachatna lhun sah in, eigimbol a eisumang go ho hi jumson lang nungno jeng tan.
\p 
\v 5 Huilah a changvai alenmang bangin lenmang sah in, Yahweh Pakaiya kon a vantil banga hung chu semmang sah in.
\p 
\v 6 A lam lhah nao thimsah inlang lhonalsah in, Yahweh Pakai vantil chun nungdel peh u hen.
\p 
\v 7 Keiman amaho kabol sepoi, ahin ama hon kei matna dingin kotong eilai khum un ahi! Ken amaho kabol sepoi ahin ama hon keimat nadin kotong alai uve.
\p 
\v 8 Hijeh chun amaho chunga hetman louvin mathahna hunglhung hen! Kei ona dia asem u kotong chu amaho manthahna hijo tahen.
\p 
\v 9 Chuteng keima Yahweh Pakai akakipa ding ahi. Eilhatdoh jeh a keima kipa thanom ding kahi.
\p 
\v 10 Katahsa chunga kagu kachang jouse pum a Yahweh Pakai ka thangvah ding ahi: “Yahweh Pakai koiham nang toh kitekah theiding? Koidang ba ham mihatpa thaneina a konna panpi beipa huhdoh a chu?”
\p 
\v 11 Engbolna dih louvin eithemmo sah un. Kahetphahlou jouthu a mkonna eikichan e.
\p 
\v 12 ama hon kathilpha bol jeng jong thilsen eile thuh un lung lhahnan kangui heltai.
\p 
\v 13 Ahijeng vangin ama hon anat tengu leh keiman amaho kalainatpi jin khaodip pon kakisil in anngol in amaho kataopeh jin ahi. Hinla kataona donbut louvin ahung kinung le jitai.
\p 
\v 14 Ka golpha le insung mi monga kagel jeh in kalungkham pin, eihinga kanu kalainatpi bang bangin kalainat pi jin ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Hinlah ken tunia boina katophat in amaho akipah un keidounan thanom tah in akiloi khomun, hiti chun kahetkhahlou miho kisan in tujengin jong eino khum un; phat tin in eihouse jing jengun ahi.
\p 
\v 16 ama hon einuisat un eitam seovin noise tah in eihagel khum un ahi.
\p 
\v 17 O Yahweh Pakai itih chan gei pi neivet a donlouva neikoi ding hitam?
\p 
\v 18 Chutengleh mipi tamtah ki khom te lah a kipathu kahin seiding ahi. Mipi ho jouse masanga nangma kahin thangvah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Kajolel nachung a hin eidou te kipa thanop sah hihbeh in. Kamuiset nachungin jong ajeh bei a eivetda ho kitai sah hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 20 ama hon chamna thu aseipouvin, ama hon thepmona neilou atoh dingdol bep tongho dounan thilse agong jingun ahi.
\p 
\v 21 “Aha! Aha! ipi bol kigo nahi kamit tah un kamudoh taove!” tin asam uve.
\p 
\v 22 O Yahweh Pakai nangin hicheghi namusohkei in nahesoh e, donlouvin koihihbeh in O Yahweh Pakai. neidalha hihbeh in O Yahweh Pakai.
\p 
\v 23 Hungthoudoh in! eihuhdoh dingin hung dingdoh jengtan! Yahweh ka Pakai le Pathen ka Pathen kachung thu hi neitan peh in.
\p 
\v 24 O Yahweh Pakai ka Pathen Pathen, kamo louna neiphondoh peh tan, ajeh chu nangma thudih a thutan nahi. Kaboina chung chon a kadougal te nuisat in neium sah hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 25 “Veovin itup uchu imutaove! Tua hi ahingsan a inehchai diu ahitai!” tisah hihbeb in.
\p 
\v 26 Kahahsatna nikhoa kipah ho sujum inlang jachat sah in. Kachunga hanla samho hi jumna leh minsetnan lhuh khumin.
\p 
\v 27 Ahin koi hileh keima ei huhdia hung ho jouse chu kipana lentah pen. “Yahweh Pakai aloupi e aman asoh hi lunglhai tah in phatthei aboh in lungmon na apei!” tin tanglouvin samjingu hen.
\p 
\v 28 Chuteng keiman nathutan adihji samphong ingting niseh a nangma kavahchoi ding ahi.
\c 36
\s1 David In Pathen Pathen Lungsetna Longlou Aphondoh
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia Pathen Pathen soh David labol
\p 
\v 1 Chonsetnin miphalou ho lungthim gilsungah thu aseijin ahi. Ama hon Pathen Pathen ginna him him anei pouve.
\p 
\v 2 Akihisah naovin amaho le amaho akijou lhepmun ichan geija gilouleh phamo hiuvam ti akihet pouve.
\p 
\v 3 Athusei anatohna hou jousehi adihlou leh kijou lhepna ngen ahi. Chingthei tah a natoh leh thilpha bol dinghi adatthei pouve.
\p 
\v 4 Jankhosot in ahah un thil dihlou tohgon tamtah agong jiuvin ahi. Atohdoh uhi apha khatcha aumpoi. Thilsea konna kiheidoh ding angaito mong mong pouve.
\p 
\v 5 O Yahweh Pakai nami ngailutna longlouhi van bangin aki hohjale, nakitahna hin meilom kaina mun ho hi akho khel e.
\p 
\v 6 Nadih na jong muolsang vum tobang ahi. Nathutan dihdan jong twikhanglen thuhtah abang e. Nangin mihemleh ganhing ho jong kibanga nangailut ahi.
\p 
\v 7 O Pathen Pathen nami ngailutna longlou hi eti mamtam hitam! Mihem jousen nami ngailutna lhaving limnoija chun choldo na anei ui.
\p 
\v 8 Na insunga nehkemlou ann a chun navah van, kanglou nalui a twi chun nadon sah e.
\p 
\v 9 Ajeh chu nangma mihem hung kondohna twinah nahin, keihon kamu u vahjonghi nanga kon ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Yahweh Pakai nangma ngailuho chung a nami ngailutna longlou chu londoh sah in, milung thengho chunga thu adih in tanpeh in.
\p 
\v 11 Mi kiletsah ho neichotpha sah hih in, ahilouleh miphalouho sot tol le neihisah hih in.
\p 
\v 12 Ven! Thil dihlou bolte ho alhugam taove! Amaho chu kithoudoh kit loudinga sot lhuh ahitaove.
\c 37
\s1 Mikitahte Le Migiloute Dinmun Kibah Loudan
\s1 David Labol
\p 
\v 1 Mikitahlou te chung a lungkham dan, thil dihlou bolte jong thangse hih in.
\p 
\v 2 Ajeh chu amaho khu hamhing banga molloi diu, nipilai pahchaho banga goplha loidiu ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakai chu tahsa inlang thilpha bollin. Chutileh gamsunga lungmongin chengin natin nakhan touding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai a kipah jingin, chutileh aman na lungsunga nangai chatchan napehding ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Nabol natoh jouse Yahweh Pakai a pelut jengin, ama chu tahsanin chutileh aman nakithopi ding ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Aman nathem na chu khovah banga muthimlah a avahdoh sahding ahi. Chuleh nachanchin jong sunlai nisa banga avahdoh sahding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai masangah lungneng chan ngahhat in Aman ahintoh ding chu ngah hat in. Mi giloute ahaotheiukhu lungkhampi hih un, athilse gon ujong lunghimo peh hih in.
\p 
\v 8 Lungchom lunghan bol-hih in! Lung sat a kon'in jong kihei mangin. Nalung lhaso hih in hichun thilse lamma bou napui lut ding ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Ajeh chu migiloute kisumang ding ahin, amavang Yahweh Pakai tahsan a dingdet ho chun gamsung alodiu ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Migilou ho hi gangtah a mangthah diu ahin, amaho chu hol le jonglehchun mangthai ding ahitaove.
\p 
\v 11 Kisunem tah a umhon gamsung alodiu ahin, lungmong tah leh ninglhing tah a inchengdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Mi gilouten Pathen Pathen ngaisah miho douna ahinbol diu; ama hon engset sanna ahin nelpehdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Hinlah Yahweh Pakaiyin amaho chu ahin nuisat in, ajeh chu aman achung thu kitanna ding nikhou ahunglhun chu amui.
\p 
\v 14 Mi-engsen hon mivaicha ho leh suhgam theija umte that dingin achemjam u hin asatdoh un, athalpiu hin loisal uvin tin, thilpha bolte chu ahin suhmang gotdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Hinlah achemjam un amaho lungchang asutpai johding chuleh athalpiu chu bong ding ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Ase bola thil tampi neisangin Pathen Pathen mite hia lhomcha nei aphachomjoi.
\p 
\v 17 Ajeh chu migiloute hatna chu kisumang ding, Pahen mite vang Yahweh Pakaiyin avenbit jing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Ani ania Yahweh Pakaiyin themmona neilou ho chu avetsui ding, chule ama hon tonsotna mang louding gou chu alodiu ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Amaho chu hahsat nikho jongleh kijumso loudiu kellhah nikho jongleh angaichat ho anei teidiu ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Migiloute mangthai diu ahi, Yahweh Pakai dougal miho jong loulaija pahcha tobang ahiuve-mei banga hung mang loi diu ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Migilouten asumpa lah u anungsah ngaipouvin, Pathen Pathen mite vang hongphal tah a peh jeng ahiuve.
\p 
\v 22 Yahweh Pakai phatthei changhon gamsung alodiu ahin, aman asapset ho vang mangthah diu ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Pathen Pathen mite, Yahweh Pakaiyin akalsondan avetpeh in, ahinkho mandan jouse aman akipapin ahi.
\p 
\v 24 Amaho chu kipal jonglehu lhupai loudiu, ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin akhut in atuh jing ui.
\p 
\v 25 Phat khat lai chun khangdong kahin tun kateh tai, ahin Pathen Pathen mite paidoh a aumlam kahepon, achateu jong khutdon apangkhapouve.
\p 
\v 26 Pathen Pathen miten khotona neitah in sumpa ahomjiuvin, chuleh achateujong phatthei achang jiuve.
\p 
\v 27 Thilse a kon'in kiheidoh in thilpha bol in, chutileh tonsot a gamsunga nachen ding ahi.
\p 
\v 28 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin thudih bou adei in, Pathen Pathen'in acha teu jong donlou a akoi louhel ding ahi. Aman ahoibit jing ding, Gitlou bol chate vang mangthah diu ahi.
\p 
\v 29 Pathen Pathen chaten gamsung alodiu ahin, tonsotna cheng jingdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 30 Pathen Pathen mite kamsunga thudih apotjin adihle adihlou ahilthem jiuve.
\p 
\v 31 Pathen Pathen Dan chu amaho changval din akisan un, hijeh a chu Ama lampi a konna vah lonle loudiu ahi.
\p 
\v 32 Migilou ten Pathen Pathen mite achanglhi leuvin, suhmang nading lampi ahol jiuve.
\p 
\v 33 Hinlah Yahweh Pakaiyin migiloute alolhin sah louhel ding Pathen Pathen'in mikitah te patepna a aum tengu le themmo achan louhel ding ahi.
\p 
\v 34 Yahweh Pakai ah kinem jingin. Alamlhong achun ching thei tah in lamjot in. Aman nadopsang a agam leiset nalosah ding ahi. Migilou te manthahvang namu ding ahi.
\p 
\v 35 Keiman migilou le khotonabei te Lebanon gama Ceder thingphung phatah banga akhantouvu kamui.
\p 
\v 36 Ahin kanungvet kitle, ana beisoh taove! Ken kahol le vang in kamudoh joutapoi!
\p 
\v 37 Milungtheng ho leh miphaho khu veovin, chamna adei ho chu amakhouva thilphatah in angah jing ui.
\p 
\v 38 Hinla thilse bolte suhmanga umdiu ahi; ama hon khonung hinkho anei pouve.
\p 
\v 39 Yahweh Pakaiyin mikitah te chu ahuhdoh jin; boina nikho hoa jong Ama hi akulpiu ahi.
\p 
\v 40 Aman amaho chu akithopin, migiloutea kon'in ahuhdohjin ahi. Aman amaho chu ahuhdoh in, ama hon ama a lungmon na anei un ahi.
\c 38
\s1 David Lungheiya Pathen Pathen Henga Ataona
\s1 Pathen Pathen'in asuh mil lou nadia David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai lung phatmo nan neilethuh hih in, nalunghan jeh in jong neijep hih in!
\p 
\v 2 Nathal changho kasunga akikam dentan, nakhuttum in neivo lhutan ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Neilunghan khum jeh in katahsa pumpi hi anan, kachonset naho jeh in katahsa achip soh tai.
\p 
\v 4 Kathepmo nan eilon khum in, agihdan poh jouhoi ahi tapoi.
\p 
\v 5 Ngol hoi tah a kana chonset jehin, kamaha anasetan auidoh leotai.
\p 
\v 6 Kathoh gimna hin ei kong konsah tai, lung gim tah in nilhum kei in kavahlen ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Khosih pi kasunga meikong bangin a allin, eidammo sahtai.
\p 
\v 8 Keima kalhasam in kapum in kagoi lhatai. Kalungthim natna a kon'in kapeng pengin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai nangin ipi kangai chat ham nahei, nangin ka khoisatna jouse najai.
\p 
\v 10 Kahaina hu alhasam tan katha beitai, chule kamit in jong kho amu tapoi.
\p 
\v 11 Kangailut chengle kagol kapaiten kahivei hi akichaovin eidalha taove. Ka insung mite jeng jong achomin aumtauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Hiche jeng a jong chun kagalmi ten kathi nading thang akam nalai uve. Kaman thahna ding toh gon anei un, nilhum keijin kathi nading agong tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Hinlah ken eikigih naho jouse chu kakijah mosah in, chuleh amasang uvah apaomo bangin thipbeh in kaumtai.
\p 
\v 14 Imacha jahlouding kanom in chuleh donbutna jong donbutlou ding kanom e.
\p 
\v 15 Ajeh chu O Yahweh Pakai nangma ngah jinga um a kahi. Nangin kataona neidonbut tei ding ahi O Yahweh Pakai Pathen ka Pathen.
\p 
\v 16 Keima katao in, “kadougalte noise tah in eivetsah dan, kalhuhna a jong kitaisah dan.”
\p 
\v 17 Keima tanglouva kathohgim na-ah akichaipai ding kahitai.
\p 
\v 18 Hinlah kachonset naho kaphong-doh in, ka na chonna ho chu kakisih behseh jenge.
\p 
\v 19 Keiman dougal khohtah tah ho kanei e; ama hon ajeh beihel in eidou ui.
\p 
\v 20 ama hon thilpha kabol chu thilsen eilethuh un, chuleh thilpha kachepi jing jeh in eidouvun ahi.
\p 
\v 21 O Yahweh Pakai neidalhahih in Pathen ka Pathen kei a kon'in um gamla hihbehin,
\p 
\v 22 O Yahweh Pakai eihuh hingpa hungloi inlang nei kithopin.
\c 39
\s1 Chomkah Louva Hinkho Kikhel
\s1 Jeduthun lalamkai pa dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 “Katohna chunga chingthei tah in thil bol ing kating, ka thusei doh chenga chonseponge. Kavel a Pathen Pathen ginglou ho aumteng kalei kakituh tang ding ahi” tin kei le kei kakihou ve.
\p 
\v 2 Hinla hitia thipbeh a kaum a thupha jeng jong changkhat cha seilouva kaum chun ka lungsunga lung gimna akhoh secheh in ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Kalunga kagelbe chan in kalung gimna akhoh cheh in, hiti chun seilou in kaum thei pon ahi:
\p 
\v 4 “Yahweh Pakai leiset a kahinkho hi ichan a chom hitam neihin hetsah jingin, kahin nikho hi akisim jinghi neigeldoh sah in, kahin kho iti chom hitam?
\p 
\v 5 Nangin kahinkhov hi ichan geija chom a nasem hitam kakhut phang sangin jong asaojo poi. Nang dingin kahinkho lhum kei jong hi haikhat bou ahi soh tan, Mihem hinkho khat cheh jong hi haikhat cheh bou ahi.”
\p 
\v 6 Mihem hinkho hi milom kitol bang bep bou ahin, kisah lunggim naho jong hetman lou kah in akichai loi ji tai. Gou ikhol khom un, kon ahin man ding ham jong ihe doh ji pouve.
\p 
\v 7 Hijeh chun Yahweh Pakai hoi a kinep na kakoi ding ham? Nanga bou kakinep na aum'e.
\p 
\v 8 Kaset bolnom na a kon'in neihuhdoh in, mingol ho neinoise sah hih in.
\p 
\v 9 Keima na ansung a thipchet in kaum'e; imacha jong kasei louding ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Ahinla Yahweh Pakai nei engbol hih in! Nakhut gu dounan kachao lhagam tai.
\p 
\v 11 Kachonset u suhdih na dia neijep tengu le, kasah lut u chonsetna chu nget in aneh banginajun lhaji tan ahi. Tahbeh in mihem khat cheh hi haikhat bou ahi.
\p 
\v 12 O Yahweh Pakai kataona ngai inlang panpi ngaija kataona neingai pih in! kamit lhi lon nah sah mon koi hih in, ajeh chu keima hi namaljin bou kahin, kema masang a kapu kapa teu bang a kholjin vahle kahi bouve.
\p 
\v 13 Hiche leiset hinkho hi kadalhah a kahin kho abei masang kakipa a kanui kit na din nalung han na, nagim bol na ho toh neichom khen in.
\c 40
\s1 David In Lungneng Tah'a Pathen Pathen Anga
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 Panpi ding ngai in Yahweh Pakai chu lungneng tah in kangah jing e, aman kahenglam ahin ngan kataona eisanpih tai.
\p 
\v 2 Aman lunglhah nathei kotong a kon'in eikai doh in, buol sung a buon ngan lah a kon'in eikai doh in tolgo chung a eidin sah in kakal skonna jong eisuh dih pih e.
\p 
\v 3 Kasah ding lathah khat eipen, I-Pathen u Pathen vahchoi na ding la khat eipen ahi. Mi tamtah in ana toh hin mu un tin adatmo ding u ahi. Hitia chu ama hon Yahweh Pakai chu atah san diu ahi.
\p 
\v 4 O Yahweh Pakai tahsan na a ding det ho iti akipah tadiuvem, ama hon mikiletsah ho chung a tahsan na anei pouvin ahilouleh semthu pathen limhou ho jong atahsan pouve.
\p 
\v 5 O Yahweh Pakai, Pathen ka Pathen, nangin keiho dingin thil kidangtah tah neibolpeh taove. Neigon peh u thilho hi simjou sutjou hoi ahipoi. Nangto kibang ding koimacha aumpoi. Na kidang natoh doh ho hi sim ding kagon, achaina gei kalhun louding kahei.
\p 
\v 6 Nangman pumgo thilto ho a hin kipana nanei poi. Nei ngaisah thu ho chu tun kahechen tai, nangin chonset thoidam na thilto leh pumgo thilto jong nangeh poi.
\p 
\v 7 Hichun keiman kaseijin, “Ven keima kahung e. Pathen Pathen Lekhabu a kisun bangin:
\p 
\v 8 Nangma lungdei lam bolding hi katha anop na ahi, O Pathen Pathen, ajeh chu ka lungsung a nangma Danthu ho hi akisun lut tai.”
\p 
\v 9 Namite jouse lah a nathutan dih je hi kaphongdoh tai. O het themna nei Yahweh Pakai, nangma banginkichaloubeh in kasei doh tai.
\p 
\v 10 Nadih jedan Kipana Thupha hi keiman kachang a din kalungthim a selguh in kakoi poi; Nakitah na le nami huhhing na thu kasei e. Nahoubung mitheng te lah a namingai lut na long lou le nakitah na chu tanglou in kasei phong jinge.
\p 
\v 11 Yahweh Pakai nangin tanglou vin neingailu jing jengin. Nangailutna le nakitahna chu neihoi bit jing sah in.
\p 
\v 12 Boinan eibom in sim a simjou hoi ahipoi! Kachonsetna akikhol sang'in kalampi jong kamu thei tapoi. Kalujang a kasam sangin atamjo tan hansan na him him kanei jou tapoi.
\p 
\v 13 Yahweh Pakai lungsettah in neihuhdoh in! hung vah in Yahweh Pakai neipanpin.
\p 
\v 14 Eisumang goho hi jumson lang kisuhboi sah in, kahahsat nikho a kipah ho lungdong in nungjam sah in.
\p 
\v 15 “Aha tun akimaikhah tai” ti a asei jeh un, jum nan kichao hen.
\p 
\v 16 Nangkom hinbel jouse kipa na le thanop nan dimset uhen. Nami huhhing na kipapi ho chun “Yahweh Pakai chu aloupi e” tin sam jing u hen.
\p 
\v 17 Keidin vang gentheile vaicha kahi jeh in, Yahweh Pakaiyin alung sung a eihoi jing hen. Yahweh Pakai nang chu eikithopi le eihuhhingpu nahi. O ka Pathen Pathen khongai sot hih in.
\c 41
\s1 Pathen Pathen In Gentheite Akhohsah
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 Mivaichate khoto ho chu anunnom ahi! Amaho chu Yahweh Pakaiyin boina ato nao a kon a ahuhdoh diu ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakaiyin amaho chu ahoibit in ahinghoi jiu ve. Aman amaho chu gamsung ah phatthei aboh in galmiho akon na ahuhdoh ji e.
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakaiyin adam mo naova panpin tin adamdoh sahding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 “O Yahweh Pakai”, katao ahi “eilungset in, neidamdoh sah in ajeh chu nangma dounan kachonsetai.”
\p 
\v 5 Ahinla kadougal ten keima dounan thilse jeng aseiyun ahi. “Itih tah le athin suhmil in aum tadem?” atiu ve.
\p 
\v 6 Kagol kapai bangineihung vil jiuvin, hinla chomloukah in kachung chang guhthim thu asei khom leuvin, eidalhah tengu le muntin in aphonjal ji taove.
\p 
\v 7 Eihot bolten keichung chang a thil phalou ngan aseijun, kachung a thilse ahung lhun dingbou adei un ahi.
\p 
\v 8 “Ama hi thina thei hiveija na ahi” atiuve. “Ama hi damdoh joulou ding ahitai!” atiuve.
\p 
\v 9 Katahsan pen kagol phapen, an kaneh khom pipa jeng jong keima eidouvin apang tai.
\p 
\v 10 Yahweh Pakai neilungset in. Neidamdoh sah kitin amaho hi kalethuh jou nadin!
\p 
\v 11 Yahweh Pakai nangma kachunga nalung lhaije ti kahei ajeh chu nangin kamelma te kachungah gal na lel sahtai.
\p 
\v 12 Nangin kahinkho neihing hoipeh tai, ajeh chu keiman lhamkonna kaneipoi, chuleh nangin atonsot a din na-angsung a neipui luttai.
\p 
\v 13 Israel Pathen Pathen Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah in umhen, Tonsot tonsot a hingjing pa chu. Amen chule Amen!
\c 42
\s1 BU NINA 42-72
\s1 Pathen Pathen Ngaicha'a Dangchah
\s1 Lalamkaipa henga Korah chilhah te labol
\p 
\v 1 Sakhi sitwi chimset ngaichat dangchah bangin, kahin ngaicha e O Pathen Pathen.
\p 
\v 2 Hingjing Pathen Pathen chu dangchah in kalha ngai e. Itih tah le kache a a-anga kachibai theiding ham?
\p 
\v 3 Sunle jan in lonlhi bou ann in kanei tai, kagal miten phat tin in ei enghouvun “Na Pathen Pathen hoija umham atiuve?”
\p 
\v 4 Kalungthim analheh ji e thil umdan ho chu kageldoh ji teng: Pathen Pathen Hou-In a mihonpi chutoh kilhon a, tanggol a Pathen Pathen'inlam jon a kitol a thangvah la kisa a mihonpin golvah kibolji ho chu!
\p 
\v 5 Ibol a kei lunglha dah kahim? Ibol a kalung hibanga hesoh a ham? Keiman Pathen Pathen a kinepna giltah kaneiyin! Ken ama kathang vah kit ding ahi ka huhhing pu Pathen ka Pathen.
\p 
\v 6 Tun keima kalung alhadah lheh jengtai, hinlah Jordan hung kondohna, Hermon molsang lang hijongleh kahin gel doh jing ding nahi.
\p 
\v 7 Nangman twipibang nakinon a naki ho twikhanglen gin chu kajai, nangma twipi kidilleh twipi kitol chun eihin lonvuh in ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Ahinlah niseh in Yahweh Pakaiyin angailutna longlou chun eiphung vuh jingin, chuleh janseh leh ama vahchoila kasajin hinkho eipe a Yahweh Pakai kom'a chun kataojin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 O Yahweh Pakai kasongpi keima kakapme, ipi dinga neisuhmil hitam? Ipidinga kadougal te bol hesoh jeh a lunggima kavale jingding ham?
\p 
\v 10 Eihou setnao hin kagep lhatan ahi, “Na Pathen hoija umham,” tin eidong jingun ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Ipi dinga keima hiti lungkham kahin, epidinga hiti lungboi kahim? Keiman Pathen Pathen nah kakinepna koijing ting chuleh eihuhhing paleh ka Pathen chu avellin thangvah kit inge.
\c 43
\s1 Them Chansah Ding Le Huhdohna Dinga Taona
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen themmona bei kahi neiphongdoh in! Pathen Pathen ginglou hoa kon'in nei vengdoh in, chutengleh mikitah lou ho leh joupan hoa kon'in neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 2 Ajeh chu nang hi kakiselna Pathen Pathen nahi, ibol a neipaidoh hitam? Ibol a keima kadougal ten eibolset jeh a lunggim a kava lele dingham?
\p 
\v 3 Nadih na le navah na chu neihinsol peh in, hichun eilamhil hen. Hiho chun nangma chenna muol theng chu eilhut hen.
\p 
\v 4 Hikom'a chun keima Pathen Pathen maicham achu kasemjang puma kathang vah ding ahi, O Pathen Pathen.
\p 
\v 5 Idia lungkham kahim? Ipidinga kalung lhadah ham? Keiman kakinepna Pathen Pathen a koi inge! Eihuhhingpa le Pathen ka Pathen keiman nangma thangvah kit inge!
\c 44
\s1 Masanga Pathen Pathen Mi Huhdohna Ho Chule Tua Gentheina
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia Korah chapa te labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen, phat sottah masanga kapu kapateu khanglai a nanatohnathil bol ho eina seipeh u chu keiho tah in kanakol un kanajaove:
\p 
\v 2 Nangin nangma helou namtin vaipi ho naban thahat in nana deljam in agam leiset uchu kapu kapateu nanapen ahi. Nangin agalmiteu nana suhlhuh peh in kapu kapateu chu nana chamlhat sah in ahi.
\p 
\v 3 ama hon achemjam uva gal anajouva gam analah u ahipoi; aban thahat uva jong gal anajou ahipoi. Amavang nangma ban thahat leh namaivah chun gal nana jopeh ahi bouve ajeh chu nangin amaho chu nana ngailun ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Nangma kalengpa le Pathen ka Pathen nahin nangin Israel te dingin gal nana jo peh tai.
\p 
\v 5 Nangma thahatna jal a bou kagal miteu kanungno jouvu ahin naming a bou keihon eidouhou kachotphao ahi bouve.
\p 
\v 6 Keiman kathalpi kasongpoi, kachemjamin eihuhdoh dingjong kakinempoi.
\p 
\v 7 Nangma bouvin kagalmi teu chunga galjona neipeh u ahi bouve, hiti hin nangin eihotbol teu chu jumna napejin ahi.
\p 
\v 8 O Pathen Pathen naloupina ho hi tantih neilou va ka samphon jing diu, chule a kumkho a ka thangvah jing diu ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Ahinla tunvang nangin jumthetna neipaidoh u ahitai. Nangin ka sepia hou jeng jong neilamkai peh tapouve.
\p 
\v 10 Nangin kagalmi teu va kon'in neinung jamsah un chuleh eidou houchu kagamsung u nalosah tai.
\p 
\v 11 Nangin kelngoiho bangin eikisat chen chen sah gamtauvin chitin vaipi lah a neithe thang gamtaove.
\p 
\v 12 Nangin nasahlut namitehi manbai tah in najohdoh in man neilouhel toh nabah sahtai.
\p 
\v 13 Nangin kaheng kakomhou noise neichansah tauvin kavelluva mite taitom le houset dingbep in neikoitaove.
\p 
\v 14 Nangin amaho totthang hoina bepseo neihisah tauvin isahlou tah in alu eihih khum tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Ki taitom jingna a konhin kakile doh jouta pouvin kamai uva jumleh jachat mel kapu den taove.
\p 
\v 16 Kajah uhi eitaitomteu housetna thucheng ngen ahin, kamit uva kamu houhi ahileh kachung uva phula nom dougal mite ngen ahiuve.
\p 
\v 17 Hichenghi kathoh jeng vangun keihon nangma kasumil deh pouvin ahi. Kitepna thuchengho jong kasukeh deh pouve.
\p 
\v 18 Kalungthim un nangma kanuse deh pouvin nalampia kon'in jong kajam mangdeh pouve.
\p 
\v 19 Hinlah nangin sial chenna neldi gam anei suchipden taove, nangin thina le muthim neikhu khum taove.
\p 
\v 20 I jemtia keihon Pathen ka Pathen u min kasuh mil uva ahilouleh gamdang semthu pathen houna a kakhut u kalhandoh khah uva ahileh,
\p 
\v 21 Pathen Pathen'in ahet tei ding ahi ajeh chu Aman mihem lungthim a thuguh jouse ahet ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Ahin, nangma jal in niseh in eiki thatnun; kelngoi bangin eiki that taove.
\p 
\v 23 O Yahweh Pakai hung thoudoh in ibol a na imut ham? Hung thoudoh in! neipaidoh pai pai hihbeh un.
\p 
\v 24 Ipidinga namai naheimang ham? Kathohgim naoleh eibolset naohi nanahsah lou hitam?
\p 
\v 25 Keiho leivui lah a kalhumat gam taove, bonlhoh lah a akhupbon kakijam taove.
\p 
\v 26 Hung kipatdoh inlang! Neikithopiuvin! Nami ngailutna longlou chun neihung lhatdoh tauvin.
\c 45
\s1 Lengpa Jineina'a Sah Ding La
\s1 Lalamkai pa dia Korah chapa ten joldei la “Lilies” lakai a sah dia abol'u.
\p 
\v 1 Kalungthim in thu hoi tah ahung kilang e. Keiman lengpa chung chang hiche jaila ngaitah hi lungchin in sei inge, ajeh chu kalei hi jaila themtah pa mol jap tobang ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Nanghi mihem jouselah a ahoipen nahi, na lei a thungei tamtah ahung potdoh e. Pathen Pathen ama tah in tonsotna din phatthei naboh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 3 O galhatpa! nachemjam chu hin kipoh in! nangmahi naloupi in nathupi e!
\p 
\v 4 Nathupina a chun hung kivon inlang galjou dingin hung kondoh tem in, thutah leh thudih chuleh kisuhnemna ho hi chejom sahdingin kondoh inlang datmo umtah tah thilho chu hung tongdoh tan!
\p 
\v 5 Nathal muh ho chu ahem in nagal mite lungsung asunvang jeng tai. Namtin vaipi nakengto noija aumtaive.
\p 
\v 6 Vo Pathen Pathen nalal touna hi tonsot tonsot a chejom jing ding ahi. Naleng tengol a chu thudih tah a vai nahomding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Nangin thudih tah a thutan nadeijin thilse nathet ahi. Hijeh chun Pathen Pathen, nangma Pathen Pathen chun thao nanu ahitai, lengdang sanga nang chungahi kipale thanopna thaotwi chu nasunlhah khum ahitai.
\p 
\v 8 Myrrh, aloes, chuleh cassia hon navon anamtui sel e. Saiha a kisem khopia chu tumging ngaitah a nakilamto ding ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Leng Chanute chu na numei nunnem te lah a aum un. Najet langa ophir sana hoipen ho a kijem lengnu ading e.
\p 
\v 10 O leng chanu te ka thusei ngai un; amapa hi jabol un ajeh chu ama hi na Yahweh Pakai pau ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Ajeh chu sahlut tah naji hi namel-hoinan alunglhai sel e; jabol in, ajeh chu amapa hi na Pakai pa ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Tyre lengpa chanuten jong kipa thilpeh tampi nahung pehdiu ahi. Mihaoten nalung lhaina ding ahin holdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Mounu, leng chanu, chu kivon na sana a kisem sangkholchol a chu iti vet loupia hitam.
\p 
\v 14 Hiche avon loupi tah kivon in lengpa kom lam a ahin pui un, anunjui nungah ho chutoh apuilut un ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Kipah tah le thanom tah a leng inpi sunga ahung akijot lut uchu iti lou a loupi hitam!
\p 
\v 16 Nachate jong apa tobang a leng hung hicheh ding ahiuve. Nangin amaho chu gam tamtah a lenga napan sah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Khang jousea na min thanna kahin pohlut pehding ahi. Hijeh achu namtin vaipin tonsot a nahin thangvah ding ahi.
\c 46
\s1 Pathen Pathen Hi Eiho Dinga Kiselna Le Thahatna Ahi
\s1 Korah chapa ten lalamkai pa heng a O chung hoa sah dia ala bol u.
\p 
\v 1 Pathen Pathenhi ikiselnao leh isongpiu ahi, boina nikho hoa eipanhu diuva kigosa ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Hijeh achu liingkihot henlang molle lhang chim henlang twikhanglen a kilehlut jongleh kicha tapouvinge.
\p 
\v 3 Twikhanglen hi kinong henlang kitum jeng hen. Twikhanglen kinong a ahung letdoh jeng banginmuolle lhang jong kihot chimlha jeng hen.
\p 
\v 4 Vadung khat in I-Pathen'u khopia chun kipa thanopna ahin polut e.
\p 
\v 5 Hiche khopi achun Pathen Pathen achengin kisumang thei louding ahi. Nikho kipat a pat Pathen Pathen'in avenbit jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Leiset chung namtin vaipihi aboitan lenggam ho jong akiling sohtan ahi! Pathen Pathen ahung kisen in ahileh leiset ajunlha gamtan ahi!
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai hatchungnung hi ilah uva aum in, Israel Pathen Pathen hi ikulpiu ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Hungin Yahweh Pakai thil loupi bolhi hungvetan, Hunginlang aman vannoi leiset asuhmang hi hungve tan.
\p 
\v 9 Aman vannoi leiset pumpia galho hi atuhtang in athalpiu leh ateng chau heboh peh gamtan ahi.
\p 
\v 10 “Thipchet un, chule Pathen Pathen kahi hi heovin! Vannoi leiset pumin eijabol cheh diu ahi. Leiset pumpia a hi dopsanga kaum ding ahi.”
\p 
\v 11 Hatchungnung Pathen Pathenhi ilah uva aumme; Israel Pathen Pathen hi ikulpiu ahi.
\c 47
\s1 Pathen Pathen Hi Leiset Pumpi Lengpa Ahi
\s1 Lalamkai pa henga korah chapa te labol
\p 
\v 1 Mijouse hungun! Nakhut benguvin! Pathen Pathen kom'a kipah tah in thangvahna sam un!
\p 
\v 2 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai Hatchungnung chu gimneitah ahi. Ama hi leiset chunga leng thupitah ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Aman imasang uvah namtin vaipi hi asonkun in eidougalteu jong ikengto noi uvah eikoipeh taove.
\p 
\v 4 Gamtep gam chu, angailut Jacob chilhahate, kithang-at tah a kijot eiho lodinga alhen ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Pathen Pathen chu gimnei tah in akal tou in, Yahweh Pakai chu sumkon gin kithong pum'in akal tou in ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Pathen Pathen thangvah la sauvin, thangvah la sauvin; ilengpau thangvah la sauvin, thangvah la sauvin!
\p 
\v 7 Ajeh chu Pathen Pathen hi leiset chung pumpi chunga leng ahi lasah pum'in thangvah un.
\p 
\v 8 Pathen Pathen alaltouna theng chunga atou in namtin vaipi lah a vai ahom'e.
\p 
\v 9 Vannoi leiset vaihomte Abraham Pathen Pathen mitetoh atoukhom'un ahi, ajeh chu leiset chunga leng jouse hi Pathen Pathen'a ahi. Ama hi vannoi leiset chung muntin'a jana achang'in ahi.
\c 48
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Hi Aloupi Tangeiye chule Loupi Tah'a Vahchoi Ding Ahi
\s1 Korah chapa te labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai hi iti loupia hitam, ichan gei a pachat dinga lom hitam, i Pathen'u Pathen chu akhopia acheng'in alhangtheng'a atou in ahi!
\p 
\v 2 Hiche hi asang'in ahoilamdang'e. Leiset pumpi'n mu ding atup un athanom cheh ui. Lhangtheng Zion molhoi hi leng thupipa chenna khopi ahi!
\p 
\v 3 Pathen Pathen ama tah chu Jerusalem indan sung'a chun acheng'in ahi Ama tah hi avengbit'a pang ahi akilang doh e.
\p 
\v 4 Vannoi mite lengho akigom'un hiche khopi dounan ahin nokhum'un ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Ahinla ama hon amuchet phat'un atangchot jeng'un atijauvin ajammang gam tauve.
\p 
\v 6 Amaho chu tijatnan numei naonei hon hahsatna atobangin akithingleu jeng'un ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Ahin nang'in Tarshishte kong thupitah ho solam huijin asuhset bangin nasuse tan ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Keihon hiche khopi loupina chu kanajaovin tunvang Pathen Pathen hatchungnung khopi chu keiho tah in kamuchen tauvin ahi. Hiche hi I-Pathen'u Pathen khopi ahi; Aman tonsot a ahoi doh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 9 O Pathen Pathen, na Hou-In theng sunga nangma kavahchoi lai un nami ngailutna longlou chu kagel jing ui.
\p 
\v 10 O Pathen Pathen namin ja dia kilom tah ahibanginleiset kolmong geija vahchoiya naum ding ahi. Najet lam ban thahat chu galjona a dimset ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Zion mol'a mipi ho kipah uhen. Judah khopiho nathutan dihjeh hin kipah uhen.
\p 
\v 12 Vo Pathen Pathen mite cheuvin Zion khopi gakholchen'un akimvel'a kijot uvin ainsangho jong gasim'un.
\p 
\v 13 Akhopi jouse jong gachon uvin lang akulpi bang nasa tah ho jong melchih'un, chule nang hon nason nachilhah teu naseipeh thei diu ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Ajeh chu Ama hi hitobang mong Pathen ahi. Ama hi tonsot tonsot geija dinga I-Pathen'u Pathen ahin Aman ithi tokah uva eipui hoi diu ahi.
\c 49
\s1 Leiset Haona Lhou Ngailou
\s1 Lalmakai pa henga Korah chapa te labol
\p 
\v 1 Nangho mipite'n hiche hi ngaijuvin! Nangho vannoi mite jouse'n ngaicheh uvin!
\p 
\v 2 Milen le mineo, ahao avai in ngaisohkeijun!
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu ka thusei ho hi chihna thu ahin, chuleh kalung'a kagel jong hi hetgilna dimset ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Keiman thuchih kaseiho chu giltah in kagel'in hiti chun semjang sai a kitilkhou in thulem kaseiho suhlhap na kanei jie.
\p 
\v 5 Kagalmite'n eihin umkimvel'uva boinan eihin lhunkhum teng idia kakichat ding ham?
\p 
\v 6 ama hon anei agouhou atahsan un ahaotheinau a akiletsah ui.
\p 
\v 7 Ahijeng vang'in athina diuva kon'in amaho le amaho akihuhdoh joupouvin Pathen Pathen henga sum in ahinkhou akichoh thei pouve.
\p 
\v 8 Lhatdamna kiti hi bailam tah a um ahipoi, ajeh chu koiman alhingset'in apejou poi;
\p 
\v 9 tonsot a hingjing a lhanmun'a chelouhel nading chu.
\p 
\v 10 Michingho chu nikhat thitei diu ahi, hiche mingol le lungel neilou ho banga anei agouhou chu adalhah cheh di'u ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Lhanmol chu atonsot inn'u ahitan achen jingna di'u mun chu ahitai. Anei agouho'u chu amaho min putsah jong leu.
\p 
\v 12 Aminthan nao chu sotlou ding ganhing ho bang'a thithou thou diu ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Amaho hi min miching dan'in geljong leu mingol bang'a thina ato thou thou di'u ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Kelngoiho bang'a lhanmun lhung thou thou di'u thina chu akelngoi chingpa'u hi ding, anei agouhou a kon'a gamla tah a lhanmun khat a monlha thou thou diu ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Ahin keivang Pathen Pathen'in kahinkho eilhatdoh peh'in tin, Aman lhanmun'a kon'in eihuhdoh nante.
\p 
\v 16 Hijeh chun migilou ho ahung hao uva, a in chen ujong ahung hoibe cheh tengu le lunglhadah hih in.
\p 
\v 17 Ajeh chu amaho athitengu leh imacha akipoh di'u aumpoi anei agou'un lhan sung'ah juilut thei pouvinte.
\p 
\v 18 Hiche lei hinkho'a hin alolhin jeh un vangpha le ochat um'in kigel jong leu,
\p 
\v 19 Chemasa ho bang bang'a thidiu khovah amukit louhel di'u ahitai.
\p 
\v 20 Anei agou'u kiletsahpi ho chun amaho jong ganhing bang'a phat khat leh thithou thou diu ahilam akihetdoh lou'u ahi.
\c 50
\s1 Katdoh Sanga Thungaina Hi Pathen Pathen Lung Lhaina Ahijoi
\s1 Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai loupipen ama chu Pathen Pathen ahin, chuleh Aman thu asei e; Niso namun apat nilhumna munho gei in mihem te akou jing e.
\p 
\v 2 Zion mol'a kon'in Amel-hoina bulhingset'in Pathen Pathen loupina chun ahinsalvah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Pathen Pathen ahunglhung tai Ama thipbeh'in aumpoi, alamlhahna a thiljouse mei in akavam gamtai, chuleh avel'ah huipi nasatah anung'in ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Aman a mite chung'a athutanna ve dingin chunglang'a van ho le leiset akou in ahi.
\p 
\v 5 “Kahenga kilhaina bol'a kitepna kasemkhom pi tahsan umtah kamite chu kaheng a hin pui lut uvin.”
\p 
\v 6 Chuleh vanho jouse'n athudihna phongdoh uhen, ajeh chu Pathen Pathen ama tah thutan'a pang ding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 “Vo kamite ka thusei hi ngai uvin, Vo Israel nangma douna kathilgon aum'e, keima hi na Pathen Pathen chu kahi!
\p 
\v 8 Kilhaina nabolna ho leh pumgo thilto nabol ho chuleh tang lou a nathilpeh jingho chung'a hin keiman lungphatmo na kaneipoi.
\p 
\v 9 Ahin keiman nabong hon lah a kon'a hiche bongchal ahin, nakel hon lah a kon kelcha jongchu kangaicha dehpoi.
\p 
\v 10 Ajeh chu gammang lah a ganhing jouse kei a ahin, chuleh mol le lhang jouse'a bong ho jouse jong kei a ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Keiman mol jouse chung'a vacha jouse kahen, chuleh gamlah a ganhing ho jouse jong keija ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Keima hi gilkel thei anahi jeng tajong leng nangma kom'a kasei angaipoi, ajeh chu vannoi leiset chung'a thil ijakai aumho jouse hi kei a ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Keiman bongchal ho sa kaneh a, kelcha ho thisan kadon khah em?
\p 
\v 14 Nang'in thangvahna hi kilhaina in mang'in, chuleh Hatchungnung kom'a nakitepna chu nit in.
\p 
\v 15 Chule genthei nikho'n keima neihin kouvin, keiman nahuhdoh ingting nang'in neichoi-at ding ahi.”
\p 
\v 16 Ahinlah miphaloute kom'a Pathen Pathen'in hiti hin asei e: “nang'in ka Dan thu kakitepna chu naboi pi khoh ham?
\p 
\v 17 Ajeh chu kahilna na la najuipon kathumop jong lahlou in nakoi e.
\p 
\v 18 Nang'in guchaho namu teng napahcha in chuleh jonthanghoi bol te nakivop pi jie.
\p 
\v 19 Nakam sunga thujou adimset'in, na lei chu thujou jengseh seinan namang'in ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Muntin in natou len nanu a konna napenpi nasopipa jeng jong jouthun naheh se lei.
\p 
\v 21 Nangma hitobang'a nakimanchah sung'in thipbeh in kaum'in ahileh keiman kanahsah lou dan'in nagel'in, tuvanghin nachung'a themmo kahinchan'a hichengse pum'a hi kahingih nahitai, nangma douna kahin lhunsah diho hi kagollha tai.
\p 
\v 22 Ei sumilho jouse kisih un, achuti loule Keiman kabotel ding nahiuve, chule koiman nakithopi loudiu ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Ahinlah kilhaina thilto khel'a thangvahna eipe'a chun eichoisang tahbeh ahi. Kalamlhahna a naum jing leh Pathen Pathen mihuhhingna chu kamusah ding nahi”
\c 51
\s1 David In Achonsetna Aphondoh Chule Ngaidam Channa Dia Atao
\s1 David lengpa Bethseba to ajon jou a Nathan themgaopa ahenga ahunga alabol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen, na mi ngailutna longlou jeh'in na mi khotona chu neimusah in. Na mi hepina kidangtah jeh chun ka chonset nenbeh jouse neisuhbei peh in.
\p 
\v 2 Kathemmona ho jouse'a kon'in neisutheng inlang neisoptheng in, ka chonsetna a kon'in neisuthengsel in.
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu ka phatlouna ka kihet'in sun le jan'in eijui jing'in ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Nangma douna mong'a chonse ka hi, Nangma mitmun thilse chu ka nabol tai. Na thusei in nadihna aphondoh ding ahi, chuleh ka chung'a nathutan jong adih'in ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Ajeh chu ka nu oisung'a ka ki jil'a pat a chonset pum'a kijil ka hin chonsesa hung peng a ka hi.
\p 
\v 6 Hinla nang'in ka nu oisung'a pat'in jong atheng a kaum ding nana ngaichat ahin hiche mun jeng'a jong chu chihna lungthim neina hilpat ahitai.
\p 
\v 7 Ka chonsetna a kon'in neisutheng lechun ka then ding ahitai, neisoptheng lechun buhbang sang'in theng tang'e.
\p 
\v 8 Oh! Ka kipana neipekit in, nang'in nei hesoh sah ahin tun neikipasah kit tan.
\p 
\v 9 Ka chonsetna ho neivet peh jing hih in, ka setna nenbeh ho sumang in.
\p 
\v 10 Lungthimthah neisem peh in O Yahweh Pakai. Kasunga um lhagao hi nei thah sempeh in.
\p 
\v 11 Na angsung'a kon'in neipaidoh hih'in, chuleh keija kon'in na Lhagao Theng chu lamang hih'in.
\p 
\v 12 Nei huhhing nikho'a ka kipana chu avel'in neipe kit inlang chuleh nathu a nung jing mi neihisah in,
\p 
\v 13 Chuteng na thua nunglou ho jong nangma deilam'a ahung chonna di'uva ka hil ding chutengleh amaho nangma kom lang'a hung kile kit ding ahi'uve.
\p 
\v 14 O Pathen Pathen mi huhhingpu, keiman thisan kaso tahjeh in neingaidam'in chutileh neingaidamna chu kipah tah a vahchoila a ka sah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 15 O Yahweh Pakai lungnachim'a nangma ka vahchoi theina dingin ka lei neilhap peh'in.
\p 
\v 16 Nangman kilhaina thilpeh na ngaicha pon, pumgo thilto ding khat jong na ngaicha pon ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Nangin na ngaichat kilhaina chu-Lhagaova kisuh gep ahin, nang'in lung kisuchip pum'a kisihna neiho napaidoh poi o Yahweh Pakai.
\p 
\v 18 Zion hi lungsetna mitvet in venlang hin kithopin, Jerusalem pal hinsem phan.
\p 
\v 19 Chutengleh kilhaina lungtheng sel a kipe pumgo thilto hon lunglhai in natin chule pumgo thil to pum bongchal ho avel'in hung kitodoh tante.
\c 52
\s1 Kiletsah Aphatchomna Umlou
\s1 Edom mi Doeg in Saul jah a “David Ahimelech mite to akimuto e” tia asei jou David labol
\p 
\v 1 Galhang nangman idia na thilse bol ho kiletsahpi nahim? Pathen Pathen thutan dihje hi tonsotna aum jing helou nahim?
\p 
\v 2 Nilhum kei keijin nangman manthahna ding jeng na gong e. Na leigui in jong chem hemtah in mi a-at abangin; jouthu sei in nangma nathem lheh e.
\p 
\v 3 Nang'in thilpha sang'in thilse na deijon, thutah sangin jong jou nadeijoi.
\p 
\v 4 Nathu jou hoa chun nangman mi suhmang ding nadei e!
\p 
\v 5 Hinlah Pathen Pathen'in nangma na hin suhmanghel ding ahi. Aman na in'a kon a nahin kaidoh ding chuleh mihing chenna gam'a kon'a na hin bodoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Mi chonpha hon hichu hin muvin tin ahin datmo di'u ahi. Ama hon hin nuisat intin aseidi'u ahi,
\p 
\v 7 “Veuvin Pathen Pathen tahsanlou galhat ho chung'a hi ipi thilsoh a hitam? Amaho ahao nao a akisong'un, athilse bol nao a akhangtou cheh cheh un ahi.”
\p 
\v 8 Hinlah, keima vang Pathen Pathen Hou-In sung'a keh Olive thing hing hoitah tobang kahin, keiman phat tin'a Pathen Pathen mi ngailutna long lou chu katahsan jing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 9 O Pathen Pathen na thilpha bol jeh hin nangma thangvah jingingting na mitheng te masang'a na min ngaitah chu tahsan jing tang'e.
\c 53
\s1 David In Mihem Chonsetna Thudol Ahilchet
\s1 Lungthim kiphumlut na; David labol
\p 
\v 1 Mingol honbou alungsung uva kon'in “Pathen Pathen aumpoi” ati'uve. Amaho chu mi kitahlou ahi'uvin, thil phalou jeng bol ahi'uvin khatchan jong thilpha abol pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Pathen Pathen'in van'a kon'in mihemte jouse hi ahinven, Aman mikhattou aching tahbeh um am, khat touvin Pathen Pathen ahol am tin ahinven ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Ahinlah khatcha amupon, abonchauvin akihei mangsoh hel ta'uvin, aboncha'uvin akitahlou ngen ahi'uvin, koimacha thilpha bol aumpouvin khatcha jong aumpoi.
\p 
\v 4 Hitobang'a thil phalou bol ho hin ahetdohlouhel di'u ham? Amaho hin kamite hi changlhah bang'a anehchai di'u ahitan Pathen Pathen kom'a tao ding jong agelpha pouve.
\p 
\v 5 Amaho hi, tu masang'a anahetphah louhel u tijatnan ahin lokhum ding ahi'uve. Pathen Pathen'in na galmite'u gu le chang ahin thejal ding, nang'in amaho hi na ahin suhjum ding ahi, ajeh chu Pathen Pathen'in amaho hi apaidoh ahi'uve.
\p 
\v 6 Zion mol'a kon'a Israel te huhdoh dia koi hung ding ham? Pathen Pathen'in amite akiledohsah tengleh, Jacob in kipah a kho asap ding Israel te kipah ding ahi'uve.
\c 54
\s1 David In Pathen Pathen'a Kon Panpina Atahsan
\s1 Ziphat ten Saul jah a “David hoi a kisel ham kei hon kahetaove” tia ahung sei jou uva David in tumging to thoa sah dia alabol.
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen thaneitah in hung'in lang neihuhdoh in! Na thahatnan nei veng'in.
\p 
\v 2 O Pathen Pathen ka taona ngaijin, ka thumna hi neihin gelkhoh peh'in,
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu gamdang mite'n eihin delkhum uvin, mi engse ten tha dingin eihol'un ahi, ama hon Pathen Pathen imachan agel pouve.
\p 
\v 4 Ahinlah kei dingin Pathen Pathen hi eipanpi ahin, Yahweh Pakai hin eihinghoi ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Ka galmi ten thilse agon jouse'u hi amaho chunga le chuh hen! Na dei dan tah in achung uva na tong'in lang amaho khu subei in.
\p 
\v 6 Keiman naheng a kiphal tah in thilpeh hinchoi ing e; Keiman namin hinthang vah ing kate Yahweh Pakai, ajeh chu hichu apha ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai nang'in ka hesohna a kon'in neihuhdoh tan, ka galmite chung'a jong galjona neimusah tan ahi.
\c 55
\s1 David In Akinaipi Golle Pai'a Kon Gimna Ato
\s1 Lalamkai pa henga David in tumging to thoa sah dia asem la
\p 
\v 1 Vo Pathen Pathen ka taona neingaipeh in, panpi ngehna ka taona neigelkhoh peh'in!
\p 
\v 2 Lungset tah in ka taona neingaipeh inlang neihin donbut teijin, ajeh chu kagimnan eihin lonvuh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Ka galmite'n eisamseu vin, eigihna'u hi akithong le'u jengin ahi. Aman boi na eilhunkhum sah un lunghang tah in eihin delkhum taove.
\p 
\v 4 Ka lung aphul lap jengin thina gimneitah hin eihin nokhum tan ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Tijatna le lunggimna'n eilonvuh tan kithing louvin kaum theipoi.
\p 
\v 6 Oh, vakhu bang'a lhaving nei hitave leng o keima lengdoh ingting ga kicholdo tang'e!
\p 
\v 7 Keima gamla tah in lengdoh ingting gamthip noi olnamun gabel tang'e.
\p 
\v 8 Hitobang kivetdatona huipi kinunglah a konhin gangtah in gamla tah a jammang tang'e.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai amaho hi kisuhmosah inlang athilse gon'u jong hi suhmopeh jeng tan, ajeh chu athilgon'u hin khopi sung'a thilse tamtah asodoh sah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Akulpi bang'u jong galmi'a kon'a hoidohna dinga asun ajan a anga'u ahi, ahinla akhohpentah chu khopi sung'a chonsetna ho hi ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Thil jouse hi asegam'a ahitai, kailhang jeng'a jong kigihna le ki joubol na adimlha tan ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Ka dougal'in eitai tomna jong ahipoi hichu ka doujou thouve, kiletsah tah a eijumso jing'a ka kidoupipa jong ahipoi, amaho a kon chun ka ki seldoh theinan ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Amavang hiche ho chu hilouvin, ka kibahpi, ka kivoppi, ka golngai nangma chu na hi.
\p 
\v 14 Phat khatna chu ichan geija ina kingailut hitam Pathen Pathen Hou-In jeng'a jong ina kijotlutji ahie!
\p 
\v 15 Ka dougalte hi thina'n lhunkhum hen, lhankhuh in ahing'in vallhum jeng'u hen, ajeh chu setna'n alungsung'u chen nan aneitan ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Ahinlah keiman Pathen ka Pathen ka kou ding chuleh Yahweh ka Pakaiyin eihuhdoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Jingkah, sun, nilhah in ka lung hesoh jeh'in ka kap'in ahileh Yahweh Pakaiyin ka-o eijahpeh tai.
\p 
\v 18 Mi tamtah in eidou jing hen lang, kei douna'n gal kisat chohjeju jeng jongleh Yahweh Pakaiyin eilhatdoh'in ol-heuvin eiumsah tai.
\p 
\v 19 Tonsot a vaihom jing Pathen Pathen chun ka taona sang'intin ka dougalte asuhnem ding ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon achondan'u akhelnom pouvin Pathen Pathen jong aging pouve;
\p 
\v 20 Keima kiloipipan vang, aloihi alhem lhan akitepna asukeh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Athu cheng chu thaotwi bangin analjet in hinlah asung uvin gal lungthim apu'uve. Athu cheng'u thaotwi nang abangin hinlah asunglang uvah chemjam ngen aum'e.
\p 
\v 22 Na pohgih chu Yahweh Pakai chung'a seplha tan Aman na ngai jangpeh nante. Aman mi chonpha ho chu akipalsah louding lhuh jong alhuhsah louding ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Nangvang O Pathen Pathen mi gilou ho chu lhuh na kokhuh a nasotlhah ding ahi. Tolthat ho le jonpan ho jong khangdong cha na thisah ding ahi, hinla keimanvang eihuhing din nang jeng katahsan e.
\c 56
\s1 David In Agalmite Akichat, Hinlah Pathen Pathen Tahsan'a Tao
\s1 Philistine ten Gath mun a amudoh nung uva lalamkai pa henga David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen, na mi khotonan neipui jing'in, ajeh chu mipite'n eidel jing'uvin eidouhon nilhumkei kei'in eidelkhum jing'un ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Eihousehon jong phattin in eidel jing'un chuleh mi tamtah in eidelkhum jing'un ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Ahinlah ka kichat teng nangma tahsanna a chun ka lut ji tan ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Aman kahenga kitepna anei jeh'in Yahweh Pakai chu ka thangvah e. Pathen Pathen tahsana a ka dindet jing le kei ipi dinga ka kichat ding ham? Hi chi mihem chun i eilo thei ding ham?
\p 
\v 5 ama hon ka thusei jouse ahilou lam in alao vin; kei suhsetna dingin anikho ho'u jong amang jing ui.
\p 
\v 6 Amaho ahung'un eihung velhi'uvin, keima eithatheina diuvin ka chaloh ka sinsah avelhi jing'un ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Achonset pum'un jammang sah hihbeh in; na lungsah na achun O Yahweh Pakai amaho chu sumang jengin.
\p 
\v 8 Nang'in ka thoh gimna neihetpeh jingnan ahi, nang'in ka lengvaina mitlhi hi khon a nakhol khom in, chuleh abonchan na lekhabu'a najihlut e.
\p 
\v 9 Keiman nangma eikithopi dinga ka kou tengleh ka galmite jammang tauvin te. Hijeh a chu keiman Pathen Pathen hi keima lang'a pang ahi ti ka het jingna ahi!
\p 
\v 10 Pathen Pathen'in kakom'a kitepna anei jeh in keiman Pathen Pathen ka thangvah e; henge, Pathen Pathen'in kahenga kitepna anei jeh in Yahweh Pakai ka thangvah ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Keiman Pathen Pathen ka tahsan na ahi ka din jing le ipi dinga ka kichat ding ham? Mihem mai hon i eilo di'u ham?
\p 
\v 12 O Pathen Pathen nang kom'a ka kitepna keiman subulhit ingting chutengleh kilhaina in thangvah na peng ka te.
\p 
\v 13 Ajeh chu nang'in ka thina dinga kon'in neihuhdoh tan kakiselhuh louna din nangin ka keng neituh peh tai. Hijeh chun O Pathen Pathen tun na angsunga hinna vah napeh na mun a chun hung lut thei tange.
\c 57
\s1 Suhgim'a Aumlaiya Huhdohna Dia Pathen Pathen Henga David Atao
\s1 Saul a kon a ajammang a songko a akisel na chunga a David labol
\p 
\v 1 Neilungset in O Pathen Pathen, nei khoton! Neivenbit jingna dingin nang malam ka hin sang'e. Hahsatna ho abeito kahsen na lhaving lim noi a ka kisel jing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Ka chung'a athilgon eisuhbulhing pehna dingin Pathen Pathen hatchungnung chu ka kouve.
\p 
\v 3 Aman eihuhdoh ding chuleh eidel lele ho jumsahna dinga van'a kon'a panpina eihinpeh ding ahi. Pathen ka Pathen'in angailutna longlou leh akitahna a chu eihung vil ding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Keipi bahkai hangtah hon mihem te a anchah dia achanlhih le banin galmite'n eiumkimvel'uvin, aha uhin tengcha leh thalchang bangin asunvangthei in, alei'u jong chemjam hemset tobanginasat tan thei uve.
\p 
\v 5 O Pathen Pathen nangma hi vanmun jouse chungvum sang'in hung kichoisang'in! Na loupina hin leiset chung mun jouse hi salvah hen!
\p 
\v 6 Ka galmite'n thang eikampeh uvin, keima lung gim leh lunglengvai in kaum'e. Ama hon ka lampi'a kotong thuhtah alai un ahinlah amaho ma alhalut jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 7 O Pathen Pathen nang a lungmon na kanei e; nang a kalung among e. Nangma thangvah la ka sahthei hi thil kidang ahipoi.
\p 
\v 8 Thou in kalung! Thou in, o Semjang le tumging! Ka vahchoila'n jingninou hi thoudoh ing e.
\p 
\v 9 O Yahweh Pakai mipi ho jouse lah a na thangvah ing'e. Namtin vaipi jouse lah a nangma na thangvah ing kate.
\p 
\v 10 Ajeh chu na mi ngailutna longlou hi vanho bangin asang e. Na kitahna in meilomlah apha'n ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Hung kichoi sang'in O Pathen Pathen, van mun sangpen ho sang'in na min hi dopsang'in umjo hen. Na loupina in leiset chung pumpi hi salvah hen.
\c 58
\s1 Migiloute Chungthu Tanna Dia David Taona
\s1 Lalamkai pa henga David labol
\p 
\v 1 Vaihom ho nang hon thutah kiti hi ipi kisei na ahi nahet u hinam? Nanghon thu adih a natan'u hinam?
\p 
\v 2 Ahipoi! Nangho'n na lungsung un thudihlou na gong'un gamsung a hunam a natohna ngen na chelheh sah un ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Miphalou ho hi chonsesa peng'a ahiuvin, ahung pen'uva pat'in jou apan'un ama deidan cheh in achon'un ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Ama hon gul bangin gu hat tah alhao vin; gulsoh banginthuhil angainom pouve.
\p 
\v 5 Gul lam sahhon atheile'u ichan geija amut ngeisel vang un akihetmosah un ahi.
\p 
\v 6 O Pathen Pathen a-ha uhi suhbong jengin, O Yahweh Pakai hiche keipi bahkai ho hi a-ha'u suhgoi peh jengin.
\p 
\v 7 Tolgo'a twi isunlhah a agotloiji bangin mangthah loi jeng'u hen. Akhut uva achoi u agal manchah'u chu manmo sosah jengin.
\p 
\v 8 Dahdeng amacham'a ajunlhah ji bangin junlhahsah'in, naosen athisa hung peng nisa mumanlou bah sah in.
\p 
\v 9 Hampa kisatlha banginateh akhang Pathen Pathen'in lhamlha jeng uhen, leibel meikou lah a ling le khao kigouvam sang a gang jo jeng u hen.
\p 
\v 10 Thildih lou ho akilethuh teng mi chonpha ho kipah di'u ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Chuteng achaina le mijousen asei diu ahi, “Pathen Pathen a dia hing ho dihtheina chu kipa thilpeh ahin; leiset a jong thudih a thutan Pathen Pathen aum mong e.”
\c 59
\s1 Galmitea Kon Huhdohna Dinga David Taona
\s1 Saul in David thana dia a inn a asepai ho asol na chunga David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen, ka galmite a kon'in neihuhdoh in, keima eisumang dinga hungho a kon'in neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 2 Mi sugentheiho a kon'in neihuhdoh inlang tolthat ho'a kon'in neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 3 ama hon eichanglhiuvin, Yahweh Pakai melma engsetahte hon eingah un ahi, keiman amaho dounan imacha thilse ka bol poi.
\p 
\v 4 Keiman imacha thilse kabol pon hinla keima eidelkhum dingin akigo jing'un ahi. Hung thoudoh in thilsohho hi hung ven lang neikithopi'n!
\p 
\v 5 O Yahweh Pakai, Pathen Pathen hatchungnung Israel te Pathen Pathen, ei hung thoudoh inlang mi phalou namtin vaipiho hi gimbolna hung petan kitahna neilou mi phaloute chung'a hin khotona neihihbeh in.
\p 
\v 6 Amaho jantengleh ahungdoh jiuvin, uingol hon mi angih bangin lamlen'a akijot'un apeng le jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Akamsung uva thu thanghoi hung potdoh khu ngai in chemjam a kisat bang'a ngaithada umtah ahi. Hitobang'a ngai thaset umtah hi kon angai ngam ding ham?
\p 
\v 8 Ahinla Yahweh Pakai nang'in amaho chu na nuisat'in, mi phalou namtin vaipiho chu na hohdal'in ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Nang hi kahatna nahi; eihuhdoh din nang kangah jing e, ajeh chu nang hi ka ki venbitna kulpi nahi.
\p 
\v 10 Ka Pathen Pathen'in, ami ngailutna longlou achu eidinpi ding ahi. Aman ka melmate jouse chung'a agaljona a eimusah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 11 O Pathen Pathen amaho chu thatgam jeng hih'in ajole ka mite'n kihil na aman u hi sumil loi get'unte; eipanpi o Yahweh Pakai amaho khu thethang'in lang akhuboh uva dilsuh sah jeng tan.
\p 
\v 12 Akam'uva chonset thu ngen aseidoh jeh uleh, alei uva thilse ngen aseidoh jeh un, akiletsahna'u, ahansetna'u chuleh ajouseina'u vin manchah jeng uhen.
\p 
\v 13 Na lunghan nan amaho chu sumang'in lang abonchauvin sumang jengin! chutengleh vannoi leiset pumpin Israel chung'a vaihom Pathen Pathen na hi chu ahetdi'u ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Ka melmate jan leh hungdoh'un tin uichangol hon mi angih bangin akisen le leuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Amaho neh ding an holna'n avahle leuvin oivan'a kham amulou jeh un gilkel pum'in alum jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Hinla keiman vang na thaneina chu vahchoila'n sangnge. Na mi ngailutna longlou chu jingkha she leh kipah tah in vahchoila'n sangnge. Ajeh chu nangma ka kulpi, ka hahsat tengleh ka kiselna na hi.
\p 
\v 17 O ka hatna Yahweh Pakai, nangma thangvahna'n la'n sangnge, O Pathen Pathen nangma ka kiselna na hin, na mi ngailutna longlou chu neimusah jing'e.
\c 60
\s1 Israel Huhdoh a Aumna Dia David Taona
\s1 David in Aram-naharaim le Aram Zobah akisat pi a Jaob ahung kile a chiputna phaicham a Edom mite mi 12,000 atha jou a, Kihil nathei tah dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen nang'in keiho hi neipaidoh tauvin ka kiselna'u jouse jong neisuh chimpeh tauve, nangma keiho chung'a analunghang jongleh chun na lungsetna neimusah tauvin.
\p 
\v 2 Ka gamsung'u na hotling in chuleh na pokehsah ji'n ahi, tun vang akehlai mehbit tan, ajeh chu gamleiset akithing'in ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Keiho hasatnatah nahin pen, jukham a lon lele ho nei sodoh jeng u ve.
\p 
\v 4 Ahinla nang'in nangma ginna neiho dingin ponlap khat neina dopsang peh'un, hichu min eihin nokhum teng'uleh eikipunkhom sah'in anapang'in ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Tun na ngailutna mite hi huhdoh tan, ka taona ngai in lang na ban thahat'in neihuhdoh tauvin.
\p 
\v 6 Aloupi na in Pathen Pathen'in, “keima kichoisangna a hiche kitep nahi ahin sem tai. Shechem hi kipa na a kakehso ding ahi. Sukkoth phaicham hi ka mite ka hoppeh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Gilead hi keija ahin, chuleh Manasseh jong ahi. Ephraim ka thih lukhuh hin galhat miho ahinsep doh ding, chue Juda ka leng tenggol hin leng tamtah hinsepdoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Ahin Moab vang hi ka kisilna kong ahin ka sohna ahin toh ding ahi chuleh Edom a hi ka kengto kathehngim ding chutengleh Philistia chung a ka galjona ka hin sapdoh ding ahi.”
\p 
\v 9 Koi pen'in kul kigetkhum khoipi'a hi eipuilut ding ham? Koi pen in Edom chung'a hi galjona eihin pohlut peh ding ham?
\p 
\v 10 O Pathen Pathen nang'in neipaidoh'u hitam? Nang'in ka sepaite toh galsatna a neihung lhonpi louding hitam?
\p 
\v 11 O lungset tah in ka galmiteuva kon'in neipanpin, ajeh chu mihem panpina hi aphachom aumpoi.
\p 
\v 12 Pathen Pathen panpina jal'a hi thil loupi tah tah tohdoh a um ding ahi, ajeh chu Aman imelmate'u achotpha ding ahi.
\c 61
\s1 Pathen Pathen In Eihong Jinge Tia David Kinepna
\s1 Semjang to thoa sah dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen ka kana neingaipeh in! Ka taona hi ngai in!
\p 
\v 2 Lungsung lunghemnan eilonkhum tenglehiset kol kimvel a kon'in panpi ngaichan ka hin kou e. Hoidoh na songpi sang chung'ah neipuitou in,
\p 
\v 3 ajeh chu nangma hi ka kiselna mun olna pen chu na hi, ka melmate'n ahin phahjoulouna kulpi chu nangma na hi.
\p 
\v 4 Na mun theng'a tonsot'in neichensah in hilai chu na lha limnoi kiselna chu ahi.
\p 
\v 5 O Pathen Pathen ka kitepna chu nei jahpehtai, nangma gingte chan dia na gonpeh na goulona mun chu neipeh ahitai.
\p 
\v 6 Lengpa hinkho hi kum tamtah pehben! Khangkit geiin jong hinghoi in!
\p 
\v 7 Pathen Pathen hoidam na achun vai hom jing hen. Na mi ngailutna longlou le na kitahna chun kaihoi jing hen.
\p 
\v 8 Hiteng chuleh nitina ka kitepna suh bulhit ingkating tonsot'in na min thangvah jing tang e.
\c 62
\s1 Pathen Pathen Bou Kiselna Detpen Ahi
\s1 Jeduthun lalamkaipa henga David labol
\p 
\v 1 Pathen Pathen ang a thipbeh chan ka ngah e, ajeh chu Ama a kon a ka galjona hung kipan ji ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Ama bou hi kasongpi le kakihuhhing na ahin, longlouhel a kaum thei kakingai na kulpi ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Mi khat seh douding melma tamtah ahiuvin-abon'un keima eithat gouve. Amaho ding hin keima hi bang chimsa le tho kigen achimsa tobang ka hi bouve.
\p 
\v 4 ama hon munsang a kon a sotlhah di eigouve. Ka chung chang a jouthu sei athanom un ahi. Ama hon kamasanga eipahchao vin alungsung uvah eigaosap un ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Keiman ka hina jouse pum in Pathen Pathen angsung a thipbehchan ka ngah e, ajeh chu ama a hin ka kinepna aum jing e.
\p 
\v 6 Ama bou hi ka sochatna leh ka kulpi chuleh ka songpi ahin keima sotlinghoi ka hi tahlou ding ahitai.
\p 
\v 7 Ka galjona leh ka minphatna Pathen Pathen a kon jeng bou ahi. Ama hi ka kiselna le ka songpi ahin, ka melma hon eihin maiphah lou diu ahi.
\p 
\v 8 O ka mite phat tinin Ama bou tahsan jingin na lungthim a na pohgih ama chuga sung lhan, ajeh chu Ama hi ikiselna u ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Milham ho hi hainahu khat hui bap a phachom lou ahibou uve, chule mithahat ho jong alim u va amelsou toh akibang deh pouve. Amahokhu lepton lang vele chun hainahu khat sanga jong jangjo ahibou uve.
\p 
\v 10 Nangin na inchen na hinkho hi hunam a lah le guhchat in kivah hih in. Na nei na gou ahung punbe a ahijongleh hiche a chun kisong hih in.
\p 
\v 11 Pathen Pathen'in ol heuvin thu asei in hichu keiman phat tin in ka na jajin ahi. O Pathen Pathen thaneina jouse hi nang a ahi.
\p 
\v 12 O Yahweh Pakai ngailutna longlou hi nang a ahi, tahbeh in nangin mijouse hi atoh dungjui cheh a na lethuh ahi.
\c 63
\s1 David Lhagaova Dangchah, Pathen Pathen In Adang Anousah
\s1 Judah a kon a vahlon lea aum chung David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen nang bou ka Pathen na hi; ken lungil tah in nang kahol e. Kalhagao in nadangchah in; twi veilouna mun gotna gamgo ahin ka tahsa pumpin nang ka hin lhangai e.
\p 
\v 2 Na mun theng'a kon'in ka hin mun na loupina leh na thaneina chu ka hin mun ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Na mi ngailutna longlou chu mihem hinkhoma ma sang a phajo ahi; nang ka hin thangvah chim theipoi.
\p 
\v 4 Hinkho ka nei laisen nangma thangvah ing kating, nahenga taonan ka khut teni hin domsang'ing kate.
\p 
\v 5 An twipen ka neh sang'in nang'in neihin lunglhaisah jon. Kipah tah in nangma thangvahnan la sangnge.
\p 
\v 6 Kalupna mun a limgeh chan nang kagel gel jin, janteng jongleh nangma lungel ho kangaito ji e.
\p 
\v 7 Nangma eikithopi nahijeh in, na lhaving lim noi ah kipah tah in vahchoila ka san ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Na ban thahat tah jet lang in det tah in neituh in ahileh keiman nang ka tuhchah in ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Keima eisumang goho chu hung mangthah diu ahi. Amaho chu leikotong athuhlai pena chu lhalut ding ahiuve.
\p 
\v 10 Amaho chu chemjam a thidiu sial ho anchah a pang diu ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Ahinla lengpa chu Pathen Pathen a kipah ding ahi. Koi hileh Ama tahsan chan chun athangvah ding, mijouho vang suhthip a umdiu ahi.
\c 64
\s1 Hetthei Louva Kiselguh Melmatea Kon Hoidohna Dinga David Taona
\s1 Lalamkaipa heng a David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen, ka kiphinna hi neingaipeh tei in. Ka melmaten eigihnauva kon hin neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 2 Hiche engset lungput a tohgon nei mipi ho a kon'in neiselmang in, hiche thilse bol hon hoa kon'in.
\p 
\v 3 ama hon chemjam kinolhem bangin alei'u anolhem'un thalchang kikap doh bangin thucheng ngaimo tah tah in mi adoi leleu ve.
\p 
\v 4 Themmona neilou miho chu akiselnauva kon'in ahin kap un kichatna neilouvin gangtah in anokhum jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Thilse bol dingin amaho le amaho akitilkhou un chujongleh aguh a iti thang kam ding ham, tichu agong'un ahi. “Hiche hi kon amudoh ding ham?” atiuve.
\p 
\v 6 Athilse gonpat'u chun hitin aseijun, “Hiche hi thilgon hoipen ahitai!” atiuve. Henge mihem lunggel le lungthim vang hi aphalou mong ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Ahinla Pathen Pathen ama tah in athalchang ahin kap ding gangtah a akaplhuh diu ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Amaho tah kampao in ahin thagam diu ahi, koi hileh amaho muchan chun alunghan khum uva alu ahihdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Chujou teng mijouse kicha diu, Pathen Pathen thil boltheina kidangtah chu aphondoh diu, chuleh athilbol datmo umtahho chu ahin hetchen diu ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Mi chonphaho Yahweh Pakai a kipah thanom diu chuleh Ama chu kiselna ahin neidiu ahi. Koi hileh thilpha bol ho jousen Pathen Pathen ahin vahchoidiu ahi.
\c 65
\s1 Pathen Pathen Hongphalna Jeh a David In Avahchoi
\s1 Lalamkai henga dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen, vahchoina thupitah chu Zion'a um nang'a dinga ahi. Keihon nang kom'a ka kitepnau chu ka molso diu ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Ajeh chu nang'in ka taona'u na sang'in, ka bonchauva nang kom'a ka hung di'u ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Ka chonsetnauvin eilonvuh jong le'u nang'in abonchan na ngaidam sohkei tan ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai, na muntheng a um nangkom naiding go ho iti akipa tadiuvem. Na Hou-Intheng sung a chu itobang kipana golnop in eingau hitam!
\p 
\v 5 Kataona hou natoh hoitah in neidonbut peh uve, O Pathen Pathen eihuhingpau. Nangma hi leiset mite jouse kinepna nahin, gamla tah twikhanglen chung'a kongtolho geiyin nang chung a kinepna anei u ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Thahatna thupitah a na kivon a, na thahatna a mol le lhang jong hi na sem ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Twikhanglen kinong le kitum jong hi nasuthip in chuleh namtin vaipi kithong lellul jong na suthip tan ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Leiset chung kolmong gei a chenghon jong na kidanna hi adatmovin ahi. Nisa sona langa pat nilhum na mun geiya umho jong kipah a asaple diuva na tildoh ahitai.
\p 
\v 9 Leiset hi na gelkhoh in gon nachapnou in, leithao leh leipha na sodoh sah in ahi. Pathen Pathen vadung a chun twi nengchet in aum in; hichun louga chang le mim aput sah e, ajeh chu hiti dinga nangman natep sah ahitai.
\p 
\v 10 Lou kikhoiho gotwi in na chap kot jin, leilhangho na su nangin, changkongho jong na kibah sah in, gotwi in leiset na noudoh sah in hiti chun chang le mim nengchet a aumnadin phatthei na boh in ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Kumlhung keiya neh le chah ding nengchet in na gongtoh in leitah lah jeng jong leiphatah na so sah tai.
\p 
\v 12 Gam golai gammang jeng jong hamhing dongset lah a sohdoh in, molpang jeng jong kipah tah in apahlha jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Hamhing lah a kelngoihon adimset un chule phaichamho jong chang le mim adimlha jeng tai. Hi hojousen thong jejun asam un kipa la asaove.
\c 66
\s1 Pathen Pathen Natoh Thilbol Kidang Ho
\p 
\v 1 Leiset mite jousen Pathen Pathen vahchoi cheh uhen!
\p 
\v 2 Amin loupi chu vahchoilan saohen! Aloupina ji vannoi a sei leu vin.
\p 
\v 3 Pathen Pathen henga sei in, “Na thilbol ho hi iti hoia lamdang hitam! Na melmate jeng jong na thaneina thupitah masang a akun jeng uve.
\p 
\v 4 Leiset chung thil jouse jong na angsung a dilsu cheh untin, nathangvahna la asahdiu, naming hi thongjenju a asahdiu ahi.”
\p 
\v 5 Hung in lang ven Pathen Pathen'in ipi atohdoh hitam, mipite dia itobang thil kidang atohdoh hitam!
\p 
\v 6 Aman twipisan a jong lamgolai asemin, chule amite chu akeng'uva ache galkai ui. Hea chun eiho Ama ah ikipah un ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Ajeh chu Aman athahatna thupitah a chun tonsot in vai ahom e. Aman namtin vaipi chaloh sinsah aboncha ave lhisohkei in; koimacha Ama dounan hung kon da jeng hen.
\p 
\v 8 Vannoi leiset mihemte jousen I-Pathen'u Pathen thangvah cheh u henlang avahchoina la choh jejun sauhen.
\p 
\v 9 I hinkhou hi Ama khut a um ahin, Aman ikipallouna diuva ikeng u eituhpeh u ahi.
\p 
\v 10 O Pathen Pathen neipatep tauve; dangka banginneisuhtheng tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Na thangkol a neimat u ahitan chuleh ka tungtun uva sohchanna pohgih chu neipoh sah u ahitai.
\p 
\v 12 Ka chunguvah midang ho lam na jotsah in hiti chun keiho meilhum leh twisohlah neipal galkaisah uvin, hinla neh ding nenna mun a neipuilut tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Tun nahenga kakitepna subulhit din pumgo thilto pum in na Hou-In ka hinjon e.
\p 
\v 14 Henge, lunggim le kakhoisat nikho hoa nakom'a kitepna ka na nei chu ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Hijeh a chu keiman kanei ho lah ka kelngoichalho hi namtui pen ding le, ka bongchalho le ka keltahchalho hi pumgo thilto a ka hin todoh ahitai.
\p 
\v 16 Pathen Pathen gin le jana neijouse hungun lang ngai un, Yahweh Pakaiyin ipi eibolpeh am na seipeh ung ka te.
\p 
\v 17 Ajeh chu keiman Ama thangvah pum in panpi thumnan ka tao in ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Keiman ka lunsunga um ka chonset phongdoh lou hile Yahweh Pakaiyin ka taona eingaipeh louding ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Hinla Pathen Pathen'in eingaipeh e! Aman khohsah tah in ka taona eingaipeh in ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Ka taona eigelkhohpehjeh le ami ngailutna longlou kei a kon a eilahdohpeh lou jeh in Pathen Pathen chu thangvah in um hen!
\c 67
\s1 Pathen Pathen Choi'an Dia Mihemte Tilkhouna
\p 
\v 1 Pathen Pathen lungsetthem hihen lang phatthei eiboh u hen. Amaivah chun eisalvah u hen.
\p 
\v 2 Leiset pumpi a nadeilam kilang hen, muntin'a mihemten na mihuhhingna thahat chu heuhen!
\p 
\v 3 O Pathen Pathen namtin vaipin na thangvah u hen. Henge, namtin vaipin na thangvah u hen.
\p 
\v 4 Vannoi leiset pumpin nangma thangvah la sauhen, ajeh chu namtin vaipi chung a hi thudih a vai hom nahin vannoi leiset pumpi hi na puihoi hoi le jinge.
\p 
\v 5 Namtin vaipin na thangvah u hen O Pathen Pathen. Henge, namtin vaipin thangvah u hen!
\p 
\v 6 Hiteng chuleh leiset in chang le mim gasosah intin chuleh Pathen Pathen, I-Pathen'un nengchet a phatthei eibohdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Henge, Pathen Pathen'in phatthei eiboh un tin, chule vannoi leiset mihemte jousen Ama chu agindiu ahi.
\c 68
\s1 Bitna Le Thil Jouse Pepa Pathen Pathen, David In Jana Apeh
\s1 Lalamkai pa heng David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen hung kipat inlang namelmate hi thethang jengin, Pathen Pathen doumah bolte jouse akihuhdohna diuvin jam uhen.
\p 
\v 2 Amaho khu meikhu banginmut mang in, meisalah a khoilu ajollhah banginjollhahsah in, Pathen Pathen ansung a kon'in migiloute mangthah jeng uhen.
\p 
\v 3 Hinla miphaho chu kipah u hen. Amaho chu Pathen Pathen angsung'ah kipah u hen. Kipa thanopnan dimset u hen.
\p 
\v 4 Pathen Pathen le amin thang vah la saovin! Meibanglom puile pa thangvahla chohthet in sauvin. Amin chu Yahweh Pakai kiti ahi–a angsung a kipah un.
\p 
\v 5 Pa neilou te dia Pa nahin, meithaiho hoidam jing nahi-hiche hi Pathen Pathen ahin aumna chu muntheng ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Pathen Pathen'in changkhatpu hinkho chu insungmi lhingtah in akoi in; Songkul a tangho chamlhat na apen akipa sah tai. Ahinlah thuanunglou ho chu nisan akahgepna neldigama achensah e.
\p 
\v 7 O Yahweh Pakai na mite Egypt gama kon a na hin puidoh a chun, gamgo lah a na hin puigalkai chun,
\p 
\v 8 Israel Pathen Pathen, Sinai Pathen Pathen nangma masang'ah leiset akithing in vanhon go ahin juhlhahsah in ahi.
\p 
\v 9 O Pathen Pathen nangman leigo chapnousah din go nengchet in neihin peuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Akhon nan hichea chun na mite na chensah in, neh le chah nengchetnin na pen, na mite ngaichat jouse jong na pe tai.
\p 
\v 11 Yahweh Pakaiyin thu chengkhat agahseileh mi tamtah in hiche kipana thu chu apoleuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Melmate lengho le asepaite ajamgam tauvin Israel numeiten athilkeo u achomgam peh taove.
\p 
\v 13 Kelngoi hong a chengho jengin jong nei le gou tamtah-alhaving teni dangka le amul sana a kisem vapal akimu uvin.
\p 
\v 14 Hatchungnung chun Zalmon molchung'a buhbang kithejal bangin melma lengho chu athejal gamtan ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Bashan a molho hi athupi thei lheh jeng uve, mol monghem tamtah in vanthamjol a kilhungdoh jenge.
\p 
\v 16 O molsang gumtahho ibolba thangthip tah a navet uham, Zion molsang Pathen Pathen'in alhen na mun, tonsot a achen nading chu?
\p 
\v 17 Sakol-kangtalai simjoulou hon akolkhum Sinai mol a kon a hung'a amuntheng a lut ding ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Nangma achung sang a na kaltou tengleh galhing a kiman tamtah na puitou ding, mipi ho'a kon'a kipaman tamtah na san ding, nangma na douho a kon'a jong na san ding ahi. Hiche'a chu Yahweh Pakai eiho lah a cheng ding ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah in umhen; eihuh hingpau Pathen Pathen chu thangvah in umhen! Niseh a aman abanjang a eikai u ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Eiho Pathen hi mihuhhing Pathen Pathen ahi. Yahweh Pakai lengchungnung hin thina a kon a eihuhdoh u ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Pathen Pathen'in amelmate luchangho asuhchip ding ahi, thilse jeng bolna a kipeho chu alugu u asuhchip ding ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Yahweh Pakaiyin asei e, “Bashan a kon'a ka melmate ka hinpui lhah ding ahi; twikhanglen lailung a kon'a ka hin puidoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Ka mite, nang hon athisan uva chu na keng u na kisoptheng diu, chuleh na uichahou jengin jong chan aneidiu ahi.”
\p 
\v 24 O Pathen Pathen gal nahin jaova na hung kijot u chu muthei in ahung kilangdoh tai, Pathen ka Pathen le ka lengpa muntheng a na kijotlut u chu.
\p 
\v 25 La saho amasang a aum un, tumging saiho a nung a aum ui; alai lunga chun nungah hon vohging theiho avouve.
\p 
\v 26 Israel mipite Pathen Pathen thangvah un; Israel hinkho hungkondohnaho Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah un.
\p 
\v 27 Ven phung neocha Benjamin'in ahin lamkai e. aban'ah Judah a kon a vaihomho, chule Zebulun le Naphtali a kon'in vaihom tamtah ahung uve.
\p 
\v 28 O Pathen Pathen, na ban thahat chu jedoh in. Achesa nikho ho bang chun na ban thahat chu nahat na hung kilangdoh hen.
\p 
\v 29 Jerusalem a na Hou-Intheng ah leiset lenghon na hunglutna u thilho ahinchoijuve.
\p 
\v 30 Na melma namtin vaipiho, pang lah a kisel gamsaho, ahatmo bongnouho lah a bongchalho hi phohsal in. Kisunem tah a ahunglutnau thil in sumlhonho hinchoisah in. Galbol'a thanom namtin vaipiho thethang in.
\p 
\v 31 Egypt a kon'in kipa thilpeh dingin thil mantamho hinchoi u hen, Ethiopia mite Pathen Pathen a akipehlutna uvin bohkhup uhen!
\p 
\v 32 Leiset gam lengho'n Yahweh Pakai, Pathen Pathen kom'ah vahchoila sauhen.
\p 
\v 33 Vanlaijol'a kon'a ogin hat tah hung kithongdoh a, masanglai vanho lah a ki tollepa vahchoila'n la sauvin.
\p 
\v 34 Pathen Pathen thuneina hi mijouse hetsah un, aloupina chun Israel te ahinsalvah in athahatna hi vanho chung'ah akilang jing'e.
\p 
\v 35 Pathen Pathen hi amuntheng'ah gimneitah in aum jing'e. Israel Pathen Pathen'in amite chu thuneina le thahatna ape'n ahi. Pathen Pathen chu thangvah in umhen!
\c 69
\s1 Gammitea Kon Kihuhdoh Ding David In Angaichat
\s1 Lalamkai pa henga dia David labol
\p 
\v 1 Eihuhdoh in, O Pathen Pathen, twisoh hin ka ngong gei achuptai.
\p 
\v 2 Bonlhoh lah a hin ka lhalut cheh cheh tai; pansatna ding ka mujou tapoi. Keima twithuh lah a ka lhalut tan twisoh hin eichup tai.
\p 
\v 3 Panpi ngai a kaka na katha achollha tai; ka lolhomsung jong agolha tai. Ka ka kanan ka mit jong apomtan, Pathen Pathen'in eipan pi ding kangah e.
\p 
\v 4 Ajehbei hel a eivetdaho hi ka lujang a ka samjang sang'in atamjouve. Ka melmate hin jou thu jeng a suhmang ding eigouvin, hiti hin ka guh louhel thil chu kanung peh din athum uve.
\p 
\v 5 O Pathen Pathen ichan gei a ngol kahi nahenai; Ka chonsetna ho hi nang'a kon'in akiselmang theipoi.
\p 
\v 6 Keijeh in, nangma tahsan ho chu jumsah hihbeh in, O van a lengchungnung Yahweh Pakai, kei jeh in nangma houmi tehi kisuh jum na nei hisah hihbeh in, O Israel Pathen Pathen.
\p 
\v 7 Ajeh chu nangma jal a housetna ka thoh ahi; jumna le jachatna kamai a adimset tai.
\p 
\v 8 Ka sopiho tah jengin jong eikihetmosah tauvin gamchommi bangin eibol tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Na Hou-In a ding a ka tompan jeh in eichaideh tan ahi, nangman na housetnau jouse chu ka chunga achu tan ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Kappum a an kangol a chun, noisetah in eihou un ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Ka genthei phondohna a khaodippon ka kisil'a ahileh einuisat un ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Keima hi khopi sung a jalhang a kihoulim nopna bep ka hitan jukhamhon kei chung chang thu totnopnan anei tauve.
\p 
\v 13 Hinla Yahweh Pakai naheng a katao jingin, tuchung beh neihin khoto ding kakinem e. O Yahweh Pakai na mingailut longlou chun katao nahi huhing na tahbeh a chun nei donbut in.
\p 
\v 14 Bonlhoh lah a kon hin neihuhdoh in; athuh jep a neilhahlutsah hihbeh in, eivetdaho lah a kon'in neihuhdoh inlang hiche twithuh lah a kon hin neikaidoh in.
\p 
\v 15 Twisohhat lai neichupsah hih in, ahilouleh twithuh gillai jong nei vallhum sah hih in, ahilouleh thina lhan kotong jong nei nehmang sah hih in.
\p 
\v 16 O Yahweh Pakai ka taona neingaipeh in, ajeh chu na mi ngailutna longlou hi kidangtah ahin, neikaihoi jingin, ajeh chu na mikhotona hi lolhing tah ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Na sohpa a kon hin kisel mang hih in; gangtah in neidonbut in ajeh chu keiman boina nasatah ka toh tai.
\p 
\v 18 Hung'in lang neihung lhatdoh tan; ka melmat a kon'in neilha-ong tan.
\p 
\v 19 Nang'in eiki houset na eikijum bolna le ei kijachat sah naho jouse na hesohkei in ahi. Ka melmaten abol jouseu na hesohkei e.
\p 
\v 20 Ami taitomnauvin ka lungthim asukeh in, kadailheh jeng tai. Mikhat seh hijongleh lungset na eimusah um hen lang; Khattou hung kiheihen lang eihin lungmonsah le kanom e.
\p 
\v 21 Ahinla chutimalah in ama hon ka nehdin gu eipeuvin ama hon ka don dingin juthuh eipeuve.
\p 
\v 22 Amasang uva neh-le-chah dimset dokhang chu akipal nao soh henlang, ahaonau chu amaho dingin thangkol hisah jeng tan.
\p 
\v 23 Kho amutheilouna diuvin amit u chojeng henlang atahsao kithing thing in umsah jengin.
\p 
\v 24 Na lunghanna chu achung uvah sunglha jengin; na lunghanna meikong achun amaho chu kavam jengin.
\p 
\v 25 A-in'u chu ahomkeo soh doh jeng henlang aponbuh u jong kihoh doh jeng hen.
\p 
\v 26 Gotna napeh mi chun, akisuhkhah na chung uva jumbol na akoibe uve; akisukha ho chu natna abelap peh uve.
\p 
\v 27 Achonsetnau setvum peh unlang, khatcha ongthol'in lha hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 28 Amin u chu hinna lekhabu a kon'in thaimangpeh in; michonpha ho lah a kisimtha sah hihbeh un.
\p 
\v 29 Keima natna thohgim in kaum e, O Pathen Pathen, na mihuhhingna thahat chun neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 30 Hiteng chuleh keiman na min pachatna la'n sangting chule thangvahna pum'a jana ka peh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 31 Ajeh chu hichun kilhaina bongchal ki todoh sang'a Yahweh Pakai chu alunglhaisah ding ahin, bongchal thaotah le akeng tin hoitah thilpeh kipe sang'in jong aphajoi.
\p 
\v 32 Mi kineosah tena Pathen Pathen'u natoh muo vintin kipahdiu ahi. Apanpi dia Pathen Pathen holte jousen kitilkhouna neicheh uhen.
\p 
\v 33 Ajeh chu Paka in ngaichageova umte taona angai in; Aman sohchang'a umho donlouvin akoi jipoi.
\p 
\v 34 O van-le-lei in Pathen Pathen vahchoi u henlang twikhanglen le asung a cheng jousen jong vahchoi u hen.
\p 
\v 35 Ajeh chu Pathen Pathen'in Jerusalem ahuhdoh ding Judah khopiho asemphat ding ahi. Hiche'a chun amite cheng untin gamsung chu alodiu ahi.
\p 
\v 36 Ama thu nitjing chaten gamsung chu louvin tin, chule ama ngailuho jouse hiche mun a chu lungmong a cheng diu ahi.
\c 70
\s1 Huhhingna Dia David Atao
\s1 Pathen Pathen'in agel doh jing nadia David labol
\p 
\v 1 Pathen Pathen lungsettah in neihuhdoh in! Yahweh Pakai, gangtah in hungin lang neihung kithopin.
\p 
\v 2 Tha dia eiholten jumna toh uhenlang jachatsah in. Ka gentheipet a kipahho jachat thohpum in kinunglesah tan.
\p 
\v 3 Amaho chu tijat le jachat thohsah in, ajeh chu ama hon “aphai tun ama ikhut uvah aumtai” atiuve.
\p 
\v 4 Hinlah koi hileh nangma holte jousen nang a kipa-le-thanopna dimset muo hen. Koi hileh na mihuhhingna ngaichaho jouse chun “Pathen Pathen hi aloupi e!” tin samging'u hen.
\p 
\v 5 Hinla keidin vang vaicha le lhasam ka hi; O Pathen Pathen lungset tah in eipanpi din hung loi in. Nanghi eipanpi le eihuhhingpa na hi; O Yahweh Pakai geisang hih in.
\c 71
\s1 Tehsepu Taona
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai eihuhdoh ding ngaichan na kom kahinbel e.
\p 
\v 2 Neihuhhing in lang neihuhdoh in, ajeh chu nangma adih na hi, na kol hinsung'in lang ka sei neingaipeh in, chule neichamlhatsah in.
\p 
\v 3 Ka kisel jing theina din kahoidam na songpi hijingin. Keima huhhing ka chan theina dingin thu peh chu pen, nangma ka songpi le ka kiselna na hi.
\p 
\v 4 Ka Pathen Pathen, miphalouho thaneina a kon'in neihuhdoh in, eibolse a mi engbolseho'a kon'in neihuhdoh in.
\p 
\v 5 O Yahweh Pakai nangbou ka kinepna na hi, O Yahweh Pakai nangma hi ka chapan laiya pat a ka hin tahsan na hi tai.
\p 
\v 6 Henge, ka pen'a pat nang'in neina umpi jingin, ka nu naobu sung'a ka kijil'a pat a neina chintuppat ahitai, hijeh a nangma ka thangvah jing hi datmo ding ahipoi.
\p 
\v 7 Ka hinkho hi mi tamtah din kihilna thei ahi, ajeh chu nangma hi ka thahatna le ka kiselna na hi.
\p 
\v 8 Hijeh a chu nangma ka thangvah chim theilou na hi; Nilhum kei kei a hi na loupina ka phondoh jing ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Tua, ka tehphat hin neipaidpoh hih in. Ka tha'n ajolou teng neinungsun hih in.
\p 
\v 10 Ka melmate hi keima douna di'n akihoutoh tauve. Amaho hin thadoh ding eigo tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 ama hon, “Pathen Pathen'in anungsun tai che'u hitin gaman'u hite ajeh chu tua hi koiman apanpi louding ahi” atiuve.
\p 
\v 12 O Pathen Pathen, munchom a potdoh hih in, Pathen ka Pathen neihung panpi loi in.
\p 
\v 13 Keima eihehseho hi sunem'in lang sumang jengin, keima eibolsenomho hi sujum'in lang jachatsah in.
\p 
\v 14 Keima vang neikithopi dinga kinem jing ding ka hi; Keiman nangma ka thangvahbe jing ding na hi.
\p 
\v 15 Keiman nangma chonphatnaho hi mijouse ka seipeh ding ahi. Keima thusei them hi hih jong leng na mihuhhingna thahatna hi nilhumkei kei a ka phondoh jing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 16 O Yahweh Pakai thaneichungnung, keiman na thilbol nasatah tahho jeh a ka thangvah ding na hi. Thudih choija nangma bou na hi hi keiman mijouse ka seipeh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 17 O Pathen Pathen nang'in ka chapanlai a pat a neinahil ahitai. Ken jong na thilbol kidang ho hi midang ho ka seipeh jing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Tunvang keima ka tehtan ka sam akang tai neinungsun hih in. Tu khangthahte lah a hin na thaneina hi samphong lengnge. Kei nung'a hung ding miho lah a jong na thilbol datmo umtahho jong phongdoh ing kate.
\p 
\v 19 O Pathen Pathen na chonphatna hi van sangpenho lah jong aphapeh e. O Pathen Pathen na thilbol kidangtahho hi koitoh na kitekahpi thei ding ham?
\p 
\v 20 Hahsatna nasatah tah neithohsah in ahinlah nang'in ka hinkho na kiledohsah ding ahi'n chule lhan lah a kon'in jong neikaidoh in.
\p 
\v 21 Nang'in lolhinna sangjo cheh a jong neikiledohsah ding avel'a neihin lhamon ding ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Hiteng chuleh keiman semjangsaito tho'a nangma ka thangvah ding ahi, ajeh chu O Pathen Pathen nangma na kitepna a na thon ngaipoi.
\p 
\v 23 Keiman nangma thangvahna la hi kipah tah a thongleuva ka sah ding ahi, ajeh chu nangin neihunglhatdoh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 24 Keiman nangma thilpha bol ho hi sun nilhum a ka seiphongle ding ahi, ajeh chu keima eibolsego chun jachatna le jumna atoh tauvin ahi.
\c 72
\s1 Israel te Leng Dinga Taona
\s1 Solomon labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen nang'in na ngaisang thutan dihna chu lengpa hinpe jing'in, chule na chonphatna chu lengpa chapa hinpe tan.
\p 
\v 2 Na mite chung'a thu adih in tansah in; genthei lengvaite jong aphalam achan dingdol chang jing u hen.
\p 
\v 3 Molsang dung hon jong mijouse dingin haodohna sodohsah hen chule thinglhang in jong gapha sodohsah hen.
\p 
\v 4 Genthei lengvaite panhusah inlang alhasamho chate huhdoh hen chule misugentheite chu sumang jeng hen.
\p 
\v 5 Vanlai jol'a nisa le lha avahjing laise'n tonsot in ama hon nangma naging jing'u hen.
\p 
\v 6 Lengpa chu amite lah a go'n leiset chung achapnou bangin hamdongho tobang amite chapnou hen.
\p 
\v 7 Ahinkho lhumkeijin chonphatna hinkho chepi jing hen. Chule lha'n vah aneilaisen khangtou jing hen.
\p 
\v 8 Alenggam in twikhanglen khat a kon'in twikhanglen langkhat hoppha hen lang chule Euphrate vadung'a kon'in leiset mong langkhat gei hop hen.
\p 
\v 9 Neldigam a ganchaching mite'n chibai aboh diu ahi; amelmate jong amasang a um nen le boh lah a chun lhu cheh unte.
\p 
\v 10 Tarshish le gamla tah a cheng lhumlam lengte'n kai hin peuhen. Sheba le Seba a kon solam lengte'n kipa thilpeh hinchoiju hen.
\p 
\v 11 Leng jouse a ang'a kun'untin namtin vaipi alhacha hung pang di'u ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Aman genthei lengvaite chu akom'a atao teng'uleh hin huhdoh intin, min abol genthei panpibeiho chu ahinpanhu ding ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Aman milhasamte neiloute akhoto'a ahin huhdoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Pumhat a kibol thohgimna noija umho chu alhatdoh ding ahi, ajeh chu Aman amaho chu alainatpi ding ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Lengpa chu hingsot hen! Sheba sana chu ama kipe hen, amite'n taopeh jing'u hen chule nilhumkei in phatthei boh uhen.
\p 
\v 16 Agamsung'uva chang-le-mim nengchet hen, thinglhangvum geiyin chang-le-mim kehdoh hen. Thei gana thingphungho jong Lebanon thingphungho bangin keh dimset'u hen. Chule mipite jong hamphung phat bangin hinhoi u hen.
\p 
\v 17 Tonsot in lengpa minthang hen, nisa asat laisen chejom jing hen. Namtin vaipi amajeh in phatthei chang'u hen.
\p 
\v 18 Yahweh Pakai, Israel Pathen Pathen chu thangvah in um hen, Ama bouvin thil kidang aboldoh thei ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Amin loupi chu tonsot in thangvah in umhen! Vannoi leiset hi Ama loupina dimset hen, Amen, Amen!
\p 
\v 20 (Hiche hi Jesse chapa David taona achaina ahi).
\c 73
\s1 BU THUMNA
\s1 Thenna Chun Malam'a Kipaman Ahin Lhut Ding Ahi
\s1 Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu Isreal te din aphai, hitobanga lungthimtheng ho dinga chun.
\p 
\v 2 Keima din vang, kalamjotna beikoncha bou ahitai. Kalamlhong anal in lhulham pai ding kahitai.
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu keiman mikiletsahho gitlou bol pum hijongleu akhangtou u kamuteng ka otchalheh jin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Amaho hi atahsa'u aphatheiyin, adamthei un, ahattheiyun lungkhamna imacha neilou dan'in aum jiuve.
\p 
\v 5 Amaho hin midang bangin boina imacha aneipouvin midang ho'n aneiyu lunggimna ama hon imacha anei pouve.
\p 
\v 6 ama hon kiletsahna songmantam a kisem khivui bangin aki ouvin, gitlouna chu pon bangin akisil'un ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Hiche miboltheiho hin alungsung uva angaichat chan'u anei un ahi.
\p 
\v 8 ama hon mi jahda dingngen aseijun kiletsah tah in midang chu suhmang ding ago uvin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 ama hon van douna'n thu asei uvin a-o cheng'un leiset pumpi asamsesoh jeng'un ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Hiti chun mipi ho'n athusei u hi ajah uleh akicha uvin akisulungdong gam tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Pathen Pathen'in ipi ahet am? “Hatchungnung in thilsohho hi ahena dem?” atiuve.
\p 
\v 12 Hiche migilouho hi veuvin hinkhonom amang un ahao tultul jeng'un ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Imacha phachomlou dinga lungthim theng ka put ham? Themmona beihel'a hinkho ka man hi mohseh ham?
\p 
\v 14 Nilhumkei in imacha phatchomna ka mupon hahsatna ngen ka mu jo'n ahi, jingkah seh in lunggimna ngen in eilonvuh in ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Keiman hitia hi ka seikhah a ahileh na mi ka hilou hijenginte.
\p 
\v 16 Hijeh chun keiman miphalouho hi i-atileh khangtou cheh cheh u ham ti hetchet dingin ka khol'in ahi. Ahinla iti hahsat hitam?
\p 
\v 17 Hichun O Pathen Pathen, nangma muntheng'a ka lut'in ahileh ajona in migiloute akhankho diu chu kahin hedoh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Tahbeh in nang'in amaho hi lhuh nathei munjeng a nakoi ahin alhuh gam nadiu a kiling gih geh songpi chung a nakoi joh ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Chomkah lou in amaho amahthahgam tauvin ahi, tijatna'n alhohmang gam tauve.
\p 
\v 20 O Yahweh Pakai nangma na hung kipatdoh tengleh nang'in amaho ngolna chu na nuisat ding ahi, mikhat in jingkah lang'a amang anuisat tobang bou ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Hijouchun ka lungsung analheh jengin, hiti chun ka sunggil lang achiplha jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Keima vang mingol le thilhethemlou kana hi-Nang a ding chun khohephalou gamsa tobang bep ka na hi bouve.
\p 
\v 23 Henge keima nang'a ka hi jing'e, nangman ka jetlang na tuh jingnai.
\p 
\v 24 Na chihna'n eikaihoi jingin, munloupi tah chu neilhut ding ahi.
\p 
\v 25 Van'a nang tailou koidangba ka nei ding ham? Leiset chung'a thil dang jouse sang'in jong kalung in na ngaicha joi.
\p 
\v 26 Ka tahsa bei henlang ka lhagao lhadai jongleh, Pathen Pathen chu ka lungthim'a ka hatna ahijing'in Ama hi tonsot a kei a ahijing'e.
\p 
\v 27 Ama dalhaho jouse chu mahthah ding ahiuve, ajeh chu nangma dalhaho jouse chu nangman na sumang jin ahi.
\p 
\v 28 Ahinla keima dingin Pathen Pathen kom nai hi iti phat a hitam! Keiman vang Yahweh Pakai Lengchungnung chu ka kiselna ahijing e, chule keiman na thilbol kidang ho hi mijouse ka seipeh ding ahi.
\c 74
\s1 Pathen Pathen Mite Douho Manthahna Dinga Taona
\s1 Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen, idia hitihchan pi neipaidoh u hitam? Ipi dinga na kelngoite douna a hichan geihi na lunghan ham?
\p 
\v 2 Khang masalai peh a nalhentum chate kahiu neisumil hihbeh un, hiche nam nagoulu tum dia na ngeh jing chu kahiuve! chule hiche lei a na inn Jerusalem jong sumil hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 3 Hiche khopi kisumangsa a hin hungvahlen lang, na melmate'n na Hou-In hi ichanggei a asuhset'u hitam hinven.
\p 
\v 4 Hiche mun a hi na melmate'n haan la anasap u hitam, hiche mun a hi aponlap u ana khaisang'u ahi.
\p 
\v 5 ama hon gammang lah a thingtuhna a heicha analap u bangin,
\p 
\v 6 Heicha le chempong toh tho'n anakhenchip'un ahi.
\p 
\v 7 ama hon namuntheng a na mintheng kitahdohho chu asuboh un,
\p 
\v 8 Chuban in jong “abonchan suseu hite” akitikit uvin, Pathen Pathen houna mun jouse jong anahallhah u ahitai.
\p 
\v 9 Keihon melchihna thil kidangtahho chu ka mudohjou tapouvin ahi. Themgaoho jouse la aumgam tapouvin, chule hiche hi itihleh kichai ding ti chu koimacha ahe aumpon ahi.
\p 
\v 10 O Pathen Pathen ka melmate'u hi itihchanggei na kihousetsah ding ham? Namin theng hi tonsot a nasuh molphou sah ding hitam?
\p 
\v 11 Ipi dia na banjet thahatna hi na chalohsah lou ham? Na khut thahat tah chu mangcha'n lang amaho khu sugam tan.
\p 
\v 12 O Pathen Pathen nangma hi khangluilai a pat a leiset chung'a huhhingna hinpolut a ka lengpa na hi.
\p 
\v 13 Nangman na ban thahat'in twikhanglen jong na lhehkhen in, twikhanglen a cheng sahemho luchang jong navohchip soh hel e.
\p 
\v 14 Nangman Leviathan luchang jong nasuchip in atahsa neldigam a um ganhingho vahnan na mangtai.
\p 
\v 15 Nangman leiset a kum nakihei sah in leiset a kon'in twi tamtah na putdohsah in chule a-itih a kang khalou vadungho jong na sukang jin ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Sun le jan jong nang'a ahin: nangman vanlai jol'a avahho jouse le nisa jong na sem in ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Nangman leiset gamgiho jouse jong na lhehkhen in chule nipilai le phalbilai jong na gongtoh in ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Ven Yahweh Pakai hiche melmaho hin ichan gei a nangma hi na houset'u hitam, ima hetkhenna neilou nam miten na min hi asuminseuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Hiche gamsa tobang miphalouho hi vapal tobang miphaho hi suhmangsah hihbeh in, na mite gentheina hi itihchan'in jong sumil hihbeh in.
\p 
\v 20 Na kitepna kinep umtahho chu sumil hihbeh in, ajeh chu gamsung hi muthim le pumhat a natohna adimset e!
\p 
\v 21 Noise le chotpha a umte hi jumna tosah kit hihbeh in, amavang mivaicha le tahlelte na min choi-at sah in.
\p 
\v 22 Na melmate'n na housetnaho le na doumah mah asap a saptho jenghou hi nahsahmon koihihbeh in.
\p 
\v 23 Namel ten aseidoh uchu nungvet kit hih in ahilou le amaho phunchel jing na chu.
\c 75
\s1 Pathen Pathen In Mikitah Ho Adopsang
\s1 Lalamkai pa henga Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen nangma kahin thangvah e! Yahweh Pakai nangma nailama naum jeh in kahin thangvah uve. Muntin a um mipiten nathilbol kidangtah ho aphongdoh un ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Pathen Pathen'in asei e, keiman thutanna phat khat kagong e, keiman dihtah a thu katan ding ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Leiset hi kihot linghenlang mihemte tija jonglehu leiset bulpi tuhchah jingding chu kahi.
\p 
\v 4 “Keiman mikiletsah ho kagih-in ‘kiletsah datan!’ Migiloulou ho kom'achun, ‘nakhut tumjel hihin!’
\p 
\v 5 Vanho dounan nakhut tum jel hihin, ahilouleh nahsah loutah in thu seihih in” kati.
\p 
\v 6 Ajeh chu, leiset chunga koimacha solam a kon hihen lhumlam-a kon hijongleh chuleh gamthip noi a kon hijongleh kihisah tah a akhuttum ajel louding aphai.
\p 
\v 7 Ajeh chu thutan vaihom-a hi Pathen Pathen Ama bou ahin, Ama hin koipen ding doh ding ham ahilouleh koipen lhuding ham gonga Ama bou ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin juphon gimnamtuitoh kihal chu akhutna khonkhat in achoiye. Aman hiche ju chu thutanna mun a sunglut in, hichu migilou chengin adon teitei diu adontheng heldiu ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Hinla keima vangin, Pathen Pathen thil bol ho hi ka phondoh jengding; Jacob Pathen Pathen henga vahchoila kasha jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Ajeh chu Pathen Pathen'in asei e “Keiman miphalouho thahatna lai chu kasuhchip ding ahinla michonphaho thahatna kahatsah beding ahi” ati.
\c 76
\s1 Pathen Pathen Bou Gin Ding Ahi
\s1 Lalamkai pa henga tumging to tho dia Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 Judah a Pathen Pathen hi akijabol in, Israel a Amin hi aloupin ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Jerusalem hi achenna ahin; Zion molchu a inn ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Hicheachun agalmite meikong tobang thalchang chu asubong in, a umphou le achemjamhou chuleh agalmachah houjouse jong asuhchip pehin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Nangma hi tonsot a um jing mol ho sang'in jong naloupi in nalamdang deh e.
\p 
\v 5 Eidou u galmi hangpenho jouse jong akisugep gam tauve. A imumil banginkamasang uvah akijamdel tauve. Galmi koiman kamasang uvah akhutnu alamp ngapchat lou diu ahitai.
\p 
\v 6 O Jacob Pathen Pathen nakam sunga nahaina hu chu ahung gindoh chun asakol jouse leh akangtalai jouseu akolchah sah soh jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Nangma hitobang tah-a ginle ja naumhi datmo ding ahipoi. Ajeh chu nalunghan ahung deujah leh koiham na-anga ding ngam dingah?
\p 
\v 8 Van'a kon'in nagalmite chunga thu nahin tan in, leiset hi akithingin na-angsung'ah adingin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 O Yahweh Pakai nangma nadingdoh-in mi engsete thu natan in leiset abol genthei a umte nahuhdohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Mihemte hi nangma doumah a achonteng hichu naloupina kilandohna ahijon ahi, ajeh chu hiche chu nangma manchah-a pangbep ji ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Na Pakai Yahweh, na Pathen Pathen heng a kitepna neiyin lang hichu nit'in, mijousen kichat umtah Pathen Pathen kom'a pehdingdol hinpecheh hen.
\p 
\v 12 Ajeh chu Aman leng chate kiletsahna avochip in, lengten jong Ama ginle jana aneiyun ahi.
\c 77
\s1 Masanga Pathen Pathen Hepina Geldoh In
\s1 Jeduthun, lalamkai pa henga Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 Keiman Yahweh Pakai kakouvin; henge, kasaptho jengin ahi. Oh, Pathen Pathen'in eingaipeh tei inte!
\p 
\v 2 Keiman hahsatna kato teng Yahweh Pakai chu kaholjin ahi. Jankhovah in vanlang sangin kakhut katungin kataojin ahi. Ahinla kalhagao in olna amujoupoi.
\p 
\v 3 Keiman Pathen Pathen kagelin apanpina ngaichatnan eilonvuh-in kamaojin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Nangman jankhovah in nei imutsahpon ahi, ajeh chu keima kalung ahesoh behsehin kataotheipoi!
\p 
\v 5 Keiman phat sottah chetasa hinkholui nopsahna chengchu kageldohjin,
\p 
\v 6 kipana dimsetna vahchoina la ana kisahna janho chu kalhagao lungthim a kakholchil tengleh tuhin masangtoh akibah louna kageldohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai hin a-itih a dia eipaidoh mong hitantem? Ama hin khotona eimulou mong mong ding hitam?
\p 
\v 8 Angailutna longlouchu chemang monga hitam? Akitepna ho chu lolhing lou mong ding hitam?
\p 
\v 9 Pathen Pathen'in eihepina chu asuhmil mong hitam? Eihepina kotchu akha mong hitam?
\p 
\v 10 Hiti hin keiman kaseijin, “hiche hi kachan ding mongchu ahi, chungnungpen'in ei engbol ahi,” kati.
\p 
\v 11 Ahinla O Yahweh Pakai nanatoh ho hi kahin geldohin, tuma sang peh-a nanatoh kidangtah ho chu kageldohin ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Hiche ho chu ka lungsunga amil thei pon ahi. Nanatoh loupitah ho chu gellouvin kaum thei jipon ahi.
\p 
\v 13 O Pathen Pathen nalampi hi atheng e. Nangma tobang patheng dang um mong nantem?
\p 
\v 14 Nanghi datmo kidangtah Pathen Pathen chu nahi ahi! Nangin chidang namdang te lah-a nabol theina gimneitah chu nakilandohsah ahitai.
\p 
\v 15 Naban thahatna a nami Jacob leh Joseph chilhah te chu nahuhdoh ahitai.
\p 
\v 16 O Yahweh Pakai twikhanglensan chun namu phat in twichun nahinven akithingtan ahi! Twikhanglen chu asunglang ho ngeiyin akithingin ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Meilhang in go ahin juhlhahsah in, van gin kithong chun vanthamjol chu agin akithonsah in ahi. Nakolphe thalchang chun ahin salvah in ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Chimpei lah-a kon chun van gin ahung kithongin kolphe chun vannoi leiset ahin salvah in ahi! Leiset chu akithingin akihot-e.
\p 
\v 19 Nalampi chu twikhanglen'ah akilhunglutnin ahi, Nakeng nung twilah ajong akigollut e, ahinlah nakhonung koima chan amudoh joupoi!
\p 
\v 20 Nangin kelngoi chingpa hina in Mose le Aaron mangcha in namite hi kelngoi honbangin napuilen ahi.
\c 78
\s1 Israel te Thusim
\s1 Asap labol
\p 
\v 1 O kamite ho, ka thuhil hi ngaiyun. Kathusei a hin nakol'u hinsungun,
\p 
\v 2 ajeh chu keiman thulem a nahenga thu kaseiding ahi, keiman achesa thilsoh ho-a kon a kahin hilding nahi,
\p 
\v 3 eihon thusim ijahsa houleh ihetsahou, thusim ipu ipateuva kon a hung kiseilhapeh ho ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Eihon hiche thutah ho hi icha inaoteu i-impeh loudiu, Yahweh Pakai natoh loupi tahtah ho hi, athaneina le akidanna ho hi ikhangthah houhi iseipehdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Ajeh chu Aman Jocob kom'a Dan anapeh-a, Israel kom'a thuhil ho anapeh ahi. Aman ipu ipateu atu achateu ahil diuva thupeh anapeh ahin,
\p 
\v 6 hitiachu ahunglhung ding khangthah ten ahet nadiuleh ahung pengloulai chapang ho dinga, chuleh aman amaho chapangte ahilskonna diuva ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Hitiachu khangthah ahunglhun channa Pathen Pathen a kinepna thah aneisah nadiu, Yahweh Pakai natoh kidang thil loupi ho chu asuhmillou nadiu chuleh athupehho anitjing nadiuva ahiljing diu ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Hiteng chuleh ipi iputeu tobang talou a lungtahna, kiphinna, kitah louna Pathen Pathen a alungthim'u pehnom louna anei lou diu ahitai.
\p 
\v 9 Ephraim galsat hon thalchang akipoh vangun akinung hei un galmun a kon'in ajam tauve.
\p 
\v 10 ama hon Pathen Pathen toh akitepnau ajuitapouvin ama thuhil dinpi ding anom tapouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Pathen Pathen'in ipi abolpeh uham thil kidangtah tah anabol ho chu,
\p 
\v 12 napu napa teu dinga thil kidang anatohdoh ho, Egypt gamsungle Zoan phaicham chunga, atohdohho asumil tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Ajeh chu Aman twikhanglen ana homkhen in twichu bang bangin aki khen in amaho anapui galkaiyun ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Sunleh meilhang in anapuijin, janleh meikong in anapuijin ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Aman gamthip gamm a songpia kon'in adondiu twi anaputdoh sah-in ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Aman songpia konna twichu vadung bangin analondohsah in ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Ahijeng vangin neldi gam achun ama hon chonset anabol'un hatchungnung dounan ana kiphin'un ahi.
\p 
\v 18 ama hon alungsung uchu lungtahna neipumin Pathen Pathen ana patep un neh ding anathumun ahi.
\p 
\v 19 ama hon Pathen Pathen Ama tah dounan thu anaseiyun “Pathen Pathen'in gamthip gam'ah an eipejou pouve” atiuve.
\p 
\v 20 “Henge, songchu ajep'un twichu aputdoh nai, ahinla amite changlhah le sa me eipejou pouve” atiuve.
\p 
\v 21 Pathen Pathen'in hiche hi ajahdoh phatnin alunghang lheh jengin, Jacob dounan alunghan na mei akoudoh jengin ahi! Hiti hin Israel douna a lunghanna ahung koudoh jengin ahi,
\p 
\v 22 ajeh chu ama hon Pathen Pathen atahsan pouvin chuleh amaho akhoukhah diuvin jong ana tahsan pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Pathen Pathen'in chungleng vanthamjol thu apen vankot jouse jong ahongdoh in,
\p 
\v 24 Aman aneh dingun van a kon'in Mana gojuh in ahin juhlhah sah in van changlhah chu ahinpen ahi.
\p 
\v 25 ama hon vantil buchu aneuvin, Pathen Pathen'in alungna chimsetnun apen ahi.
\p 
\v 26 Aman solam huichu ahin nunsah in, Athahatnan lhanglang huijong anunsah in ahi.
\p 
\v 27 Aman aneh dingun sachu vutdi jat ahin juhlhah sahin, vachaho chu twikhanglen panga neldi jat ahin,
\p 
\v 28 Aman vachaho chu aponbuh sungu leh avel uvah ahin lenlhah sah in ahi.
\p 
\v 29 ama hon oivasetin aneuvin ahi. Angaichat dungjuitah in apen ahi.
\p 
\v 30 Hinla ama hon angaichat dungjuiya anehva masangu, akam sung uva sa aumpet jeng jong chun,
\p 
\v 31 Pathen Pathen lunghana achung uvah ahunglhungtan ahileh Aman alah uva ahatpen pen ho chu athat tan ahi. Israel khangthah anasapen ho chu athat gamtan ahi.
\p 
\v 32 Ahijeng vangin mipi ho chun chonset aboljom jingun ahi, thilkidang ijat abol vangin atahsan dehpouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 33 Hiti chun ahinkhou chu lhuhgam na ahitan akum khouchu kichatnan adimtai.
\p 
\v 34 Pathen Pathen'in amaho ahin thapat phatnun ama hon ajona langin Ama chu ahin holtauvin ahi. Kisihna ahin neitauvin Pathen Pathen ahin holtauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 35 Hiti chun Pathen Pathen chu asongpiu ahi chuleh Pathen Pathen chu hatchungnung le ahuhhing pao ahi ahin geldoh tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 36 Ahijeng vangin hichu kamnal a anaseijiu ahibouvin alei u mangchan jou anaseiyun ahi.
\p 
\v 37 Alung sungu chu Pathen Pathen a ana petheng pouvin Pathen Pathen toh anakitep nauva jong ana dingdet pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 38 Hinla lungsetna dim Pathen Pathen chun achonset nau anangai damun amaho chu ana sumang deh pouvin ahi. Phat atamjon alunghan na anatuh tangin hiche bangchun ima ana tongdoh pon ahi.
\p 
\v 39 Tahsa mihembep ahiuve ti ahejingin, hui anun leh heikhat kahbou ahin ahung kiletapoi ti ageldoh in ahi.
\p 
\v 40 Gamthip sunga ijatvei Ama douna ana kiphin jengu chuleh alungsung anatsah vangin,
\p 
\v 41 Avel vel in Pathen Pathen thohhat nachu apatep jiuvin Israel Pathen Pathen chu asulunghang jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 42 ama hon athahatna in agalmi houva kon a anahuhdoh u hi ageldoh joutapouve.
\p 
\v 43 Egypt gamsunga thil kidang ijat abolu hitam chuleh Zoan phaicham a athil kidang bol ho chu ageldoh tapouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 44 Vadungho thisan asosah a don mohella alha, vadung twi donmo hella alha jengchu.
\p 
\v 45 Pathen Pathen'in amaho lah a thousi vaibong alansah a, uphohte alansah a agam ujong a suh set peh chu ahepha tapouve.
\p 
\v 46 Aman achang jouseu khongbai aneh gamsah in alousoh jouseu jong khaokhopi anehgam sah e.
\p 
\v 47 Alengpithei jouseu gel avohlhah sah sohkei in, atheipiu phung jouseu jong daibang athagamsah in ahi.
\p 
\v 48 Agancha jouseu gel lah a dalhah in aumsah in, akelngoi houjong keh alhah lihsah sohtai.
\p 
\v 49 Achung uva nasatah in alunghangin, alung dammona a lunghanna, mi sumang vantil hon tamtah alhahkhum tan ahi.
\p 
\v 50 Aman alunghanna achung uvah achuh sahtan, Egypt mite hinkho anahing hoipon, amangthah gamtan ahi,
\p 
\v 51 Egypt insunga achapa tahpen cheh athat in Egypt gamsung pumpia khangdongte pahcha amolsahtai.
\p 
\v 52 Hinla Aman amite chu kelngoi honbangin apuiyin gamthip noija bitkei in apui galkai tan ahi.
\p 
\v 53 Aman mongtah in apuilen hijeh chun ama hon kichatna anei pouve, chujongleh twikhanglen in agalteu alhoh mangpeh gamtai.
\p 
\v 54 Amaho chu Pathen Pathen'in agamtheng abanjetna atundoh, molsang vum achun ahin puilut in,
\p 
\v 55 Amaho masangah namtin vaipi adelmang peh sohkeiyin, abonchauvin achan dingu gam ahoppeh chehin, Israel phung namtin abonchauvin ama ama ponbuh cheh a achensah tai.
\p 
\v 56 Ahijeng vangin ama hon hatchungnung Pathen Pathen dounan thil abol jingun athupeh ho khatcha anitpeh pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 57 Apu apateu bangin avah mang-uvin jou jengin na atonguvin ahi. Amaho chu thalpi janglou bangin akitah pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 58 ama hon pathen dang ho doiphung aphutdoh un Pathen Pathen alunghan sah uvin, chuleh semthu pathen ahoujeh un Pathen Pathen athangthip sahtauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 59 Pathen Pathen'in ajahdoh phat in hatah in alunghangin Israel chu pumpai in apaimangtan ahi.
\p 
\v 60 Pathen Pathen'in Shiloh achenna mun adalhan mihemte lah a aumna ponbuh chu adalhatai.
\p 
\v 61 Aman aloupina le athaneina hetna kitepna thingkong chu galmiho khutna apehdohtan ahi.
\p 
\v 62 Ama amite chunga alunghan jeh-in agalmiteu athasah gamtan ahi.
\p 
\v 63 Gollhangho galah athigam tauvin, nungah ho akichenpidiu aumtapon ahi.
\p 
\v 64 Thempute athat gamtauvin ameithai houvin alhasetpi thei tapouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 65 Ajonan Yahweh Pakai chu a-ihmua ahung khangdoh bangin ahung thoudoh in mihatpa hung kiltildoh bangin ahung kitildohin,
\p 
\v 66 Galmi ho chu anungno in a-itih a ding jumna atosah tan ahi.
\p 
\v 67 Ahinla Joseph chilhah ho chu apaidohin, chuleh Ephraim phungchu alheng tapon ahi.
\p 
\v 68 Aman akhellin Judah leh angailut Zion molchu alhengin,
\p 
\v 69 hichea chun vanho san banga sang, leiset banga chah a-itih a um jing dingin Hou-In khat atungdoh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 70 Aman asohpa David chu akelngoi chinna a kon'in anakoudoh'in analheng tan ahi.
\p 
\v 71 Aman kelngoipi le anou achin laijin akoudoh'in amite Israel Jacob chilhah ho chu kelngoi chinna ching dingin anapansah tan ahi.
\p 
\v 72 David in amaho chu lungtheng tah leh chingtheitah in analamkaiyin ahi.
\c 79
\s1 Jerusalem Kisuhmang Jeh a Kana La
\s1 Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen chi ding namdang ten nanga dinga nanakilhendoh nagamchu ahinlo tauvin, na Hou-In theng asuboh'un chuleh Jerusalem chu khogemsa abahsah tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 2 ama hon nasohte tahsa chu vantham jolla lengle vachate adalhahpeh tauvin, pathen mi thengte tahsaphe chu gamlah a ganhingho an le chahin apangtan ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Jerusalem kimvellah thisan hi twilon in along jengin mithi vuiding koimacha aumpoi.
\p 
\v 4 Kaheng kakomho noise ding leh kajet kavei a umho dingin noise le taitomin kaumtauve.
\p 
\v 5 O Yahweh Pakai phat ichan geija kachung uva nalunghan ding hitam? Tonsot geijin em? Phat ichan geija nathangthipna chu meikong banga aljeng dingham?
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakai nalunghanna chu nang na donnom loute chidang namdang ho leh naminpan nomloute lenggam ho chungah bunglhatan.
\p 
\v 7 Ajeh chu ama hon namite Israel te hi avallhum gamtauvin chuleh gamsung hi gamgem asodohsah tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Kapu kapateu chonset jehin keiho neithep mosah hihbeh un! Nami khotonan gangtah in kangaichatnu neisuh bulhitpeh un, achutilouleh kakinepnau beiding ahitai.
\p 
\v 9 O Pathen Pathen kasochatnau, neipanhu loiyun! namin loupina dingin neipanhuvin, kachonset nau ngaidam inlang neihuhdoh'un namin loupina dingin.
\p 
\v 10 Ipi dinga chi ding namdang te hin eihouset uva “A Pathen u Pathen hoilai a umham?” natisah nahlai dingham? Hiche chi ding namdang ho chunga naphulahna chu neimusahih in, ajeh chu amaho hin nasohte thisan aso u ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Sohchangho lhasetna hi ngaipehin, thi dinga athu kitansa ho hi huhdoh inlang na thaneina chu neivet sah'un.
\p 
\v 12 O Yahweh Pakai kaheng kakom hon noise tah a nahousetnao hi ajat sagin lethuh tei in.
\p 
\v 13 Hiteng chuleh keiho namite na ngailutna ankonga kivah nakelngoiten akhang khangin nang vahchoi ungting, vahchoijing taovinge.
\c 80
\s1 Israel Semphatna Dinga Taona
\s1 Lalamkaipa henga Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 O Israel neingaipehun, nangma Joseph chilhah te gancha hon ho banga puihoija kelngoi chin a chingpa. O Pathen Pathen Cherub chunga laltouna a toupan naloupinavah hoi chu hin kimudoh sah in.
\p 
\v 2 Ephraim, Benjamin leh Mannaseh chungah hintah langin, nathahatna gimneitah chu neimusah unlang neihung huhdoh tauvin.
\p 
\v 3 O Pathen Pathen nangma kom'ah neihoilutnun, namaivah chun neihin salvah un, chuteng boule huhhing kachandiu ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai, Pathen ka Pathen, phat itihchan gei a kataona sanlou a nakoi dingham?
\p 
\v 5 Nangin lungkhamna a ichan gei a neivah uva chuleh khondimset a mitlhi neilonsah diuham?
\p 
\v 6 Nangin hengle kom chi ding namdang te taitomna neichansah tauvin kagalmi teuvin totnan einei tauve.
\p 
\v 7 O Pathen Pathen hatchungnung nangma kom neingatsah un, namaivah chun neisalvah'un chutenglehbou huhhing kachandiu ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Nangin lengpiga twi bangin Egyptma kon'in neihin puidohun, nangin chi ding namdang ho nadel mangna na gamsunga neipuilutnu ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Nangman keiho ding amun neisuhtheng pehun chuleh hichea chun keiho kajung khouvin gamsung chu kadimset tauve.
\p 
\v 10 keiho len molsangho atomjouvin, kabah houvin Cedar thingphung lentah tahho atomjouvin,
\p 
\v 11 keihon kabah hou lhumlam Mediterranean twikhanglen gei in kathejalun chuleh kajungun Euphrate vadung gei ka thejallun ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Hinla tunvang, kabangu ipi dinga neivoh lhahpeh uva, hilang lampia hinhopa jousen kagao akiguh u hitam?
\p 
\v 13 Gammanga kon'in ngalchang hangin avallhum in, gamlah ganchahon kivahnan anei un ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Hungkile kit in O Pathen Pathen hatchungnung, kahung tao un ahi. Van'a kon'in neihin veuvin kahahsat nau neihin vetpeh un, hiche lengpi gui hi hin khoukhah'in.
\p 
\v 15 Nangma tah in nanatu ahi. Hiche chapa hi nangma tah in nangma dinga nahin khoukhah ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Ajeh chu keiho hi thing banga eikitan bong bonga kagal miteuvin eihal lhah'u ahitai. Nangman navetsah chu amutengu leh manthahnan juiju hen.
\p 
\v 17 Mihem na ngailut nacha nadeilhen chu hatsah-in,
\p 
\v 18 Chutengleh keihon itihchan injong nanungsun pouvinge. Nei suhal kit un chutileh namin avel'a kahin koukit theidiu ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Nangma komlang nei ngatsah kitnun, O Yahweh Pakai, Pathen ka Pathen hatchungnung namaivah chun neihin salvah'un, chutenglehbou huhhing kachandiu ahi.
\c 81
\s1 Egypt'a Kon Potdoh Golvahna
\s1 Lalamkai pa henga Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 Ei thahatsah u Pathen Pathen thangvahnan la sauvin, Jacob Pathen Pathen vahchoinan la sauvin.
\p 
\v 2 Sauvin! tumging tothon avahchoila sauvin voh gingthei vouvin, semjang kisai ginleh selangdah gin to thouvin,
\p 
\v 3 Lhathah janle sumkon mut-uvin lang, lhalih janle lhalih nikhoa golvah bolteng sumkon mut uvin.
\p 
\v 4 Ajeh chu hiche hi Israel dinga chondan thupeh ahin Jacob Pathen Pathen thugahsa ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Egypt gam a kon a ahungdoh uchun Aman Joseph kom'a hettohsah khat anaphutdoh tai. Keiman kahetchetlou thukhat kajan,
\p 
\v 6 Keiman apohgih kangai jangin akhut a jong thilgih kangai jangin akhut a jong thilgih hahsa kathamsah tapoi.
\p 
\v 7 Nagimna a kon'in neihin kouvin keiman kahuhdohtai. Meivom lhangkhat kiheh chetchut lah a kahin houjin, Meribah a twi umloupet in natahsah kapatepjin ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Ngai uvin O kamite, nangho gihna nasatah kapeh pet-hin, Vo Israel kaseihi nangai poupou uleh,
\p 
\v 9 Nanghon imatihchan ajong gamchom mit pathen koipouvin nate, pathen lhem masanga kun pouvin nate.
\p 
\v 10 Ajeh chu Egypt-a kon a nahin puidoh uva Yahweh Pakai na Pathen'u Pathen keima kahi. Nakam hakatnin ka-in keiman thilpha tamtah adimsetna kahin sunlut pehding ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Ahinla kamiten angainom pouvin, Israel'in Keima eingaicha pouve.
\p 
\v 12 Hijeh chun Keiman alouchallu dungjuijin amaho deilam lam a chondin kalha kangtai.
\p 
\v 13 O kamiten kaseihi ngaipou pouleu, O Kamite Israel te hin eijuiju henlang kalampia hin chenom poupouleu!
\p 
\v 14 Ichan geija gang in agalmiteu kajopeh tadiuvem! Ichan geija gangtah in akidoupiteu chunga kakhut kalha tadem!
\p 
\v 15 Koi hileh Yahweh Pakai nahsah loute chu a-angsunga kisuchipdiu atonsotna mahthahdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Ahinla keiman nehthei aphapen a kavah ding nahin, keiman songpia kon a kimu khoijua kavahdiu nahi.
\c 82
\s1 Pathen Pathen In Migiloute Chunga Thu Atan Ding
\s1 Asaph labol
\p 
\v 1 Van'a thutanna chunga Pathen Pathen'in vai ahomin Van mite chunga athutanna aphondoh e.
\p 
\v 2 Nangman itihchan hi miphalouho napanpia thudihlou ho nachelhah sah dingham?
\p 
\v 3 “Chaga leh vaichate chungah thudih chepin lang; tahlel tele engbolla umte chungah thudih phongdoh in.
\p 
\v 4 Panpi bei tele engbolla umte huhdoh in, miphalouho khut a kon'in huhdoh-in.
\p 
\v 5 Hinla mibolse ten imacha ahepouve; amahokhu hetna lhasam ahiuve. Muthim noi a avah leuvin, leiset sungil lamgei in ahotling tai.
\p 
\v 6 Keiman kasei in, ‘Nangho Pathen nahiuve; nangho hatchungnung chilhah te nahiu ve.
\p 
\v 7 Hinlah nangho mihem tobang bep a nathi diu, thunei vaihom dang ho banga nalhuh tei diu ahi.’”
\p 
\v 8 Hung kipatin, O Pathen Pathen vannoi leiset hi athu tannin, ajeh chu chi ding namdang ho jouse jonghi aboncha nanga ahi.
\c 83
\s1 Leiset Chunga Pathen Pathen Bou Asang Pen Ahi
\s1 Asap labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen, thipbeh in umhih'in! Na-ngong in umhih'in. O Pathen Pathen thipsan jeng hih in.
\p 
\v 2 Nagalmite cho leng lung khu najahlou ham? Kiletsah tah nagalmiho ahung kipatdoh khu nahet louham?
\p 
\v 3 ama hon namite douna dingin aguh in thil agong uvin, nangin napanhu mite dounan thil phalou agong uvin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 ama hon aseijun “Hungun hiche nam mite hi sumang uhite akitiuve, chutileh Israel hi isuhmit heldiu ahi” atiuve.
\p 
\v 5 Hiche tohgon ahi amaho akinop to uvin nang dounan kiloikhomna khat anei taove.
\p 
\v 6 Ama ho hi Edom mite, Ishmael mite, Moab mite, Hagrit mite,
\p 
\v 7 Gebal mite, Ammon mite, Amalek mite chuleh Philistine leh Tyre akon mipi ho ahiuve.
\p 
\v 8 Assyria miten jong ajopmun ahin, Lot chilhah hoto jong kiloikhom ahiuve.
\p 
\v 9 Amaho hi Midian, Sisera, Jabin mite Kishion vadunga nabol bang bangin boljengin.
\p 
\v 10 Amaho chu Endor lah nasumang in chuleh atahsa'u monlha chu leiset leipha sosahnan akimang in ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Nangin alamkai ho chu Oreb le Zoab nabolna banginsumang in lang chuleh avaipo ho chu Zebah le Zalmunna nabolna banginthatdoh tan,
\p 
\v 12 ajeh chu ama hon hitin aseijuve, “eihon hiche Pathen Pathen gam ho hi eiho phatchom na dingin lahpeh-u hite” akitiuve.
\p 
\v 13 O Pathen Pathen amaho hi huilah a changvai akithejal bangin thejaltan!
\p 
\v 14 Meijin gammang ahal banginchuleh meikong in molle lhang ahal lhah banginhallha jengin,
\p 
\v 15 Huile gon melse tah a adelmang bangindelmang'in, nakhopi huijin kichat sah in,
\p 
\v 16 Nasatah in sujumm in O Yahweh Pakai, namin a ahung kipehlut tokah un.
\p 
\v 17 Amaho hi tonsotna jum ding leh kicha jing dingin melsetah in thisah tan.
\p 
\v 18 Hiteng chuleh ama hon nangbou hi Hatchungnung leiset chunga thunei chungnung nahi hi hin hetau vinte.
\c 84
\s1 Pathen Pathen Hou-In a Kikhom Ding Ngaichat
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai hatchungnung naHou-In hi iti kangailut hitam?
\p 
\v 2 Hiche a chu iti kaum nom hitam! Yahweh Pakai Hou-Inn chu kangaicha lheh jenge, kahina apumpin hingjing Pathen Pathen ah kakipana lan sange.
\p 
\v 3 Inva jengin jong abuh akisah in, chuleh pengpalep injong intum akison e. Vo Yahweh Pakai hatchungnung, kalengpa le ka Pathen Pathen! Vachan jong namaicham kom'a anou kicholdo nading abuh akisem ahi.
\p 
\v 4 NaHou-Inn'a chenghon ichan gei a hinkho nopna anei'u hitam phat tin in nangma vahchoila asauve.
\p 
\v 5 Athahatna Yahweh Pakai a kon a kimuho hinkho iti nop a hitam, alungsungun Jerusalem'ah akholjing jengun ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Beca phaicham ajot tengu jongleh, twisam putna twinah tampi umna bangin abol'un, gotwi hunglha masapen in jong twikul tampi ahinsemdoh pehjiuve.
\p 
\v 7 Amaho akalson chan uva ahetbe cheh chehjingdiu ahin, ama hon Jerusalem a Yahweh Pakai chu amudiu ahi.
\p 
\v 8 O Yahweh Pakai, Ka Pathen Pathen hatchungnung kataona neingaipeh'in, O Jacob Pathen Pathen.
\p 
\v 9 O Pathen Pathen kalengpauhi phatthei boh'in, ama hi kaluum u ahi, nathaonusa nalhen pahi khotona musah jingin.
\p 
\v 10 Munchom a ni sangkhat umsangin na Hou-In a nikhat um aphajoi. Miphalou inna chen sangin ka Pathen Pathen'inn'a kotngah a pan aphajoi.
\p 
\v 11 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai, Pathen Pathen hi eiho dia nisa le umpho ahi. Aman khoto na le loupina eipeuvin ahi. Yahweh Pakaiyin thildih jeng bol mihoa kon'in thilpha alamang pon ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Yahweh Pakai hatchungnung nangma tahsan miho hi iti kipa um a hitam?
\c 85
\s1 Hepina Le Huhhingna Dia Taona
\s1 Korah chilhah te labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai nangin na gamsung'ah phatthei bohna nasunglhan ahi! Hiti chun nangin Israel phatthei naboh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Nangman namite chonsetna nangaidam in hichun achonset nau jouse na lekhu peh e.
\p 
\v 3 Nangin na lunghan na natuh tang'in, na lunghanna deujah jengchu naki kham jie.
\p 
\v 4 Ei suhal kit uvin, eihuhhingpau O Pathen Pathen! kachung uva nalunghan na tolmang kittan.
\p 
\v 5 Kachung uva nalunghan jing jeng dingham? Na lunghanna khang jouse chung naumsah jing jengding hitam?
\p 
\v 6 Nei suhhal kit loudiu hitam? Namite kipa le thanom a aum jing theina ding a.
\p 
\v 7 Vo Pathen Pathen nami ngailutna longlou chu neimu sah'in nami huhhing najong neipe uvin.
\p 
\v 8 Pathen na Pathen chun ipi asei am, chingthei tah in ngai in ajeh chu Aman mi kitah ho kom'ah chamna thu asei e. Ahinla amaho angolna lampi uvah kilekit dahen.
\p 
\v 9 Tahbeh in Ama gingte dingin huhing na naicha um a ahi. Chuti leh igamsung u jong aloupina dimding ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Ngailutna longlou leh thutah akimuto'in chonphat na le chamna akichopto lhon e.
\p 
\v 11 Kitah nahi leiset a kon a hungdoh ahi. Chuleh chonphatna chu van'a kon a mai lhaisel'a hung kumlha ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Adih'e, Yahweh Pakaiyin phatthei boh hi ahin lonlhahsah ahin gam leiset a hi ninglhing tah a ahin gadoh sah a ikisan ji u ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Chonphat nahin Yahweh Pakai hung nading semtoh nading nikho asap masat ji ahi.
\c 86
\s1 David Tahsanna'a Akibul Phu
\s1 David Taona
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai hung kisunem'in lang kataona neingai peh'in, neidonbut in ajeh chu napanpi ngaicha jing kahi.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakai nanga dinga kiphaldoh jing kahi neihuhdoh'in ajeh chu nangma hi ka Pathen Pathen nahin, keima hi nakinbol kahin chuleh nangma hi katansan jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai nami khotona neimusah jingin ajeh chu keiman Nangmahi ka koujing nahi.
\p 
\v 4 O Yahweh Pakai kipana neimusah jingin ajeh chu keimahi Nangkom'a kiphaldoh jing kahi.
\p 
\v 5 O Yahweh Pakai nangma hi naphatna jalla eingaidam jing nahi, nakom'a panpi ngaichaho dinga longlou ngailutna dimsah nahi.
\p 
\v 6 O Yahweh Pakai kataonahi khotonan neingaipeh'in gangtah a kap kahi neingaipehin.
\p 
\v 7 Kahahsat channa nangma kakou ding ahin nangin neidonbut jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 O Pathen Pathen! Semthu pathen ho nang tobang khatcha aumpoi, nabolthei ho bolthei jong aumpoi.
\p 
\v 9 Naemsa chitin namtin ho jong na ang a hungdiu chibai naboh cheh diu ahi Yahweh Pakai; ama hon na mintheng avahchoi diu ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Ajeh chu nangma bou Pathen Pathen nahin naloupin, nangin bou thil loupiho naboldoh jin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 O Yahweh Pakai, na lampiho neihil in, nathudih dung jui a hinkho kaman theina dingin, nangma loupina kadopsang jingna dingin lungtheng neipen.
\p 
\v 12 O Yahweh ka Pakai, Pathen ka Pathen! kalungthim pumpin nangma nathangvah ingkate, phattin'in naloupina domsang jing tange.
\p 
\v 13 Ajeh chu nei ngailutna hi akidange. Nangman thina kulkhuh a kon'in nei huhdoh tai
\p 
\v 14 O Yahweh Pakai mijumso hatho keima dounan ahung ding doh un; misunoh phah a pang hon thading eigouve. Ama hon nangma hi imachan nagel pouve.
\p 
\v 15 Ahinlah Yahweh Pakai Nangma hi khoto na leh ngailutna nei Pathen Pathen nahin lunghang vahlou chuleh kitahna leh tang theilou lungsetna dim a nahi.
\p 
\v 16 Nami lungsetna chun noilang hinven lang nasoh hi tha neipen, nasohpa chapa kahi neihuhdoh'in.
\p 
\v 17 Nei hepina melchihna chu hin tahlang'in chutileh eivetda ho hin jumna amudiu ahi. O Yahweh Pakai neipanpin nei lungmonsah jingin.
\c 87
\s1 Pathen Pathen Khopi Loupi
\s1 Korah chilhah te labol
\p 
\v 1 Moltheng chunga chun Yahweh Pakai tundohsa khopi chu aum'e.
\p 
\v 2 Aman Jerusalem khopi hi Israel khopi dang ho sangin angailu joi.
\p 
\v 3 O Pathen Pathen khopi, nangma chung chang ahi itibang thuloupi tahtah kisei a hitam!
\p 
\v 4 Keima eiheho lah a hin, Egypt le Babylon chule Philistine leh Tyre chuleh gamla tah Ethiopia jong kasimtha e. Amaho hi Jerusalem khomite ahitaove.
\p 
\v 5 Jerusalem chung chang a hitia hi kisei ding ahi, “amijousen nammi hina a thaneina chu akipapi cheh uve”, chule hatchungnung ama tah in khopi chu phatthei aboh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakaiyin chitin namtin hi ajihlut teng, aseiding, “amaho jouse hi Jerusalem khomite ahitaove” atiding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Mipi ho chun theile amut'uva la asahdiu, “Kahinkho hung kipat nahi Jerusalem ahi” atidiu ahi.
\c 88
\s1 Thina Kona Lhatdohna Dinga Taona
\s1 Hesoh genthei lakai a sah dia Ezrahite mipa Heman in lalamkai pa henga dia alabol.
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, eihuhhing'a ka Pathen Pathen, sun leh nangma kakou in, jan leh nakom kahin nailut ji e.
\p 
\v 2 Tun kakouna neijah peh'in lang katona neisan peh'in.
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu kahin kho hi boina adim in, thinan eikainai chehcheh e.
\p 
\v 4 Athisa bang bep kahitai, mithahat tah khat athahat na bei nungsang bep kahitai.
\p 
\v 5 ama hon mithi lah a eidalha uvin lhan ah mithi lup'in kalum e. Keima hi suhmil in kaumtai, nami kaihoina a kon'in eiki lamang tai.
\p 
\v 6 Nangin kotong noinung pen athim pen ah neison lha e.
\p 
\v 7 Nalung han na gihtah chun eidelphan, hichu twi kinong bangin akinong'in eichup tai.
\p 
\v 8 Keima hi doumah in neisem in kagol kapai ho neidelmang peh gamtai. Keima hi thang'ah ka-oh in kitoldoh theilouvin kaum'e.
\p 
\v 9 Kamit lhin kamit achupmin kho muthei louvin kaum'e. O Yahweh Pakai niseh'in na panpina kathum in nami lungsetna ngaichan kakhut teni kahin sange.
\p 
\v 10 Nathil kidang bol ho hi mithi dinga phachom ding hinam? Mithi hungthodoh a nathangvah theiding hinam?
\p 
\v 11 Lhankhuh a kon'in ama hon nami ngailutna longlou hi ahin phongdoh theina diuvem? Suhmangna mun'a umhon nakitah nahi aphongdoh theina diuvem?
\p 
\v 12 Muthim'in nathilbol kidang ho hi aseiphong nadiuvem? Thil suhmil delna gama umhon na chonphat na ho chu aseiphong theina diuvem?
\p 
\v 13 O Yahweh Pakai nangma kakouve, niseh-a nakom'a katao jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 O Yahweh Pakai, ibolla kei nei paidoh hitam? Ibol a kei a kon a naki heimang hitam?
\p 
\v 15 Kakhang don lai a pat a, kanatna hin thina komcha eina lhutsa ahitan, nagim neina masanga hin thabei leh lungkham tah in kading e.
\p 
\v 16 Nalunghan na tijat umtah chun eilonvuh'in, tijat naumna chun eithabei sah e.
\p 
\v 17 Hiche ho chun sun nilhum in twisoh bangin kavel a eilon khum un ahi. Muthimhi kakinai pipen kagol in apang un ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Nangman ka mite le ka ngailut cheng neilahpeh tai, Thimjing hi kaki naipi pen ka loi chu ahitai.
\c 89
\s1 Akitepna Asem Jeh'in Pathen Pathen Thangvah In Umhen
\s1 Ezrahite mipa Ethan labol
\p 
\v 1 Keiman Yahweh Pakai mi ngailutna longlou thu hi vahchoilan sajing tange, khangdong ho leh tehse hon nakitahna hi ajauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Nami ngailutna longlou hi itih hijongleh um jing ding ahi. Nakitah nahi vanho bangin aum jinge.
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakaiyin hitin asei e “kalhendoh kasohpa David toh kitepna kanabol ahi. Hiche kitepna a hi kana kihahsel ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Keiman na chilhah te chu lenga katun jingding ahi. Amaho nalaltouna a chu tu apat tonsot gei a toujingdiu ahi.”
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai van mite jousen nakidan naho hi navahchoi diu ahi. Nakitahna ho jeh a hi simjoulou vantil ten navahchoi diu ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Ajeh chu van gam a umho jouse koipen tah hi Yahweh Pakai toh tekah thei umbeh am? Vantil thupipen ho jeng jong Yahweh Pakai toh tekah pithei um'am?
\p 
\v 7 Vantil thaneipen ho jong Pathen Pathen ang'a kithing thinga ahi bouve. Ama hi alaltouna vel a ding ho jousen jong agimnei na aphapouve.
\p 
\v 8 O Yahweh Pakai hatchungnung sepai ho! Hoilai mun a nang tobanga thanei a umbeh am Yahweh Pakai? Nanghi kitahna lhingset nahi.
\p 
\v 9 Twikhanglen jong na thaneina noia umma ahi. Nangin huipi le twipi kithoa twi kinong jong nasutang'in,
\p 
\v 10 twikhanglen'a um sa lenpen ho jong na sugep in, Naban thahat in nagal mite jong nahocheh jitai.
\p 
\v 11 Vanho jouse jong nanga ahin, leiset jong nanga ahi, vannoi a um thiljouse jong aboncha nanga ahin nangin nasem ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Nangin sahlang lhanglang jong nasem ahin, Tabor Mol leh Hermon mol'in jong naming athangvah ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Nabantha hi iti hat hitam! Nakhut hi iti hat hitam! Najetlang jonghi nathahat loupitah in adomsange.
\p 
\v 14 Chonphat na le thudih chu nalaltouna khombul ahi. Longlou ngailutna le kitahna chu nalhachate bangin na angsung'ah avahlen ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Pathen Pathen houna dinga kipa umtah kouna jaho chu anunnom ahiuve, ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai amaho hi na umpina vah a chu lhalediu ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Naminthan na kidangtah ho hi ama hon nilhum kei keija akipapi diu ahi. Ama hon nachon phatna hi akithang-atpiu vin ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Nangma hi amaho dinga thahatna loupitah chu nahi. Keiho thahat sah dinghi nangma kipana ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Ahi, keiho hoidohna hi Yahweh Pakai a kon ahi. Chuleh Israel Pathen Pathen hin lengjong eipeh u ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Masang lai in kitah tah a nangma jui namipite lah-a gaothu nana seijin ahi. Nangin nasei in, Keiman galsat ding kanalhengdoh'in keiman milhamho lah a konna lengding jong kanalhendoh ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Keiman kasoh David kana mudoh'in chuleh kathaotheng kana nun ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Keiman kakhut a kana dindoh sah a, kaban thahatna kahatdoh sahding ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Agal miten ajoloudiu ahilouleh miphalou honjong athajou loudiu ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Keiman akidoupi ho hi amasang tah a kasuhlhuh ding ahin chuleh ama douho jouse jong ka suhmang ding ahi.
\p 
\v 24 Kakitahna leh kangailutna longlou hin aumpi jingding kathuneina jalla ama hi atha kahatsah jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 25 Keiman twikhanglen chunga jong athaneina kalhunlut ding vadungho chung jenga jong vai ahomding ahi.
\p 
\v 26 Chutengleh aman eihin kou intin, “Nangma kapa nahin ka Pathen Pathen, kasongpi le kasochatna nahi” atiding ahi.
\p 
\v 27 Keiman Ama hi kachapa masapen, leiset chunga leng thaneipen kahisah ding,
\p 
\v 28 Kangailut ding chuleh tonsot gei a kakhoto ding, ama toh kaki tepna hi angahtih umlouding ahi.
\p 
\v 29 Keiman ama dinga ason apah ho kahoibit pehding, van gam'a nikhon beitih aneilou banga alaltounan jong beitih aneilouding ahi.
\p 
\v 30 Ahinlah achilhah ten ka thuhil ho hi apaidoh uva, kachedan hi ajuilou uva,
\p 
\v 31 ka Dan semho hi anit lou uva chuleh kathupeh hi angailou uleh,
\p 
\v 32 keiman achonset nau chunga gambol na mol kalap ding, chuleh athungailou naojeh a kavoh diu ahi.
\p 
\v 33 Hijeng jongleh kangailutna chu beideh louding kakitepna jong achunga kasuhmil deh louding ahi.
\p 
\v 34 Ahipoi, kakitepna chu kasuhkeh louding ahi; keiman kana seidoh saho chu changkhat jong kanung lahdoh louding ahi.
\p 
\v 35 Keiman David kom'a h kihahselna khat kana nei in chule atheng kahi jeh in jou seiponge.
\p 
\v 36 Ama chilhah te itihchan hijongleh chelha jingding alenggam jong nisa banga chelhum ding ahi.
\p 
\v 37 Vantham jolla ka hettohsah nachu lhavah banga kikheltih aneitah louding ahi.
\p 
\v 38 Ahinlah nangin tuhin ama chu nakahdoh tan chuleh napaidoh tai. Tuhin Nangma nathaonu lengpa chungah nalunghang tan,
\p 
\v 39 nangin Ama toh nakitepna napaidohtan, nangin alal lukhuh jong vutvai lah-a nasep lhatai.
\p 
\v 40 Nangin akhopiu bangho navohlhah pehtan chuleh akulpiu jong khogem nasodohsah ahitai.
\p 
\v 41 Koi hileh ahin hopa jousen athilkeu u akichomgam hellun aheng akomho jousen anuisat'un ahi.
\p 
\v 42 Nangin agal miteu galjona namusahin, abonchauvin nakipasah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 43 Nangin agal manchah u manmo naso'in chuleh galmunnah gal na lelsah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 44 Nangin aleng tenggol nalahpehin chuleh alaltouna tolsenan naneipeh in ahi.
\p 
\v 45 Nangin aphat achang louvin natehset sah'in chuleh jumthet in nalhan ahi.
\p 
\v 46 Yahweh Pakai nangma hi hitia hi kisel jing jingding nahi hitam? Ichan gei nalunghanna meikong jing jeng dingham?
\p 
\v 47 Kahinkho hi itihchom a hitam geldoh'in, keiho hi thitei dinga neisem'u ahi ti geldoh'in!
\p 
\v 48 Mihing koihi athi theilou ding um'am? Mihem koipen ham lhan a kon a ahoidohthei dingah?
\p 
\v 49 Yahweh Pakai tumasanga nei ngailut nau chu ahet theina mudohthei ipi umam? David kom'a nakitepna ho hi hoilang geija hitam?
\p 
\v 50 Nasohpa keimahi ichan gei a jumna kato hitam? Hiche nangma hedohlou mitehin eisapsetnau ichan gei a kathoh hitam?
\p 
\v 51 O Yahweh Pakai nadeilhen na lengpa hi nangma dou miten nahsah loutah in abollun ahi! Achena chan a asujum un ahi.
\p 
\v 52 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah in um jing jenghen! Amen, Amen!
\c 90
\s1 BU LINA
\s1 Nam Mite Dinga Mose Taona
\s1 Pathen Pathen mipa Mose taona
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai, akhang khanga nangmahi kachennao inn nahijenge!
\p 
\v 2 Moul le lhang ho pen masang, vannoi le leiset hi natundoh masangin, thiljoue kipat a pat ajo na chen in jong, nangma Pathen Pathen nahijing e.
\p 
\v 3 Nangin mihemhi anahina masa-a kile kitdingin nasollin leivui na lesosah kitjin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Nangdin Kum sangkhat jeng jonghi achejing tunikho bangbep ahin, jan phat chomcha tobang bou ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Nangin twisoh bangin neilhohmang jiuvin mang sangin asot jodeh poi. Keiho hi hampa jingkah langa hung pahdoh tobang bou kahiuve.
\p 
\v 6 Hichu akhangdoh loijin ahinla nilhah langle agop lhajin athijitai.
\p 
\v 7 Keiho hi nangma lunghan nan eisumang jitauvin chuleh nalung satnan eikichatsah'un ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Nangin kachonset nau namasangah natahlang jin ahi, aguh a kachonset nauhi nakilandoh sahjin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Nalungsat na noi a higjing kahinkhou ahin, kakumkhou jong lungsat nan abeiloi jitai.
\p 
\v 10 Kei ho hi kum 70 hingding bep kahiuvin, kahat tah'uleh kum 80 bep hingding kahiuve, ahinla hiche sunga chun natna le boina bou ahin; amang loiji tauvin, chule keiho kaleng mang taove.
\p 
\v 11 Nalunghanna thahat koiham ahe thei dingah? Naging a nalungsat khohje gelkhoh a koi ham?
\p 
\v 12 Kachih theina diuvin kahinkhou chomdan hi neihetsah tauvin.
\p 
\v 13 O Yahweh Pakai, kaheng lam uva hung kile kit tan! Itihchan neikho ngai diu hitam?
\p 
\v 14 Jingkah seh le nalungset longlou chun kalungthim kipasah in, chutile kahinkhou lhumkei a navah choi la kasha jing diu ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Hesoh genthei kana thoh hou chuga kon'in lunglhai na themkhat beh nei peu vin! Kakhoisat nao kumho jong kipana neisoh doh peh un.
\p 
\v 16 Nasohte hi nathilbol kidangtah ho chu neimusah'un; kachilhah teuvin na thaneina loupitah chu mu uhen.
\p 
\v 17 Chuteng Yahweh Pakai ka Pathen Pathen un namalsom nauchu eimu sah uhen lang katohna jouseuvah lolhinna eipetao hen. Henge, katoh gao neiso peh un.
\c 91
\s1 Pathen Pathen Venbitna Noiya Um Ding
\p 
\v 1 Chungnungpen cholngah na noi a um chan chun hatchungnung lhalim noi a choldo na amu ding ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakai chung chang a hiche hi kaphong e: Ama bou eivengbit ahin, kahoidam na mun ahi; Ama chu ka Pathen Pathen ahin, keiman ama katah san e.
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu aman thangkol jouse a kon'in nahuhdoh intin thinathei hivei hoa kon a nahuhdohding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Aman alhavinga na le khu ding ahi. A lhalim noi a nahoidoh ding ahi. Kitah tah a akihahsel naho chu nading a galvon le ompho ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Jan a misu lung linglao ho kichat dan, sun lai a thalchang leng le ho jong kichat dan.
\p 
\v 6 Jan noi a donthah nantna hivei gimnei tah ho kichat dan, sun lai a nadelkhum hesoh na jong kicha hih in.
\p 
\v 7 Nasih langa sangkhat lhu henlang, navel a sangsom thijongleh, hiche boina hon nangma natoh khah louding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Namit hah in lang vejengin, itilom a migilou te chung a got na lhung hitam?
\p 
\v 9 Nangin Yahweh Pakai chu napanpi ding a nakisem le, Yahweh Pakai chu nahuhdoh ding a nakigon ahi le,
\p 
\v 10 Setna imachan najo louding ahi; natna hivei khatchan jong na inn ahinphah louding ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Chutengleh Pathen Pathen'in navale nachan a navengbit din avantil te thu pen tai.
\p 
\v 12 Nakeng chu songa nakisuhkhah louna dinga vantil ten akhut uva nadopdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Nangin keipi bahkai ho nasuh goi a; gul hang ho chuleh gunei gul ho nalhonat gamding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Yahweh Pakaiyin hitin ati, “keima eingailu ho kahuh hing ding ahi. Kamin a tahsan na nei ho chu kahoi dam ding ahi.
\p 
\v 15 ama hon eihin koutengu leh keiman kadonbut ding chuleh hahsatna ato tengu leh keiman kaumpi ding ahi, keiman amaho chu kahuhdoh a jabolna kachan sah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Keiman hinkho sotna kapehding chuleh kavenbit jingdiu ahi” ati.
\c 92
\s1 Pathen Pathen Hi Vahchoi Dia Lom Ahi
\s1 Sabbath nikhoa sah ding la
\p 
\v 1 Thangvah na Yahweh Pakai peh a, chungnungpen vah choi ding hi thilpha ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Jingkah le nami ngailutna longlou sap phong a, nilhah le nakitah na sap phong hi thilpha ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Tumging jangsom to tho a lyre gin ngai tah to tho dia pha tah ahi.
\p 
\v 4 O Yahweh Pakai nei bol peh thil loupitah ho chun kalung lai atongkha in, natohdoh ho jehchun keiman kipa la kasan ahi.
\p 
\v 5 O Yahweh Pakai nanatohdoh ho hi iti loupi hitam! nalunggel ngeito ho jong iti gil a gil jeng hitam.
\p 
\v 6 Mihem mai mai het jou hoi ahipon, chih na a lhasam hon jong hedoh jou pouvin te.
\p 
\v 7 Migilou ho chu hamhing bangin khangtou'un tin, thilse bol ho chu pungthei jong leu, tonsot a suhmanga umdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Hinla Yahweh Pakai, nangma vang, tonsot a dopsang a naum jing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Namel ma te jouse mangthah tei diu ahi; chule gitlou nabol jouse suh chat vai a um diu ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Nangin keimahi bongchal bangin neihatdoh sahtan, chuleh nangin kipanan neimalsom tan ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Kamit hin kagal mite lhuh amun; kana kol in jong eidou a migiloute gallel na thu ajai.
\p 
\v 12 Michonphate chu chahthing bangin khangtou untin, Lebanon a Cedar thing banga hat tah khangtoudiu ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Amaho hi Yahweh Pakaiyinn a kehdoh thingphung likeh ahiuvin, I-Pathen'u Pathen angsung a khangtouva ahiuve,
\p 
\v 14 Teh nung jeng a jong ga aso nalai diu; chuleh phattin'a noujing leh hatjing diu ahi.
\p 
\v 15 ama hon aphondoh uva hitia hi asei diu ahi, “Yahweh Pakai chu adih jingin! Ama chu kasong pi ahi! Ama a chun set na aumpoi!”
\c 93
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Vaihomna
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai hi lengpa ahi! Ama loupi na in a kivon e. Hiti chun Yahweh Pakai chu loupi na le hat nan akivon e. Leiset hi ading det in suh ling hoi ahipoi.
\p 
\v 2 O Yahweh Pakai nalaltouna chu phat kisim masang a pat a umsa ahitai. Nangma jeng jong phat kipat masanga aum jingsa nahitai.
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai twikhanglen akikhan tou e. Twisoh hi van gin abang tai; twisoh in gih tah in akinon sah e.
\p 
\v 4 Hinlah twikhanglen kinong ging dem dum sang a nasa jo le, twipi pang a twinong kivoging sang'in jong Yahweh Pakai thilbol theina anasa joi.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai na Dan thu sem ho hin kikhel tih anei poi. Navai hop na jong Yahweh Pakai, tonsot a theng jing jeng ding ahi.
\c 94
\s1 Yahweh Pakaiyin Amite Dinga Phu Alah Ding
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, phulaji Pathen Pathen, O phula ji Pathen Pathen nathutanna dihtah chu loupitah chu hung kilang doh hen.
\p 
\v 2 Hungthou doh in, vainoi thutan pa. Mi kiletsah ho chu achan ding dol u chansah in!
\p 
\v 3 Miphalou ho hi itih chanpi kipah diuham, ichan gei in em Yahweh Pakai?
\p 
\v 4 Itih chan kiletsah tah a thu asei diu ham? Hiche migilou ho hi itih chanpi kihatsah diu ham?
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai ama hon namite asuchip gam tauve. Nangma mite ho hi ama hon asugenthei'un ahi.
\p 
\v 6 ama hon meithai ho leh gamdang mi chule chaga ho athat gam un ahi.
\p 
\v 7 ama hon aseiyun, “Yahweh Pakaiyin eive pouve chule, Israel Pathen Pathen'in anasah poi.”
\p 
\v 8 Kigel pha kit un, mingol ho! Itihleh tah le nahin hethei diuvem?
\p 
\v 9 Na nakol sempa chu a nangong ham? Namit sempau chu amitcho a ham?
\p 
\v 10 Aman chitin namtinte ana engbol in ahi, nangjong na engbol louding ham? Aman ima jouse ahesohkei in ahi, nangin ipi naboljong ahetsohkei louding ham?
\p 
\v 11 Yahweh Pakaiyin mitin lunggel ahesohkei e, imacha phatchomna neilou ahi ahesohkei e.
\p 
\v 12 Yahweh Pakai, nadanthu a nahil ho leh nasuhdih ho chu iti kipah u hitam?
\p 
\v 13 Migilou te kimat nading leiko tong akilai kah sen nangman amaho chu boina a kon'in lung ol na nape e.
\p 
\v 14 Yahweh Pakaiyin amite nungsun ponte; Aman ami deitumte donlou in koi ponte.
\p 
\v 15 Thutan na mun a thudih kimu ding chuleh michonpha ho jousen apanhu diu ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Gitlou na akon a koiham eidal ding? Miphalou ho masang a ei din peh ding koi ham?
\p 
\v 17 Yahweh Pakaiyin eina kithopi lou hile, keima thina lhankhuh mun a thipchet a ana kicholdo tading kahi.
\p 
\v 18 “Keima kalhutai” tin kakap jah in, O Yahweh Pakai nami ngailutna longlou chun eiphong dingin ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Keima lungdon na a kadim teng, nami lungmon nachun kinep na le kipa na eipe ji e.
\p 
\v 20 Dandih lou a natong lamkai ho chun Yahweh Pakai kalang a pangding hi ati ngam nadiu vem?
\p 
\v 21 Themmo nabei ho dou din amaho akipun khom un mona neilou chungah thina chan in athepmo sah uve.
\p 
\v 22 Ahin Yahweh Pakai, ka Pathen Pathen hi kakisel na songpi kakulpi chu ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Pathen Pathen'in migiloute achonset nau chu ale thuh ding ahi. Achonset nau jeh a asuh gam ding ahi. Yahweh Pakai, I-Pathen'uvin asuh gam ding u ahi.
\c 95
\s1 Pathen Pathen Vahchoi Dia Nagilut Kouna
\p 
\v 1 Hungun, Yahweh Pakai vahchoiyu te! Eihuhdoh uva Pathen Pathen ah kipah tah in vahchoila sau te!
\p 
\v 2 Thangvah pum in a angsung jon u hite. Avahchoina la sau te.
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai chu loupitah Pathen Pathen ahin, pathen dang chung a leng loupi ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Mollen penle leiset laigil athuhlai abon'a Aman akhut a atuhchah ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Twikhanglen hi Ama a ahi, ajeh chu Ama sem ahi. Ama khut in leigo jonghi asem ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Hungun, eisempau Yahweh Pakai angsung'ah dilsu-u hitin amahou u te,
\p 
\v 7 ajeh chu Ama I-Pathen'u ahin, eiho hi aman achinjing amite ihiuvin akaihoijing akelngoihon ihiuve.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaiyin asei e, “Israel ten gamthipnoi masah a abol bangu leh Meribah a alungtah bang bangun nalung tahsah hih'un.
\p 
\v 9 Ajeh chu hilai munna chun napu napa teu vin kathilbol ho chengse hi amu uvin chule eipatep'un ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Kum somli sunga hin keima achung uva kana lunghang'in chuleh Keiman kasei in ahi, ‘amaho hi keija kon a kinung heidoh mipi chu ahiuvin, keiman kasei dungjui a chon nomlou ahiuve.’
\p 
\v 11 Hijeh chun kalunghan jehin kana kihahsel'in: ‘amaho hi kachol ngahna munna hunglut thei louhel diu ahi!’”
\c 96
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Din Lathah La Sauvin
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai kom'ah lathah sauvin! Leiset pumpin Yahweh Pakai vahchoila sauvin!
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakai vahchoila sauvin amin thangvah un. Ami huhhingna kipa umtah chu niseh'in samphongin.
\p 
\v 3 Chitin namtin holah a athilbol kidangtah ho hi samphong'in, Aman thil loupi tahtah abol ho hi mijouse seipeh'un.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai hi aloupi e! Ama hi vahchoi dinga lompen ahi! Ama hi pathen jouse sanga kichat umpentah ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Chidang namdang ho pathen ho hi semthu pathen ngen ahiuve hinla Yahweh Pakai hin vanho asem ahi!
\p 
\v 6 Gin na le jana-in aumkimvel ahi, thahatna le mel-hoina hin muntheng alosoh ahi.
\p 
\v 7 O chitin namtin vannoi mite ho, Yahweh Pakai hethem un Yahweh Pakai ahat na le aloupina ho hi hethem un.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai chu achan dinga lomtah loupi na le jana chan sah'un! Nathilpeh ding kichoiyin lang a-angsunga lut in.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai chu athenna loupina vah chutoh kitohin chibai boh'un. Vannoi leiset pumpi hi a-angsung'ah kithing jenghen.
\p 
\v 10 Chitin namtin hi seipeh un, “Yahweh Pakaiyin vai ahom e!” Vannoi hi adingdetna ahitan holingbut ahitapon ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Vanho kipah hen chuleh vannoi leiset kipah-u hen! Twikhanglen leh asunga um jousen thangvah'un.
\p 
\v 12 Loujao ho leh asunga kehho jouse jong kipahtah in hung gadoh sohkei uhen, gammangsunga thingphungho jousen jong
\p 
\v 13 Yahweh Pakai angsung'ah thangvah la sauhen, ajeh chu Ama ahungtai! Leiset chungthu tan dingin ahunge. Aman vannoi mite le chitin namtinhi kitahna-a achungthu atan ding ahi.
\c 97
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Thaneina Le Alengvaipoh
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai hi leng ahi! Vannoi mite kipah hen! Twikhanglen akimvelle agamla penna um miho jong kipah uhen.
\p 
\v 2 Ama hi meilhang thim in atomin, chonphatna le thudih chu alaltouna khombul ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Amasang ah meikong aleng'in akidoupi ho ahallih gamin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Akolphe vah in vannoi leiset asalvah'in ahi. Leiset in amun akithing thingin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Molle lhangjong Yahweh Pakai masanga khoilu bangin ajunlha jengin ahi. Leiset pumpi Yahweh Pakai masanga hitia hi thilsoh -a ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Vanhon adih na le akitahna aphongdoh'in namtin'in aloupina amu'uvin ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Milimsemthu doihou ho jouse, panna bei semthu pathen kiletsahpi hojouse jumle jachat athoh'un ahi, ajeh chu semthu pathen hojouse a-anga kun teidiu ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Jerusalem in ajauvin akipah un chuleh Judah khopiho jouse jong athanom'un ahi. Ajeh chu O Yahweh Pakai nangma thudih nahi.
\p 
\v 9 Nangma hi O Yahweh Pakai vannoi leisetna athupipen nahin, semthu pathen ho jouse chunga dopsang'in naumin ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Nangho Yahweh Pakai ngailuhon thilse nahot bollun ahi. Aman ami chonphate ahinkho-u ahuhdohjin ahi, chuleh miphalouho thaneina a kon'in ahuhdohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Michonpha ho vah-in asalvah'in, chuleh milungdih ho akipah jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Koi hileh michonpha ho jouse kipah henlang amintheng chu thangvah'u hen!
\c 98
\s1 Pathen Pathen Adihna Vahchoina
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai ah lathah sauvin, ajeh chu Aman thil kidangtah tah aboldoh tai. Aban jet in gal nasatah ajou tai; Aban thengin huhhingna thahat amusah e.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakaiyin galjona aphongdoh tai, chuleh adihna leh akitahna chitin namtin lah a aphongjal tai.
\p 
\v 3 Aman Israel te dinga ngailutna le kitahna nei a akitep nachu ageldoh'in ahi. Leiset kolmang gei in jong I-Pathen'u Pathen galjona hi amudoh tauve.
\p 
\v 4 Leiset mihemten Yahweh Pakai ah kho sam'un; thangvahna bunglhauvin kipah tah in thangvah la sauvin!
\p 
\v 5 Tumging toh thon Yahweh Pakai vahchoi la sauvin, tumging tothon langai chu sauvin.
\p 
\v 6 Sumkon toh kelngoi ki gin kithong tohthon iPakai u Yahweh le ilengpau masanga chohjejun la sauvin.
\p 
\v 7 Twikhanglen leh asunga um jousen athangvahna samphongun! Leiset chunga hinna nei jousen jom un.
\p 
\v 8 Vadung jousen kipah'in akhut beng uhen! Thinglhang gam jousen kipah'in la sauhen,
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai masangah. Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai chu leiset chung thu tandinga hung ding ahi. Vannoi hi thudih a athu atan ding chitin namtin thu hi dihtah a atan ding ahi.
\c 99
\s1 Zion Dinga Yahweh Pakai Kitahna
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai hi leng ahi! Chitin namtin kithing thingjeng hen! Ama Cherub teni kikah a laltouna a atouvin ahi. Vannoi leiset pumpi kithing hen.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakai chu Jerusalem ah loupitah in atouvin ahi. Chitin namtin ho jouse chung vum a dopsang'in aum'e.
\p 
\v 3 ama hon namin gimneitah chu thangvah uhen, naminhi athenge!
\p 
\v 4 Lengloupi thudih ngailua, nangin thildih hi nadomsang'in, thudih in kal nasong'in Israel lah-a thudih nachelhah sah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai I-Pathen'u Pathen hi dopsangin umhen! A-angsung'ah bohkhup un, ajeh chu Ama hi atheng ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Mose le Aaron jongchu thempu ahilhon e, Samuel injong Amin anakouve. Ama hon Yahweh Pakai kom'ah panpi ngaichan anakouvun ahi, chuleh Aman anahouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Aman meilom lah a kon'in Israel ho lah-a thu anasei in, ama hon Yahweh Pakaiyin apeh-u Dan le thupeh ho chu anajui un ahi.
\p 
\v 8 O Yahweh Pakai ka Pathen'u Pathen! nangin amaho nana donbut in ahi. Nangma hi amaho ding a mi ngaidam jing Pathen Pathen nahi, ahinla amaho achekhel tengu leh nagim boljin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai, I-Pathen'u Pathen hi domsang'un chuleh Jerusalem a moltheng achun chibai boh'un ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai, I-Pathen'u Pathen hi atheng ahi.
\c 100
\s1 Thangvahna Le Tikhouna La
\s1 Thangvah na la
\p 
\v 1 Leiset pumpin Yahweh Pakai a kipana samphong'un,
\p 
\v 2 kipah tah in Yahweh Pakai chu chibai boh'un vahchoila sapum pumin a-angah hungun
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakai, Pathen Pathen ahi tin hettohna phongdohun, Aman eisem uva eiho Ama a ihiu ahi. Eiho Ama mite ihiu vin a-an a kivah akelngoite ihiuve.
\p 
\v 4 Thangvah pum in akulpi sungah lut un, vahchoi pum in a insungah lut in, Akom'a kipa thu sei un, amin thangvah'un.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai phatna jehchun, ami ngailutna longlou hi tonsot in aum jinge, chuleh akitah nahi akhang khangin aum jinge
\c 101
\s1 Lamdih'a Hinkho Manna Dia David Taona
\s1 David labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai keiman nami ngailutna le nathudihna lan sange. Keiman nangma thangvah nahi lan sange.
\p 
\v 2 Keiman monabei hinkho kaman theina dingin chingthei tah in um inge, itihleh eipanpi dinga nahung ding hitam? Keiman ka insungah kitahna hinkho kaman jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Keiman ipi hijongleh athenglou chuleh vet hoilou ho veponge. Thil adihlouva kitongho jouse kathet ahi, hichengse hitoh kakitimat louhel ding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Keiman dei umlou thil ho jouse hi kapaidoh sohkei ding thilgilou hojousea kon a kakidalse ding ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Aheng akom aseiseho jouse kadeplouhel ding ahi. Keiman akiphatsei leh akiletsah ho kadeplou ding ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Keiman tahsan um miho kaholdoh ding amaho chu kakivoppi ding ahi. Koi hileh oimothei hilou miho bouchu kakivoppi ding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Keiman milepche ho ka insunga kamanchah louding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Aniseh a katoh ding chu mi jonchih ho deldohding chuleh khopi hi hitiho tobanga konna hoidoh sahding hi kakin ahi.
\c 102
\s1 Gim Le Hesoh Pet'a Taona
\s1 Boina hahsat nan atom mikhat in taona a Pathen Pathen heng alhut
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai kataona ngai in! Ka ngeh nahi neisanpeh in.
\p 
\v 2 Kei a kon'in kiheimang hih'in, kahahsat phatleh khohsah tah in neingaipeh in, kangaichat phatleh neihin gelkhoh in,
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu kahinkho hi meikhu bangin abeipai jitai, kagu kachang hi asadohji tai.
\p 
\v 4 Kalungsung hi anadohjin hamhing bangin agolha jitai, chutengleh chun kagilkel jong abeipaiji tai.
\p 
\v 5 Ajeh chu lunggim a kakhoisat sat jeh'in kavun le kagu hobou kahitai.
\p 
\v 6 Keima neldi gam a sumbupi toh kabangtai, gamla tah gamthip gam a sumbupi noutoh kabangtai.
\p 
\v 7 Keima kahah khovahjin, inting vumma vacha changkhat seh lunghel tah-a um kabange.
\p 
\v 8 Kagal miten sun nilhum in eitaitom jingun, ama hon eisamseuvin eitaitom jingun ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Keima buneh jong vutvai jeng ahitai. Kadon na sunga jong kamitlhi alonglut tai.
\p 
\v 10 Nalunghan na le nagimbol nachun eidom sang'in eipaidoh tai.
\p 
\v 11 Kahinkho hi nilhah lang nilep bangin achemang loijitai. Keima hampa bangin kagop lhaloi jitai.
\p 
\v 12 Ahinla Yahweh Pakai nangvang nalaltouna a natoujing ding ahi. Naminthan na akhang khanga chelhajing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Nangma hung kipat in natin Jerusalem hi nahin khoto ding ahi. Tua hi nangnam na khohsah phat ahin, tuhi na kitepna dungjui a mi kithopi phat ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Ajeh chu namiten bang'a song jouse angailu uvin chuleh lamlenna vutvai hojeng jong angaisang'un ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Chujou tengleh chitin namtin ten Yahweh Pakai ang-a kithing thingding ahi,
\p 
\v 16 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin Jerusalem ahin thahsem kitding chutengleh Ama aloupina-a hung kilang ding,
\p 
\v 17 Aman tahlelte taona ahin sanding Aman angaichat hou asanpehding ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Khonunga khangthahho dinga kijihlut pehding hitiachu tua pengloulai hon Yahweh Pakai chu ahin thangvah dingu ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Yahweh Pakaiyin van muntheng a kon a ahin vetsuh ding, Aman van a kon a leiset hi ahin vetsuh ding
\p 
\v 20 songkul tangte khoisatna ajahding thi dinga themmo kichanho alha doh dinga,
\p 
\v 21 hiteng chuleh Yahweh Pakai minthanna chu Zion a lopna um ding, chule Jerusalem a kithangvah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Mihonpi tamtah chu ahung ki khopkhom tengleh lenggam hojouse chu Yahweh Pakai chibai boh a hungdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Aman kaban thahat akim laitah avolhun kahinkho asuchomtai.
\p 
\v 24 Hinla keiman Ama kakouvin, Oh Yahweh Pakai tonsot a hingjing kakhandon laitah ahin kahinkho lahih'in.
\p 
\v 25 Kum tamtah achetai, nangin hiche leiset leibul nana lhungdoh'in, vanho hi nakhut tah in nanasemdoh in,
\p 
\v 26 hihojouse hung mangthah ding ahinlah nang tonsotna nahinjing ding ahi, amaho ponlui bangin hungvui lhantin, Nangin amaho chu von banga nakhel ding chujou teng napai mangdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 27 Hinla Yahweh Pakai nangvang abang chu nahijingin ahi.
\p 
\v 28 Nangma mite chate jouse lungmong a umdiu ahi. Achate chate ho chu na-anga hung khanglen diu ahi.
\c 103
\s1 Yahweh Pakaiya Kon Phatchomna Jeh a David In Avahchoi
\s1 David labol
\p 
\v 1 Kahinaho jouse pum'in Yahweh Pakai chu thagvah ingkate. Kalungthim pumpin amintheng choian inge.
\p 
\v 2 Kahinaho jouse pum'in Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah ingkate. Keidinga thilpha eibolpeh ho itihchan hijongleh sumil ponge.
\p 
\v 3 Aman kachonsetna jouse angaidam tai, chuleh kadam mona hojouse le kahivei hojouse eiboldam pehtai.
\p 
\v 4 Aman kathina dinga kon'in eihuhdohtai chuleh ngailutna leh khotona dimset in eiphungvuh tai.
\p 
\v 5 Aman kahinkho hi thilpha dimset in eiphungvuh tai, Muvanlai bangin kakhandon hinkho akiledohsah tai!
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakaiyin chonphatna leh dihna chu suhgenthei a umte chu amusah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Aman ahina tahbeh chu Mose kom'ah anatahlang'in chuleh anatoh ho chu Israel mipite lah-a ana phongdoh 'in ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai hi mikhoto them tah leh mihepi themtah lunghang vahlou chuleh longlou ngailutna a dimset ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Ama hin phat tinnin eithepmosah pouvin tin ahilouleh lunghang jingjeng ponte.
\p 
\v 10 Aman ichonset nauva jong ei engbol pouvin tin chuleh Aman eiho chan ding dol hotbolna jong einei pouvinte.
\p 
\v 11 Ama gingte chunga angailutna tanglou hi leiset chunga van asan banga hi sanga ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Aman eiho chonset nahi, solam le lhumlam akigamlat bangin gamla tah in atolmang tai.
\p 
\v 13 Yahweh Pakai hi chapangte dinga apauva panga ahin, ama gingte dinga khoto them tah le ngailutna dimset ahijing e.
\p 
\v 14 Ajeh chu Aman ihatmonau eihet thempeh'un chuleh eiho hi vutvai tobang bou ihiu ageldoh jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Leiset chunga ihinkho hou jong hampa bangbep ahin, gam pahcha tobangin ipahdoh'un athi loikitji tai.
\p 
\v 16 Hui ahung nung jin a-itih a aumkhlou banginbep in eimut mang ji taove.
\p 
\v 17 Hinla Yahweh Pakai gingte din vang ami ngailutna nitin in aum jinge. Ami huhhing nanjong achate chate ho gei in,
\p 
\v 18 hitobanga aDan thua kitahna nei ho le, athupeh jui jing ho din aumpeh jing e.
\p 
\v 19 Yahweh Pakaiyin vanmun ho hi alaltouna in asemin; hichea kon'in muntin chunga vai ahom e.
\p 
\v 20 Nangho vantil te ho, nangho mithupitahte ho, ana tongdoh a pangho Yahweh Pakai hi thangvah un.
\p 
\v 21 Ahi, nangho vantil sepaite ho alungdeilam boljinga Ama janlea pangjing ho Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un.
\p 
\v 22 Asemsa ho jousen, chuleh alengam a um jouse n Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un. Keima kahina jouse pum in Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah jinging kate.
\c 104
\s1 Yahweh Pakaiyin Athilsemsa Khohsahna Anei
\p 
\v 1 Kahina jouse pum in Yahweh Pakai thangvah inge. O Yahweh Pakai, ka Pathen Pathen, iti lom a nathupi hitam! Nangma, naloupina le nathupina toh nakivon e.
\p 
\v 2 Nangman khovah chu ponsil bangin nakisil in, Nangin vanho ahin ahsi ho hi pondal bangin nadahdoh in;
\p 
\v 3 twimei chunga na iin natungdoh in, meilom chu sakol kangtalai in namangin, huihi nalhavingin namangin na lenglen ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Huihi sottol len namangin, meile meikong jong nasoh'in namangin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Nangin, itihchan hijongleh kil ling louhel dingin nangman vannoi leiset bul naphutdoh tai.
\p 
\v 6 Nangin twipi veihi leiset dingin ponsil in nasilpeh'in molsangho jong nachupsah soh hel in ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Nangin thu napehleh twipi chu alengmang jingin, na ogin ajahleh ajammang hel jenge.
\p 
\v 8 Mol ho adingdoh in phaicham atonglha jengin nangin nathupeh bang bangin akijam jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Chujouvin nangin twikhanglen ho chu aphah nadiu chanbep naphahsah'in, hitiachu leiset hi avel'a achupkit louna diuvin nasemtoh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Nangin twisamho naphuldoh sah'in kotong dunga nalonlutsah'in, vachaho chu molle lhanga kon'in ahung lengsuh'in,
\p 
\v 11 ganhingho jouse dingin twi na suhmang peh'in ahi, chuleh sangan honjong dangnou nan anei un ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Vacha hon va pang dunga buh akisem un thingbah lah a la asajiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Nangin navan inmun a kon'in molle lhang chunga go nahinjuhsah in chuteng nakhutsoh gachun leiset nasudimjin ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Nangin hampa ho nakhandohsah in ganchaho, thingphungho le mihemho manchah pha nasodoh sah'in ahi. Chujongleh nangman leiset chunga amaho dingin nehpha nasodohsah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Akipana diuvin adondiu lengpitwi nagonpeh in atahsauva akinu diuvin Olive thao nasosah'in, chule athaneina diuva neh ding changlhah napen ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Yahweh Pakaiyin athingphung ho hi phatah in akhoukhah in, Lebanon ah Cedar thingphung ho akedohsah'in,
\p 
\v 17 hichea chun vachaten abu-u akison un chuleh vakang ten Cypress thing chunga inn akise un ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Molsang chungvum langa gamlah kelho achengun chuleh songpi ho chu kollah saho dingin na phatah in apangin ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Nangin lha nasemmin kum kiheichin aphongdoh e, chule nisan alhum ding phatjong akihetne.
\p 
\v 20 Nangin janjong nasemin, jan ahunglhung jin ahi, gammang ganchaho anunkho jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Keipi nouhon amatdiu ho chu angihjiuvin, Pathen Pathen'in apeh'u amaho anchah ho chu matdingin agemjiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Jingpitah leh abusung uva kicholdo dingin anungche jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Hichejou tengleh chun mipi ho chu ama ama natohna dingcheh ajon un hicheachun nilhah gei in na atong ji tao ve.
\p 
\v 24 O Yahweh Pakai nangin thilho hi jatchom chom in nasem jinge! Nachihna a hiche ho hi nasemdoh ahije. Leiset hi nathilsemsa ho adimset e.
\p 
\v 25 Hiti chun twikhanglen lentah leh kiphahjal tah nasemin, asunga ganhing achatthei alen aneo nasemin ahi.
\p 
\v 26 Ven, kong inneiho akitol un, Leviathan jong twikhanglen'a kichem din nasem e.
\p 
\v 27 Amaho jousen angaichat'u an amun'adiu hi ngang chunga kingaicheh ahiuve.
\p 
\v 28 Anehdiu nangin napehtengu leh ama hon achomkhom jiuvin nangin nakhut a nalhangdoh in namop jin hiti chun amaho lungna chimset'in navah jin ahi.
\p 
\v 29 Ahinla Nang, amahoa konna nakinunghei tengleh amaho kichadiu ahi. Nangin ahinna hu'u nalahdoh tengleh amaho thi ding vutvai soh ding ahi tauve.
\p 
\v 30 Nangin nahu napeh tengleh hinna nasemdohji a, hiteng chuleh leiset maihi akithahsem kitjin ahi.
\p 
\v 31 Yahweh Pakai loupina hi tonsotnin um jing jenghen. Yahweh Pakaiyin athilsem jousea hin kipana aneiyin ahi.
\p 
\v 32 Leiset hi avetleh akithing jengin molho jonghi akhoi khahleh meikhu alengdoh jengjin ahi.
\p 
\v 33 Hinkho kanei laisen Yahweh Pakai vahchoi la sange, kahai hu bei chan geijin jong ka Pathen Pathen thangvah ingkate.
\p 
\v 34 Kalunggel ngaito jouse jonghi Ama lunglhaina hihen, ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai hi kakipana ahi.
\p 
\v 35 Hiche leisetna konhin michonsete jouse mangthah gam jengu hen, miphalou ho jouse mangthah jengu hen. Kahina ho jouse pummin Yahweh Pakai thangvah ingkate, Yahweh Pakai loupina ding hitahen!
\c 105
\s1 Pathen Pathen Melchihna Kidang Umna Ding Angeh
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai kom'a kipathu sei in aloupina samphong'un. Vannoi leiset mihemte jousen ipi abol ham heuhen,
\p 
\v 2 Aheng a la sauvin; henge avahchoila saovin. Athilbol kidang ho hi mijouse seipeh'un,
\p 
\v 3 Amintheng hi domsang'un, nangho Yahweh Pakai chibai bohte jouse kipah'un,
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai athahatna chu kholchil in phattin'in ama chu hol'un,
\p 
\v 5 datmo umtah tah atohdoh ho chuleh thilkidang abol ho, athupeh eipeh hou,
\p 
\v 6 nangho asoh Abraham chate ho, Jacob chilhah ho alhendoh sate ho, geldoh'un.
\p 
\v 7 Ama hi Yahweh Pakai, I-Pathen'u Pathen ahin, Ama thudih nahi gamsung jousea akimudoh sohkeijin
\p 
\v 8 Ama hi akitepna itihchan hijongleh dingjing ahin, khang sangkhat dinga ana kipehdoh na,
\p 
\v 9 Abraham toh anasem kitepna chuleh Issac kom'a ana kihahselna,
\p 
\v 10 Aman Jacob kom'ah Dan khat apen anasuhdet in, chuleh Israel mipite dinga beithei lou kitepna ana sem in:
\p 
\v 11 “Keiman Canaan gam kapehding nahi, nang dinga jatchombeh a kapeh natouphadiu gamchu ahi” anati.
\p 
\v 12 Aman hiche hi hon lhomcha ahipet'uva, Canaan gama kholjin hon lhomcha ahipet uva anasei ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Amaho namkhat a kon a namkhat, lenggam khatna konna lenggam khat a akholjin pet'uva asei ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Aman koimacha anasuh genthei sahpon ahi. Aman amaho huhnan namdang lengho chu anagih'in ahi.
\p 
\v 15 “Kami lhentum ho chu tongkha hih'un, chuleh kathemgao ho jong tongkhahih'un,” anati.
\p 
\v 16 Aman nehle chah ho chu akhahtan'in Canaan gamah kel analhahsah'in ahi,
\p 
\v 17 hiti chun amaho masanga Egypt gam'achun mikhat anasol masan ahi, amaho soh a anajoh Joseph chu ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Ama chu akengphang tenia thihkhao avouvin, angongchang'a thihkol a-opeh uve.
\p 
\v 19 Amang lolhinna dinga thil ahung sodoh tokah'in Yahweh Pakaiyin Joseph chu ahina tahbeh hetdohna dingin ana patepmin ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Hichejou chun Pharaoh in ama chu agakousah'in alhadohtai; Gamsung vaipopan songkul kotchu ahonpeh tai.
\p 
\v 21 Joseph chu lengpa insunga thil jouse chunga vaihom dingin apansahtan ahi. Hiti chun lengpa thil ho jouse chungah vaipon ahung pangtai.
\p 
\v 22 Hiti chun aman adei bang tah in lengpa noi a vaihom pipuiho chu avaihop in chule lengpa thumop lea pang ho chu ahil ji tai.
\p 
\v 23 Hi jouchun Israel chu Egypt gam alhungtan, Jacob chu Ham gamsunga chun gamchom mi hinan ana chengtan ahi.
\p 
\v 24 Yahweh Pakaiyin Israel mipite chu hapun'in apunsah tan hiti chun agalmite diuvin kichat aumleu tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 25 Hichun Egypt te chu Israel te vetda dingin atildoh tan hijeh chun Yahweh Pakai mite dounan tohgon aneitauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 26 Ahin Pathen Pathen nin asoh Mose chu ahinsol'in aman ana lhendoh Aaron chutoh asolthan ahi.
\p 
\v 27 Amanin Egypt mite dounan melchihna kidangtah chuleh datmo umtah tah Ham gamsunga anatongdoh lhonnin ahi.
\p 
\v 28 Yahweh Pakaiyin Egypt chu mu anathimsah tan ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon Yahweh Pakai thupeh Israel te soldoh dingchu ananom pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 29 Aman twi thisan anasosah'in, ngaho dingin thina thei gu ahitan ahi.
\p 
\v 30 Uphoh honjong agamsung'u alonvuh jengin lengpa lupna dansang jenga jong alhailut jengun ahi.
\p 
\v 31 Yahweh Pakaiyin thu aseileh thousiho Egypt mite chunga ahung chu'uvin, Egypt gam pumpi thousi vaibong'in alo jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 32 Aman go khel in gel anajuhsah'in, keh in agamsung'u anasepchap jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 33 Aman alengpithei uleh atheichang ujong asuhmangpeh'in athingphung houjong asatchap jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 34 Aman thu aseileh khaokhote ahung kitollutnun khaokho noute jong simsenlou ahung kitollut tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 35 ama hon gamsunga ado eng jouse anechai jengun, loulai a anche louhing jouse jong achaidoh jengun ahi.
\p 
\v 36 Hiche jouchun Aman Egypt te insung jousea chapa tahpen ho aban thapeh'in ahi. Hiti chun aki letsah pipen ule aki panapen hou asuhbei peh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 37 Yahweh Pakaiyin amite chu sana le dangka dimset pum in Egypt'a kon'in ahin puidoh'in, Israel phungho lah a khat chajong akipallhua aumpouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 38 Egypt miten nana kichat behseh jeh un apotdoh uchu ana kipapi lheh jengun ahi.
\p 
\v 39 Yahweh Pakaiyin sun leh meilom akhu khum sah'in janleh meikong in asalvah peh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 40 ama hon sa athum uleh vamim alhalutpeh'in a-oivan'a diuvin van changlhah mama chu anapen ahi.
\p 
\v 41 Aman songpi chu ahomsah'in twi ahung kiphidoh sah'in gamchai lah a vadung bangin alondonsah'un ahi.
\p 
\v 42 Ajeh chu Aman asohpa Abraham kom'a akitepna atheng chu ageldoh'in,
\p 
\v 43 hijeh chun amite Egypt'a kon'in amilhendoh chu kipah tah in ahin puidoh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 44 Aman gamsung mite Pathen Pathen helou chitin namtinte chenna chu alahpeh'in Ama mite ho chu apen, hiti chun ama hon mi tusa chang ga ho chu aki-at'un ahi.
\p 
\v 45 Hitiho jouse anachelhah sahchu ama hon a Dan thupeh leh athuhil ho dungjui a achon nadiu adeijeh ahi. Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen!
\c 106
\s1 Israel Lungheiya Kisih Chule Pathen Pathen Avahchoi
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen! Pathen Pathen chu aphatna jeh'in thangvahna peuvin.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakaiyin thil loupi kidangtah atohdoh ho hi kon asim jou ding ham? Kon Ama hi ahina bangtah in athangvah joudem?
\p 
\v 3 Mi ahina bangtah a pachatna pethei ho leh phat tin a adih jeng bol hon kipana anei thei jengun ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai nangin namite khotona namusah tengleh neihin geldoh'in lang neihin nai in neihuhdoh'in.
\p 
\v 5 Nalhendoh namite phatthei naboh nahoa keijong chan neineisah'in. Namite kipana a keijong neikipa sah'in. Nagou chang toh nangma thangvah khom kanom e.
\p 
\v 6 Kapu kapateu bangin keiho jong kachonse tauve, keihon kabolkhel tauve, keiho phaloutah in kanachon tauve,
\p 
\v 7 Egypt gam a ana um kapu kapateu chu Yahweh Pakaiyin thil kidang aboldoh ho chun atilkhou pouve. Ama hon ading uva Yahweh Pakai phatna ho chu ana sumil loiji tauve. Ama hon Twipi San mun nachun Yahweh Pakai dounan ahung phunchel tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Achuti jeng vangun, Amin loupi dopsangna ding leh athaneina thupitah chu akilandohna dingin amaho chu ana huhdoh thouthou jin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Aman Twipi Sanchu akan-na dingin thu apen, Aman twikhanglen chu neldigam abahsah'in Israel te chu ahinpui galkai in ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Hiti chun agalmiteuva kon'in anahuhdoh jin, chuleh akidoupihoa kon'in ana hoidohsah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Twichu akinung ledoh sah'in agalmiteu akhukhum jin khatcha jong anahingdoh pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Hitengleh chun amiten akitepna chu atahsan jiuvin Ama vahchoina la chu asajiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Ahinla Yahweh Pakaiyin abolpeh houchu gangtah in asumilji tauvin, Ama thuhil angahji pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Gamthip noi achun amaho tahsa ngaichat thilngen anathum'un hiche gamchai lah a chun Pathen Pathen chu anapatep'un,
\p 
\v 15 hijeh chun Aman angaichat'u chu anapen ahinlah nat na toh apehthan ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Camp sunga umho chu Mose chungah athangthipmun chuleh Yahweh Pakai thempu theng Aaron a-ot'un ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Hiche jeh chun leiset chu ahung kamkan, Dathan, Abiram leh akiphinho jouse chu anavallhum'in avuimangtan ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Anungjui ho chungah meikong achun miphalou ho jouse chu meikong'in ahalgam tan ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Sinai mol'a sana a kisem bongnou chu chibai aboh'un,
\p 
\v 20 Loupitah Pathen Pathen chu hampane bonglim toh analheh tauve.
\p 
\v 21 ama hon ahuhingpau, Egypt gam'a konna ahinpuidoh pau,
\p 
\v 22 Ham gamsunga thil kidang tamtah ahin boldohpeh pau, Twipi San na gimneitah thil ana tongdohpa a Pathen'u Pathen chu anasumil tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Hijeh chun Aman ka suhmang ding ahi tin ana phongdoh tan ahi. Ahinlah Mose, lhendoh mipa chu Yahweh Pakai leh amipite kikah a anadingtan, aman Yahweh Pakai kom'a chun alunghanna'a konna kile heija amipite chu asuhmang louna dingin ataotai.
\p 
\v 24 Mipite chu gam nom lutding chu ana nom tapouvin ahi, ajeh chu Pathen Pathen'in ana kitepna banga apuihoi dingchu ana nom tapouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 25 Ajeh chu akaleh langin achon un, aponbuh sung uvah ana phunchel gam un, Yahweh Pakai thu anangainom pouvin,
\p 
\v 26 hijeh chun Yahweh Pakai chu lunghemtah in ana kihahsel'in amaho hi hiche gamthip noi a kathagam ding ahiuve anatitai.
\p 
\v 27 Chutengleh ason apahteu chu chitin namtin lah a kathejal soh ding, chuleh gamla tah tah a kaimang'a umdiu ahi ati.
\p 
\v 28 Hiti chun, ipu apateu chu Baal leh Peor chibai bohna a anapang'un, mithi dinga kitodoh sa jeng jong ananeuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 29 Hitiho jehhin ama hon Yahweh Pakai chu ana sulang hangun hijeh chun alah uva natset analangtan ahi.
\p 
\v 30 Ahinla Phenehas kitipa chun hangsantah in nat se chu ana tingtan'in ahileh natset chu atangtai.
\p 
\v 31 Hijeh chun hichea patchun michonpha tin jana anapetauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 32 Meribah-a jong Yahweh Pakai chu ana lunghansah'un hichun Mose chu anasuboi lheh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 33 ama hon Mose chu analunghan sah'un ahileh amanngolkaitah in thu anaseilo tan ahi
\p 
\v 34 Israel ten chidang namdang ho chu Yahweh Pakaiyin thu anapeh dungjuijin anasohjou pouvin,
\p 
\v 35 hichu hilouvin agamsung mite lah a chun ana chenghal un achonna o phaloutah ho chu ana joptauvin,
\p 
\v 36 amilim doi houvu chu anahou un hichun alhuhnao asodohsahtan ahi.
\p 
\v 37 ama hon achateu kisan chu anatodoh'un chuleh achanuteu jeng jong thillha hounan anapedoh'un,
\p 
\v 38 ama hon themmona neilou thisan anasouvin, achapa teu leh achanuteu thisan chu Canaan mite doi hounan anamang'un tolthanan gamsung chu anasuboh'un,
\p 
\v 39 amaho leh amaho jong thilgilou bolnan anakisuboh'un adoihou thanopnau chu Yahweh Pakai mitmun jonthanhoi ana hidohtan ahi.
\p 
\v 40 Hiche jeh chun Yahweh Pakai lunghanna chu amite chungah anakoudoh jengin ahileh Yahweh Pakaiyin ama-a tum ho chu ana kidah lotan ahi.
\p 
\v 41 Hijeh chun Yahweh Pakaiyin amaho chu agamsung nammite lah a chun ana pedoh'in chuleh athet nammiteu chun amaho chungah vai anahomji tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 42 Agalmi houchun asugep jiuvin chuleh abolgimnao khut thahatna noi a anakoiji tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 43 Avel vellin Aman ahuhdohjin, ahinlah ama hon Ama dounan akipedohji tauvin ahi, chutengleh amaho chu achonset jeh un suhmangin aumji tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 44 Ahijeng vangin ahahsat tengu leh Aman akhotokit jiuvin akanao angaipeh kitjitan ahi.
\p 
\v 45 Aman amaho toh akitepnao ahin geldoh kitji in angailutna chultheilou jeh in alung ahinhei kitji in,
\p 
\v 46 Aman ganhing a amanteu khutnah khotona amusah kitji nalaijin ahi.
\p 
\v 47 O Yahweh Pakai, ka Pathen'u Pathen neihuhdoh'un! Chitin namtin lah a konhin neichomkhom kitnun hitiachu namintheng ka thangvah theina diuvin chuleh kipah a nangma ka thangvah theina diuvin.
\p 
\v 48 Israel Pathen Pathen, Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un, Ama hi tonsot a pat tonsot geija hingjing Pathen Pathen ahi! Mi jousen “Amen” tiuhen. Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen!
\c 107
\s1 BU NGANA
\s1 Gentheina Kona Yahweh Pakai Mihuhdohna
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai hi aphatjeh'in thangvahna peuvin, Ami ngailutna dihtah hi tonsot a dettou jing ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakaiyin nalhatdoh hitam? Achutileh phongdoh'in! Aman namelma holah a kon a nahoidohsahhi miho seipeh'in.
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu Aman gam tamtah a kon'in solamle lhumlam'a kon'in, sahlam le lhanglam a kon'in sohchangho ahin puikhom'in ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Miloi khat hi gamthip gam mah avah mang'un, in le lou beijin avah mang'un,
\p 
\v 5 Gilkil leh dangchah geovin a thi ding konchan aum mun,
\p 
\v 6 “Yahweh Pakai neipanpin” tin ahahsat nauva Pakai Yahweh akouvun, chuteng Aman agenthei nauva kon'in ahuhdoh jin ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Aman amaho chu bitkei chan apuijin achenna theiju khopi khatna akoiyin ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai chu angailutna thupi tah jehleh thil kidangtahtah abolpeh jeh un thangvahna peuhen.
\p 
\v 9 Ajeh chu Aman adangchah ho adangnou sah'in, agilkil'ho thilpha tamtah tothon a-oiva sahjin ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Miloikhat muthim lah athimlah pen a atouvin, lung gimna thihkhao vin ahen oh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Amaho Pathen Pathen thu dounan akiphin un, Pathen Pathen thumop chu anelpeh'un ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Hijeh chun Aman amaho chu akhut hamtah in avo lhun, amaho alhuh phatnun koima akithopidiu aumpon ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Ahahsat tengu leh Yahweh Pakai akoujiuvin “Yahweh Pakai neipanpin” atiuve. Hitengleh chun Aman athohgim nauva kon'in ahuhdohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Aman amaho chu muthimleh ahahsat nau thimjin banga thimlah a kon'in apui galkaijin akihennao asutlhappeh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Yahweh Pakai chu ami ngailutna thupitah jehleh thil kidangtah tah abolpeh jeh'in thangvah uhen,
\p 
\v 16 ajeh chu Aman sum-eng songkul kotpi avohlhahpeh'in chuleh akihennao thihkhao avohtan pehtan ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Mingol themkhat chun boina asemuvin achonset jeh un thohgimna atoh'un ahi.
\p 
\v 18 An le twi ngaichatnan athohlel lheh'un hiti chun amaho chu athi ding kon ahiuve.
\p 
\v 19 “Yahweh Pakai neikithopin” tin ahahsat tengu leh Yahweh Pakai akoujiuvin Aman athohgim nauva kon'in ahuhdohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Aman thu changkhat agahseijin aboldamjin, thina kotbul a kon'in aloidohtan ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Ami lungsetna thupi tah jehleh amaho dinga thil kidang tamtah anabolpeh jeh'in Yahweh Pakai chu thangvahna peuhen.
\p 
\v 22 Kilhaina gantha pummin thangvahna peuhen, chuleh athilbol kidangtah ho jeh'in thangvahna peuhen.
\p 
\v 23 Mi phabep chu kong innei mangchan twikhanglen'ah vannoi leiset kiveina lampi ajot un akitollun ahi.
\p 
\v 24 Amaho jonghin twikhanglen athuhlang tah a Yahweh Pakai thuneitah a anatohna leh thil thupi tahtah abolna ho amu'vin ahi.
\p 
\v 25 Aman thu aseijin hui ahungnung doh'in twikhanglen ahin kinongsah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 26 Kong innei ho chu vanlanga anuh touvin chule twi thuhlah a ahung kilehlut kitjin kongtol ho chu kichatnan akileh leuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 27 Amaho jukham ho bangin a-onle leuvin kichat tijat nan adim'un ahi.
\p 
\v 28 “Yahweh Pakai neihuh'un” tin ahahsat phatnun Yahweh Pakai akouvun, Amanjong agimnauva kon'in ahuhdohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 29 A-o neochakhat'in hui le guo kitho chu athipsah'in chuleh twi kinong jong asutang'in ahi.
\p 
\v 30 Hiche athip theina chu ichan gei a pha a phatthei bohna hitam? Kongchu kong mun'ah bitkeichan apuilut in ahi.
\p 
\v 31 Yahweh Pakai chu angailutna thupitah jehleh thilkidang tamtah abolpeh jeh un thangvahna peuhen.
\p 
\v 32 Nam lamkaiho masangleh, mipi kikhomho masangah japi hetthei doltah in thangvahna peuhen.
\p 
\v 33 Aman vadung jong neldigam aso sahjin, twisam putna munho jong gamgo leh adang chahna aso sahjin ahi.
\p 
\v 34 Aman ga phatah sona gam phatah jong ima sodoh louna chitwi-al gamgo asosah thei in ahi, agamsunga cheng mipite phatmo jeh a hitiachu abolji ahi.
\p 
\v 35 Ahinlah Aman neldigam chu twikul asosah'in, chuleh gamgo jong twi putna mun aso sahjin ahi.
\p 
\v 36 Aman gilkel dangchah te chu khopi semdoh dinga hiche mun a chu achensah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 37 ama hon aloulai uva muchi kitheuvin tin lengpi gui tu uvin tin ga lhingsetna akilodiu ahi.
\p 
\v 38 Aman ichan gei a phatthei aboh hitam? ama hon insungmi tamtah atungdoh'un chuleh aganchahou ninglhingset ding ahi.
\p 
\v 39 Ijemtia bolgentheina jalle, boina le hahsatna jalla umho mihem a akemsuh uva avaichat phatnuleh,
\p 
\v 40 Yahweh Pakaiyin alengteu hinpaidoh intin amaho gamgo laija panna bei in umsah leleu vintin,
\p 
\v 41 hinla Yahweh Pakaiyin mivaichaho ahahsat nauva kon'in kelngoihon phatah bangin a insunga hinpunsah intin,
\p 
\v 42 Miphahon hiche thilsoh ho hi hinveu vintin kipahdiu ahinla miphalou ho chu suhthipma umdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 43 Michingho jousen hitia thilsoh ho hi lunggiltah in hinheu vintin, ama hon hitobang ikhankhouva kon a hi Yahweh Pakai mi ngailutna dihtah chu ahin mudohdiu ahi.
\c 108
\s1 Pathen Pathen Kitahna David In Avahchoi
\s1 David labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen kalungthim hi nang ah akinem jinge, ahijeh chun kalungthim pumpia nangma thangvah la kasha theihi datmo ding ahipoi.
\p 
\v 2 Hungthouvin, katheile leh kasemjang, jingpi ihmuhi kavahchoilan sukhang'ing kate.
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai mitinlah a hin nangma hin thangvah ingkate. Keiman chitin namtin lah a hin nangma vahchoila sange.
\p 
\v 4 Nami ngailutna longlouhi vanho sangin asangjon ahi. Nakitahna hin meilomlah ho aphan ahi.
\p 
\v 5 O Pathen Pathen vanho lah a asangpen sangin namin hi dopsangin umjo hen. Naloupina leiset pumpi chung vumma hin vahdoh hen.
\p 
\v 6 Tuhin name ngailut tehi huhdoh tan. Naban thahatnan neidonbutnun lang neihuhdoh tauvin,
\p 
\v 7 Pathen Pathen'in athenna a chu hiche hi akitepna ahi. “Keiman kipahtah a Sechemhi kabokhen ding, Keiman Succoth phaicham hi katetoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Gilead hi kei a ahin, Manasseh jong kei a ahi, Ephraim kathih lukhuh ahin, ama a kon a hi kagalsat ding ho hungkondoh diu ahi, chuleh Judah hi kaleng tenggol ahin ama a kon a hi kalengte hung kondoh diu ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Hinla Moab hi kakeng silna kong ahin ama a kon a hi kasohte hungkondoh diu ahi, chuleh Keiman Edom chunga hi kakeng kasilding ahi. Philistia chunga galjona kasapkhum ding ahi.”
\p 
\v 10 Koipenham kulpi kikaikhum khopi sunga eipuilut ding ah? Koiham Edom chunga galjona a eipuilut ding ah?
\p 
\v 11 O Pathen Pathen nangin neipaidoh hitam? Nangin kasepaite toh galsat'a nakonkhom louding hitam?
\p 
\v 12 O Yahweh Pakai kagalmite toh kidouna a hi neipanhu louding hitam, ajeh chu mihem kithopina hi aphachom aumpoi.
\p 
\v 13 Pathen Pathen toh pankhom hi thil loupi tahtah tohdoh theina ahi, ajeh chu Aman eikidoupi ho chu akengtoa alhopha ding ahi.
\c 109
\s1 Phulah Pehna Dinga David Taona
\s1 Lalamkai pa henga Dabid labol
\p 
\v 1 O Pathen Pathen koiham ka thangvah ding, kei a kon'in thipbeh leh gamla tah in umdan lang,
\p 
\v 2 miphalouten eihousetna thujou eiseikhum teng u jong le thipbeh in umdan.
\p 
\v 3 Thet umtah thucheng ho pum in eiumkim vel un, ajeh beihel'in eikisat piuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Keiman amaho hi kangailui amaho dinga kataolai hin ama hon thepmosah tei ding leh suhmang dingin eigong jingun ahi.
\p 
\v 5 ama hon thilpha kabol ho thilse jengin eilethuh'un, kangailutna hi vetda nan eithuh'un ahi.
\p 
\v 6 ama hon aseiyun, “Ama doudin miphalou khat hintungdoh un, achungthu kitan theina dinga athepmo sahding hinsol'un” atiuve.
\p 
\v 7 Achungthu akitan teng ama hi thepmosah uhitin, ataona chu chonsetnin simmu hite,
\p 
\v 8 Akum lhomsah uhite, michomkhat ama munna dinsah'u hite,
\p 
\v 9 achate paneilou hisah uhitin aji meithai hisah'u hite,
\p 
\v 10 achate khutdo a moh vahlele hiu henlang, inn gem in vah mang jeng uhen.
\p 
\v 11 Bat le tham houvin a in alou chuleh anei agou kichom u hen, kholgam mihon asum lodoh jouse lahpeh uhen,
\p 
\v 12 koima chan lungset dauhen; koima chan panei louva um achate chu khoto dauhen.
\p 
\v 13 Ason apah jouse thisoh hen. A inn sung pumpiu min jong akhang cheh a din lah doh in um mai hen.
\p 
\v 14 Yahweh Pakaiyin apateu chonsetna ngaidam hihbeh hen, anu-u chonsetna jong lekhabua kon'in kikahdoh hihbeh hen,
\p 
\v 15 Yahweh Pakaiyin achonset nau geldoh jinghen, chuleh aminjong mihemten geldoh hihbeh hen.
\p 
\v 16 Ajeh chu mi koima ngailut aneipoi, aman mivaichaho leh tahlelte abol genthei e, chuleh lung gentheite thina a adellut e.
\p 
\v 17 Ama mi samset athanom in; tun nang ama sugoi tan. Aman midang phatthei aboh khapoi; tun nangman ama jong phatthei boh hih in.
\p 
\v 18 Mi sapset hi ama dinga aponsil, atwidon, abuneh tobang a angaito ahitai.
\p 
\v 19 Tun amisapsetna chu hung kile henlang ama chunga pon bangin behdoh henlang angonga kong gah bangin kikhit chah hen,
\p 
\v 20 Tun hiche sapsetna ho chu eiseise ho leh eidem demho chungah Yahweh Pakai engbolna chujohen.
\p 
\v 21 Hinla O thaneipen Yahweh Pakai neidin pi in, nangma min khoto najal chun! Neihuhdoh in ajeh chu nangma hi chutobangtah a pha le kitah nahi.
\p 
\v 22 Ajeh chu keimahi mivaicha le tahlel tah kahin kalungthim hi ana behseh jenge.
\p 
\v 23 Nilhah langa nisa lim achemang bang a mangthah ding kahi, min khaokhopi apaidoh banga eikipaidoh ahitai,
\p 
\v 24 Ka ann ngol na-a kon'in kakengpah ho kisan atha aumtapon kavunleh kagu keubou kahitai.
\p 
\v 25 Keima hi muntin'a mi totnopna bep kahitan ama hon eimu tengu leh noisena'in alu-u eiheikhum jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 26 Nei kithopin O Yahweh Pakai, ka Pathen Pathen! Nami ngailutna longlou chun neihuhdoh'in.
\p 
\v 27 Yahweh Pakai nangin ka chung ahi nangma natoh mong ahiti ahetchet nadiuvin musah'in.
\p 
\v 28 Hiteng chuleh ama hon eisapset nom u jongleh eisamseuhen ajeh chu nangman phatthei neiboh ding ahinai. Ama hon eihin delkhum tengu leh jumna akimudiu ahi. Ahinla nasohkeimavang kipah a kagalkai ding ahi.
\p 
\v 29 Eitaitom jingho vang jumna ponbanga akikhu khumdiu ahin, suhnem a aum nao chun ponbanga atomkhudiu ahi.
\p 
\v 30 Ahinla kenvang Yahweh Pakai kom'a kipathu kasei jingding mijouse kom'a kasei choile ding ahi.
\p 
\v 31 Ajeh chu Aman tahlelte adinpi jingin suhmang ding gohoa kon'in ahuhdoh jingin ahi.
\c 110
\s1 Messiah Hungna Ding David In Gaothua Asei
\s1 David labol
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakaiyin ka leng pakai kom'ah, “nagal mite kasuhnem a, nakengtoa kachotpha sah tokahsen kakhut jetlam naloupina mun tou jengin” ati.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakaiyin na lenggam thaneitah chu Jerusalem a kon a ahin lhundoh ding, nangin nagalmite chunga vai na homding ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Galsat'a nacheteng namiten thanomtah a najuidiu ahi, nangma vonthenga nakivon ding chutengleh jingkah daitwi banga nisehleh natha kidodoh jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakaiyin kihahselna anei ahin akitepna chu asuhkeh louding ahi. “Nangma Melchizedek hina banga tonsot thempu nahi ding ahi” ati.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai chu najet langa dinga napuihoi jing ahi. Ama alunghanna ahung koudoh leh lengle lalho tamtah asuhlhuh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Aman chitin namtin ajepding agamsunga thilong dimset ding, aman leiset pumpia lengle lalte aban vohlhuh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Ahinlah amavang lampi pang dunga long twi adon a hatdoh jingding ahi. Hitiachu ama hi galjoupa hijengding ahi.
\c 111
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Natoh Kidang Ho
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen! Michonpha hotoh kikhop khomna chan ah keiman kalungthim apumpin Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah ingkate.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakai natoh hi iti kidan a hitam! Koi hileh ama a lunglhaina neijousen giltah a agel angaije.
\p 
\v 3 Athilbol ho jouse hin aloupina leh aja ngaina aphongdoh'in ahi. Athu adih nahi athon ngaipon ahi.
\p 
\v 4 IYahweh Pakaiyu mi ngailutna le amikhotona hi iti kidan hitam tihi aman eigeldoh sahjiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Aman akitepna hi ageldoh jingin ama gingte chu nehle chah apejingin ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Aman amite chu chidang namdang ho gam alahpeh a amaho apeh achun athaneina thupitah chu akilandoh sah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Athilbol ho jouse hi adih'in aphan ahi, chuleh athupeh ho jouse hi tahsan theicheh ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Hiche ho hi tonsotna dihjing jeng ahin tahsan tah leh kitahna neitah a jui ding ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Aman amite Manchu lhingsetna anapeh ahitai. Aman a mite toh akitepna chu tonsotna dinga asuhdet ahi. O ichan geija gimnei leh minthang hitam!
\p 
\v 10 Yahweh Pakai ginhi chihna dihtah kiphudohna khombul ahi. Athupeh hoitah a nit ho dingin chihna a khangtou cheh chehding ahi. Atonsotnin thangvah'in um jing tahen.
\c 112
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Gin Jeh a Phattheina Ho
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah un! Yahweh Pakai ginna neija athupeh ho lunglhai tah a juiho dinga iti kipa um a hitam.
\p 
\v 2 Achaten muntin'a lolhinna anei ding ahi. Khangkhat lhingset a mipha ngen hina phatthei changdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Amaho hung haodoh ding ahiuve chuleh athilpha bol u um jing jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Michonpha ho dingin jan jeng jong avah'in ahi. Amaho hi ahongphal un, khotona aneiyun chuleh thudih achepiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Hongphal tah a sumpa hom ho leh thengtah a akiveina chepiho phatthei changdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Hitobang miho chu thilsen asuhmo joulou ding ahi. Mikitah ho hi min asumil thei pon ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Amaho hin thuse hung kithangho jeng jong akichapon ama hon Yahweh Pakaiyin ahoibit diuvin tahsan na dettah aneiyun ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Amaho hin tahsanna dettah aneiyun kichatna aneipouvin ahi, chuleh akidoupi hojeng jong jotei ding tahsan nan akimai topiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Hitobang ho hin panpi ngaichaho hongphal tah in apeuvin kiphaltah in mitoh chan aching khomji nom un ahi. Atohphat nahou geldoh'in aum jingin ahi. Amaho hin mi thujona leh jana achang'un ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Milungdihlou hon hiche hi mu uvin tin alung hanpi diu ahi. Ama hon lunghang tah in aha gel unte, chuleh akinepnau thonjeh'in jumthet in kilapdoh tauvin te.
\c 113
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Tobang Koima Aumpoi
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai thangvah'in umhen! Yahweh Pakai sohte ho thangvahna peuvin, Yahweh Pakai minchu choian un!
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakai minchu nunnom hen, tuleh tonsot gei a dingin.
\p 
\v 3 Muntin a solam le lhanglam a kon'in Yahweh Pakai minchu choiat in umhen.
\p 
\v 4 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai hi chitin namtin jouse sangin asangjon aloupina hi vanho jouse sangin jong asangjon ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Koi hintem Yahweh Pakai I-Pathen'u Pathen toh tekahpi thei chu, Ama hi choisanga alaltouna a touva ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Aman kisunemtah in van leh leiset ahinven ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Aman mivaichate vutvai lah a kon'in aphongdingin chuleh tahlelte munnom pen a kon'in akaidingin,
\p 
\v 8 leng chate toh atoukhomsah'in Ama mite leng chapa te jengto jong atoukhomsah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Aman chaneilou numeiho cha le nao apen minu nomsatah in asemdohjin ahi. Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen!
\c 114
\s1 Egypt'a Kon Israel Hin Puidohpa Yahweh Pakai Vahchoiyun
\p 
\v 1 Israel te Egyptma kon a ajamdoh jouvun, Jacob insung miten hiche midang ho gamchu adalhah phatnun
\p 
\v 2 Judah gamchu Pathen Pathen muntheng a sohdoh tan Israel chu alenggam asoh doh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Twipi San chun ahungu amun ajammangtan Jordan vadunga twi ho jong ana kiheimang'in,
\p 
\v 4 Mol ho jong kelngoichal ho bangin akichom un thinglhang ho chu kelngoinou bangin akichom leuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Twipi San ipibol a na lhaimang loijeng ham? Jordan vadung ipibol a na lhaimang jengham?
\p 
\v 6 Mol ho nangho ipidinga kelngoichal banga nakichop uham? Thinglhang ho ipi dinga kelngoinou banga nakichop uham?
\p 
\v 7 O leiset, Yahweh Pakai angsung'leh Jacob Pathen Pathen masangah kithing thingin um in.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaiyin songpi chu twi veina twikul asosah'in, songpi tahbetna kon'in twisam alondoh sahjin ahi.
\c 115
\s1 Pathen Pathen Hi Dihtah a Loupi Ahi
\p 
\v 1 Keiho a ahipoi, O Yahweh Pakai keiho a ahipoi, amavang loupina jouse hi nami ngailutna longlou jeh a chun nang ding jingbou ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Chitin namtin ho hina Pathen'u Pathen hoi a umham tia aseidingu ham?
\p 
\v 3 Ka Pathen'u Pathen hi vanho chunga aum'inthil adeidan dana abolji ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Amaho semthu doihon vang sana le dangka a kisem ngenchang bou ahiuvin mihem khut in asemthu jeng ahiuve.
\p 
\v 5 ama hon kam anei un ahinla apaothei pon , chuleh mit anei un kho amuthei pouvin,
\p 
\v 6 kol aneiyun ajathei pouvin, nahkui anei un anahthei pouvin,
\p 
\v 7 khut anei un ima tohnan amangthei pouvin chuleh keng anei un achele theipouvin, lolhom anei un ahin thucheng ahungdoh thei pon ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Hitiachu doilimsemthu ho hi hiche tobang ahiuve, hiche ho tahsan ho jong hitobang machu ahiuve.
\p 
\v 9 O Israel Yahweh Pakai chu tahsan un! Ama chu napanhu na lum a pang ahi.
\p 
\v 10 O thempuho Aaron ho Yahweh Pakai chu tahsan un! Ama hi napanpia leh na lumdel a pang'a ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Nangho Yahweh Pakai gingjing ho Yahweh Pakai chu tahsan un! Ama chu napanpi le nalumdal ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Yahweh Pakaiyin nahin geldoh jingin phatthei nabohjing ding ahi. Aman Israel mipite hi phatthei aboh ding ahi, chuleh thempuho le Aaron chilhah ho jong phatthei aboh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Mithupi hihenlang milham hijongleh Yahweh Pakai ging ho chu Aman phatthei aboh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Yahweh Pakaiyin nangma nahin nachate ahin phattheina lhingset in napehen,
\p 
\v 15 Van le lei sem a Yahweh Pakai chun phatthei naboh hen,
\p 
\v 16 Vanho hi Yahweh Pakai a ahin, leiset vanghi mihemte apeh ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Mithin Yahweh Pakai thangvah la asatheipoi, ajeh chu amaho chu lhan munthip gam a che ahiuve.
\p 
\v 18 Ahinlah eihon tu le tonsot geija Yahweh Pakai ithangvah theiju ahi. Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen!
\c 116
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Hi Mihepi Ahi
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakaiyin ka o eingai peh eikhoto dia katao na eisan peh jeh in keiman Yahweh Pakai kangailui.
\p 
\v 2 Aman eihin ang ngat a kataona eingaipeh'in kahaithei laisea keima katao jing jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Thinan apon in eihin tomkhum e; lhankhuh gimneitah chun eihin lonvuh e. Keiman lungkhamna leh lunggimna ngen kamu e.
\p 
\v 4 hiteng chuleh keiman Yahweh Pakai min kakoujin, “Yahweh Pakai lungset'in neihuhdoh'in!” katijin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai hi itobang tah a milungsetthem hitam! Chuleh itobang tah a pha a hitam! I-Pathen'u Pathen hi ichan gei a mikhoto them hitam!
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakaiyin chapang lungthengtah atahsanna neijachu ahahsatna'a ahoidoh jin ahi. Keima thina toh kimaitoa kaum laitah in aman eihuhdoh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Kalhagao, nacholdo namun hinjon kittan ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai hi keidingin aphalheh jenge.
\p 
\v 8 Aman kathina dinga kon'in eihuhdoh'in kamitna mitlhi lonlouna ding leh kakeng hi kakiselhuh louna dingin eiveng jenge.
\p 
\v 9 Hiche leisetna kahin laisen Yahweh Pakai masanga kavahle jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Yahweh Pakai keima kagenthei behseh jengtai katiteng jongleh nangma katahsan jing nalai e.
\p 
\v 11 Kahahsat teng jongleh nangma kahin koujin ahi, ajeh chu hiche mitehi tahsan thei ahi pouve.
\p 
\v 12 Thilpha simjoulou eibolpeh jeh a hi Yahweh Pakai chu ipi kapehding ham?
\p 
\v 13 Keiman huhhingna khon hi domsang'ing ting eihuhhing jeh a amin ka thangvah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Keiman amite ho jouse masangah Yahweh Pakai ah kakitepna nitjinging kate.
\p 
\v 15 Yahweh Pakaiyin angailut mite athitengleh alainatpi lheh jengjin ahi.
\p 
\v 16 O Yahweh Pakai keima nasoh kahi, nangin kasoh channa'a kon'in neihuhdoh tai.
\p 
\v 17 Keiman thangvahna hi kilhaina gantha napengting Yahweh Pakai min'in taovinge.
\p 
\v 18 Keiman Yahweh Pakai a kakitepna chu amite jouse masangah pengtin,
\p 
\v 19 Yahweh Pakai Hou-In ah Jerusalem lailungah subulhit'ing kate. Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen!
\c 117
\s1 Yahweh Pakaiyin Lungsetna Tantih Neilouva Anei Jeh a Vahchoina
\p 
\v 1 Chitin namtin in Yahweh Pakai chu thangvahna peuhen, leiset chungcheng jousen thangvah cheh hen,
\p 
\v 2 Ama hi tonsot a kitahjing Yahweh Pakai ahin eingailutnao hi longlou ahijeh in Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen.
\c 118
\s1 Pathen Pathen Mingailutna Hi Tonsot a Ding Ahi
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu aphatna jeh'in thangvah'un! Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tanglouvin aum jinge.
\p 
\v 2 Israel pumpin avel in seikit hen. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tanglouvin aum jinge.
\p 
\v 3 Aaron chilhah ho leh thempuhon avel in seikitnu hen. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tanglouvin aum jinge.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai ging jousen seikit uhen agailut thutah chun tonsot in athoh jing e.
\p 
\v 5 Kagenthei pet in Yahweh Pakai kom'ah kataovin ahileh Yahweh Pakaiyin kataona asangin eilhadoh tai.
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakai keilanga apanleh ipi kakichat ding ham? kon I-eilothei dingham?
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai keilanga apanleh Aman eipapin tin, eidou ho chu kajosa tobanga kavetding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Mihem a kingai sangin, Yahweh Pakai kiselna a nei aphajoi.
\p 
\v 9 Leng chapa te a kingai sangin, Yahweh Pakai a kisel aphajoi.
\p 
\v 10 Eidouva chidang namdang ten eiumkimvel jongleh keiman amaho chu Yahweh Pakai thahatna jalla ka suhmang ding ahi.
\p 
\v 11 ama hon eiumkimvellun eidelkhummun ahi, ahinla ken amaho chu Yahweh Pakai hanta jallin kasumang gamtan ahi.
\p 
\v 12 ama hon khoi bangin eiumkimvellun eitommun, meikong a-al leng lungngin eileo tobangin eibolseuvin ahinla keiman Yahweh Pakai thahatna jallin amaho chu kasumangtan ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Kagal miten tha tei ding eigouvin ahin Yahweh Pakaiyin eihuhdoh tai.
\p 
\v 14 Yahweh Pakai hi kathahatna leh kala ahin Aman galjona eipetan ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Kipana le galjona lahi michonphate ponbuh sungah akisan, Yahweh Pakai thahatna banjet in thil loupitah atongdohtan ahi!
\p 
\v 16 Yahweh Pakai thahatna banjetchun thil loupitah atongdohtan ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Keima thilou ding kahin, Yahweh Pakaiyin eibolpeh thilho phongdoh dinga kahinjoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Yahweh Pakaiyin nasatah in eijepmin, ahinlah eithisah pon ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Mikitah ho lutna kot chu neihondoh peh'in keima lut ing ting Yahweh Pakai chu thangvahna kapehding ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Hiche kelkot ho hi Yahweh Pakai kom lhuntheina ahin michonpha ho jong hicheahi lutji ahiuve.
\p 
\v 21 Kataona neisanpeh jehleh galjona neipeh jeh'in nangma ka thangvah e!
\p 
\v 22 Insahon adeimova apaimangu inning'a songpi khomdet pennin apangtai.
\p 
\v 23 Hiche hi Yahweh Pakai natoh ahin mitvet dinga thilkidangtah ahi.
\p 
\v 24 Hiche nikho hi Yahweh Pakaiyin asem ahin, eihon kipahtah leh thanomtah a imandiu ahi.
\p 
\v 25 O Yahweh Pakai lungsettah in neihuhdoh'un, O Yahweh Pakai lungset tah in neilolhin sahtei teijun.
\p 
\v 26 Yahweh Pakai minna hungpa chu anunnomme. Yahweh Pakai Hou-Inna kon'in nangho phatthei kahinboh'un ahi.
\p 
\v 27 Yahweh Pakai chu Pathen Pathen, ichung uva hi vahjinga um a ahi. Kilhaina sa chu khaovin khitninlang maicham ki ho chutoh khitbeh'in
\p 
\v 28 Nangma ka Pathen Pathen nahin keiman kavahchoi ding nahi! Nangma ka Pathen Pathen nahin keiman kachoisang ding ahi.
\p 
\v 29 Yahweh Pakai chu aphatna ho jeh'in thangvah'un! Ajeh chu ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a um jing ahi.
\c 119
\s1 Pathen Pathen Danthu Phatchom Na
\s1 Aleph
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai thupeh dungjui a chonho leh kitahna neiho chu kipah uhen.
\p 
\v 2 Koi hileh a Dan thu nit a alungthim pumpia Ama holjing ho chu kipah'u hen.
\p 
\v 3 Amaho chun thil phalou achepi pouvin Yahweh Pakai deilampi joh ajui un ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai nangin nathupeh ho chu phatah a kanit diuvin nei seipeh'un ahi.
\p 
\v 5 O Yahweh Pakai kanitin hinkho Mandan ahin nangman neideipeh hinkho hi kilangdoh jengle kati e.
\p 
\v 6 Chuleh nathupeh leh ka chondan kavetkah teng kajum louding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Keiman nei thuhilna dihtah ho chu kahet dungjui a kakiman ding dol a kakimanchah theijeh a nangma chu ka thangvah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Neidalha hihbeh'in, keiman na Dan chu kanitjing ding ahi.
\s1 Beth
\p 
\v 9 Khangthah khatchu itileh ahinkho atheng theidem? Nangma thu angaileh hitheiding ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Keiman nangma mudoh tei ding kagelkhoh'in ahi, nangma thupeh a kon'in neilam vai sahhih'in.
\p 
\v 11 Nangma douna kachonset louna dingin ka lungsung ah nathu chu kachensah jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 12 O Yahweh Pakai nangma ka thangvah'e nathupeh nitji dan neihil in.
\p 
\v 13 Ka chonding dan nangin neipeh ho chu keiman kasimphongjin ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Nei le gou va housangin na Dan thu chu jui ding katha anomjoi.
\p 
\v 15 Neithupeh na Dan ho chu keiman simjingingting nei deipeh lampia chejing dingin kingaito jing nange.
\p 
\v 16 Na Dan thu ho hi kakipapin, jui dinga neithupeh ho jong sumil ponge.
\s1 Gimel
\p 
\v 17 Nasohpa keima hi thilpha neibolpen kahinkhoa hi nathupeh kanit jingna dingin.
\p 
\v 18 Nathupeh hoa thudih kidangtah ho hi kamuchet theina dingin kamit hi hadohsah'in.
\p 
\v 19 Keima hiche leisetna hi kholjin bep kahi bouve nathupeh ho chu keima nei impeh hihbeh'in.
\p 
\v 20 Phatin in keiman nachondan jui ding ngaichatna hin eilonvuhtan ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Nangin mikiletsah ho chu nahousejin, nathupeh a kon a pampet ho chu nasamsejin ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Na Dan sem ho hi kajui jingnai amaho hi neinoise sahhihbeh'in.
\p 
\v 23 Leng chapa te ho toukhom u henlang keima dounan thu seijonglehu keivangin na Dan semho hi jui ding geljing nange.
\p 
\v 24 Na Dan semho hi kakipapi lheh jenge ajeh chu hiche ho hin chihna thu eihil jingin ahi.
\s1 Daleth
\p 
\v 25 Keima leivui lah a kijama kahitai nathu chun neisuhal kittan.
\p 
\v 26 Ka chondan, kaumchan nakom'ah kaphongdoh tai, tun nadan semchu neisei pehtan.
\p 
\v 27 Na Dan thupeh chu neithem sah'in, chutengleh keiman natohdoh datmo umtah ho chu kalungin geljing nange.
\p 
\v 28 Lungkhamnan eibom in kakaptai, nakam changing neihaldoh sahkit tan.
\p 
\v 29 Mijou milepche hotoh neichom khen in, nathuhil kahetthem theina ding thuguh chu neipen.
\p 
\v 30 Kitah tah a hinkho man ding hi kakilhen ahitai, nathuhil dungjui a hinkho man dinghi kadinpi ahitai.
\p 
\v 31 Na Dan semhi katuhchah ahitai, O Yahweh Pakai neijumso hihbeh'in!
\p 
\v 32 Nathupeh ho hi kajui jingding ahi, ajeh chu nangin hetthem theina neipeh jingding jehin.
\s1 He
\p 
\v 33 O Yahweh Pakai nathupeh chu neihillin, keiman achaina gei in juijinging kate.
\p 
\v 34 Nathuhil kajuijing theina dingin hetthem theina neipen. Kalungthim pumpin hichu natohman podoh ingkate.
\p 
\v 35 Nathupeh dungjuijin neikalson sah'in hichu kakipanapen ahi.
\p 
\v 36 Sum ngaichatna sangin na Dan thu hetthemding ngaichat theina neipejon.
\p 
\v 37 Thil phachomlou hoa kon'in kamit heimangin lang nathuchengin neihindoh sah'in.
\p 
\v 38 Nangma ginle jana neiho napeh kitepna chu keima kom'ah neisuhdetpeh'in.
\p 
\v 39 Kajumna hinkho hi neipailhah sah'in ajeh chu na Dan semho hi aphalheh jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 40 Nathupeh ho hi kajuinomlheh jenge naphatna'in kahinkho hi neithah sempeh kittan.
\s1 Waw
\p 
\v 41 Yahweh Pakai nami ngailutna longlou tonsot hinna neiteppeh chu neipetan,
\p 
\v 42 Chutileh eitaitom ho donbutje kahetding ahi ajeh chu keiman nathutep chu katahsan in ahi.
\p 
\v 43 Phat tin in thutah jeng neisei sah'in ajeh chu nangma chondan thupeh a bouhin kinepna kaneiyin ahi.
\p 
\v 44 Keiman nathupeh ho chu itihchan hijongleh kanit jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 45 Keiman chamlhatna tahbeh chu kaneitai, ajeh chu nangma thuhil jui dinga kigo kahitai.
\p 
\v 46 Keiman nathupehho hi jahchalouhel la lengte masanga jong ka phondoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 47 Keiman nang thupeh jui dinghi kakipanapen ahitai ajeh chu hiche ho hi keiman kadeilheh jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 48 Keiman na thupeh ho hi kadeilheh jengin chuleh jana jong kaneiyin ahi, na Dan thu ho hi giltah in kagellin ahi.
\s1 Zayin
\p 
\v 49 Kakom'a na kitepna chu geldoh'in hiche bouchu ahi kakinepna.
\p 
\v 50 Hiche nakitepna hin kahinkho akiledohsah kit in kalungthim boina hoa kon'in jong lungmon na eipen ahi.
\p 
\v 51 Mikiletsah hon noise tah in eibol jonglehu keivang nangma thuhilhoa kon'in kapotdoh pon ahi.
\p 
\v 52 Masanglai peh a na Dan sem nachepi ho chu kangaito leh O Yahweh Pakai hichechun eilhamon sahlheh jenge.
\p 
\v 53 Keima miphalou ho chunga kalung ahang'in ahi, ajeh chu ama hon nathuhil apompouve.
\p 
\v 54 Hiche kakholjinna munhi hoilai hijongleh na Dan thu semho hi kala ngeipen ahijinge.
\p 
\v 55 O Yahweh Pakai jantengleh nangma nahina hi ka lungsung ah akilangjin, hijeh chun nathuhil ho hi kajui jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 56 Nathupeh juijinghi kahinkho mandan hitoh kilhon khoma ahitai.
\s1 Heth
\p 
\v 57 O Yahweh Pakai, kachan ding gouchu nangma nahi! Nathupeh jui dingin kakiphaldoh jinge!
\p 
\v 58 Kalungthim pumpi hi namalsomna ngaichajing kahi, Nakitepna bangin neihepi jingtan.
\p 
\v 59 Kahinkho ka lam lhahdan hi kanung gel jin chutengleh na Dan thu juina dingahin ka lutkit ji tai.
\p 
\v 60 Nathupeh juina dingahin gangtah in kipelut jing nange.
\p 
\v 61 Miphalou hon chonsetna a lhohlut tei ding eigo jiuvin ahinla keima vang na Dan thuhilna a hin dettah in kading jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 62 Na Dan thupeh ho hi adih jeh'in jankhang jongleh kathoudoh'in nangma ka thangvah jin ahi.
\p 
\v 63 Nangma thupeh juijing ho leh nangma ging jingho dingin agolphao kahijinge.
\p 
\v 64 O Yahweh Pakai nami ngailutna tanglou hin leiset chunghi adipmin, na Dan thu hi neihil jingin.
\s1 Teth
\p 
\v 65 Yahweh Pakai nangin nakitepna dungjuijin thilpha tamtah neibolpeh tai.
\p 
\v 66 Nathupeh hoachun kading jinge, hetna thepna leh thu adih a tantheina thuguh chu neihil in,
\p 
\v 67 Nangin neihilchah masang chun kana lamvaijin, tunvang nathu thun kanungtai.
\p 
\v 68 Nangman naphatna'in thilpha bou nabol jie, na Dan thu chu neihil in.
\p 
\v 69 Miphalou ho jouthu eisei khum jiuvin, ahinla kenvang kalungthim pumpin nathupeh ho dihtah in kajuijing nai.
\p 
\v 70 Alungthim u ngol hoitah ahin; keivang nangma thupehho juijing hi kakipana ahijinge.
\p 
\v 71 Ka thohgimna chu keidinga thilphajo anahi, ajeh chu hiche hin nathupeh juina ding langa lunglutna eipetheijin ahi.
\p 
\v 72 Nathuhil ho jui ding hi sana le dangka simsenlou sangin aman atamjon ahi.
\s1 Yodh
\p 
\v 73 Nangin neina gon a neinasemdoh ahin, tunvang nathupeh juina dinga hin hetthem theina neipen.
\p 
\v 74 Nangma ging ho jousen kei a konna hin kipa na mu u heuhen, ajeh chu keiman nathupeh ahin kinepna dihtah kaneiyin ahi.
\p 
\v 75 O Yahweh Pakai keiman na Dan semho adihdan hi kahethem tai, neisuhgim ji ding hi keidia thilphachom ahi.
\p 
\v 76 Tuhin nasohpa neiteppeh bangin nami ngailutna longlou chun eilungmonsah jin ahi.
\p 
\v 77 Kahintheina dingin namihepina chun neiumkimvel jingin ajeh chu neithuhilna ho hi keidinga kipana leh lunglhaina ahi.
\p 
\v 78 Keichung changa thujou seiho miphalou ho chu jumle jachatna penlang, keivangin nangma thupehho chu kangai jingding ahinai.
\p 
\v 79 Nangma Dan he themho leh nangma ging jingho chutoh nei ki vopkhom sah jingin.
\p 
\v 80 Na Dan thu kajuina ahin bolkhel kaneilouna dingin neivengin, chutileh jumna leh jachatna kaneilou ding ahi.
\s1 Kaph
\p 
\v 81 Nangma huhdohna ding kangana lamma hin abeipaiding kahitai, ahinlah nathupeh ahin kakinepna adetjinge.
\p 
\v 82 Nakitepna ahung gulhunna ding vetnan kamit achahleutai, itih tah leh neilhamon dingham?
\p 
\v 83 Lengpitwipai savun ahun ahulgot bangin kagolhatai ahinlah na Dan thu jui ding kasumil dehpon ahi.
\p 
\v 84 Itihchanpi hi kanga jingding hitam? Keima eibolse ho hi itihleh aphu nalah dingham?
\p 
\v 85 Nangma thuhil nahsahlou mi kiletsah ho hin keima kipalna ding ko thuhtah alaijun ahi.
\p 
\v 86 Nathupeh jouse hi tahsan dinga lomtah cheh ahi. Ajeh bei a eidel lele hoa konhin neihuhdoh'in.
\p 
\v 87 Amaho hin eichaidohpai got u ahitai, ahinla keiman nathupeh ho hi kajuida dehpoi.
\p 
\v 88 Na mi ngailutna longlou chun kahinkho hi huhdoh'in, chutileh na Dan thu kajui theiding ahi.
\s1 Lamedh
\p 
\v 89 O Yahweh Pakai tonsot a dinga nakitepna chu van a dettah in aum jinge.
\p 
\v 90 Nangin nanatundoh hiche leiset hi aum jing bangin nakitahna jong akhang khanga um jing ahi.
\p 
\v 91 Nathilgon jouse hi nathupeh dungjuijin tuni chan geihin aumsohkei un ahi, ajeh chu amaho hi aboncha nalhacha ahisohkei un ahi.
\p 
\v 92 Na Dan thupeh hin kipana hinkho'ah eihin khoukhah hihleh kagenthei lengvaina a kana mol lem ding ahitai.
\p 
\v 93 Na thupeh Dan ho hi itihchan hijongleh ka suhmillouhel ding ahi, ajeh chu hiche ho hin eihinghoi ahi.
\p 
\v 94 Yahweh Pakai nanga kahi; neihuhdoh'in! Ajeh chu nadan thu nitna a hin ka kihabol lheh jenge.
\p 
\v 95 Mi phalouhon suhmang dingin lampi dungah eichanglhi le jonguleh keiman vang na Dan thu hi ka lungsungah thipbeh chan geljing nange.
\p 
\v 96 Thiljouse hin akhkonna aneisohkeije ahinlah na Dan thupeh hin akhkonna aneipoi.
\s1 Mem
\p 
\v 97 Oh, na Dan thupeh hi iti kahin dei hitam! Ni lhumkei kei in hiche ho hi kageljin in ahi.
\p 
\v 98 Na Dan thupeh ho hin kagal mite sangin eichihsah'e, ajeh chu hiche ho hin phattin in eiveng jinge.
\p 
\v 99 Na Dan thu hi phattin a ka geljing jeh'in eihilho sangin jong hetgilna ka neijotai.
\p 
\v 100 Na thupeh Dan ho kanitjing jeh'in kachunga upa tehse ho sangin jong kachingjo tai.
\p 
\v 101 Nathupeh dettah a kajuijing theina dingin thilse bolna a cheding kanompon ahi.
\p 
\v 102 Nangin phate keicha neihil ahitah jeh'in na Dan thu juina a kon'in ka ki heimang nompon ahi.
\p 
\v 103 Na thupeh hi kapatep leh alhum lheh jenge, khoiju sangin alhumjon ahi.
\p 
\v 104 Na Dan thupeh ho hin hetthemna eipen; hiti chun hinkho adihlou lam a cheding hi kathet lheh ji e.
\s1 Nun
\p 
\v 105 Nathupeh hi kakalskonna a eipuiding thaomei jin apangin, kalampi salvah ding vah'in apangin ahi.
\p 
\v 106 Na Dan thupeh dihtah ho hi kajuijing ding ahin, hiche dinga hi kitepna kananei ahitan avel a kakitep kitding ahi.
\p 
\v 107 Yahweh Pakai nathutep dungjuijin ka hinkho hoidoh sah'in ajeh chu kathohlel behseh jenge.
\p 
\v 108 O Yahweh Pakai ka thangvah nahi kilhaina thilto bangin neisanpeh'in lang chuleh na Dan thupeh ho neihil in.
\p 
\v 109 Keima ka hinkho hi kilep ditdet in aum'e, ahinlah na thuhil hi ka juidadeh pong e.
\p 
\v 110 Mi phalou hon ka kipalna dingin thang akam jingun ahi, ahi vangin nathupeh a kon a ka ki heimang doh louding ahi.
\p 
\v 111 Na Dan thu hi keidinga gou ahi, hiche ho hin ka lungthim akipasah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 112 Ka thini chan gei a na Dan thu nitding hi ka dinpi ahitai.
\p 
\v 113 Kitahna neiloute hi kathet ahin keivang na thuhil ho jui dinghi katha nopna ahi.
\s1 Samekh
\p 
\v 114 Nangma hi kakiselna leh kalumdal nahi, nathupeh hi kakinepna bulpi ahijinge.
\p 
\v 115 Milung gilouho keija kon'in potdoh'un, ajeh chu keiman ka Yahweh Pakai thupeh ho hi kajuinom e.
\p 
\v 116 Yahweh Pakai, nakitepna bangin kahinjouna dingin tha neipen kakinepna hi neijumso hihbeh'in,
\p 
\v 117 Nathahatnan neituh'in chutileh kahoidohding ahi, chutengleh nathupeh hi kachepi jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 118 Nathupeh a kon a potdoh ho hi nangin napaidoh gamheltan ahi. Amaho hi amaho leh amaho kijoulhep ahi bouve.
\p 
\v 119 Nangin mi-engse ho chu leiset chunga kon'in bohse bangin napaidoh jitan ahi, hijeh chun kei vangin na Dan thu ho hi kajui nom e.
\p 
\v 120 Nangma ginnan ka kithinge, na thutan dihtah ho jeh'in ki chatnan kadim e.
\s1 Ayin
\p 
\v 121 Keiman thudih tah leh kitahna neitah in na katonge, kagal mite khut a neidalhahih'in.
\p 
\v 122 Phatthei neibohding kinepna neipen, mi kiletsahho neibolsetsah hihbeh'in.
\p 
\v 123 Nathutep dihtah chu asuh bulhit nadinga neihuhdohna dingchu kavet vetnan kamit achah leutan ahi.
\p 
\v 124 Nami ngailutna longlou chun nasoh hi neibolpha jingin, chuleh na Dan thu ho chu neihil in.
\p 
\v 125 Na Dan thu ho hi kahettheina dingin nasohhi hetthem theina neipen.
\p 
\v 126 Yahweh Pakai tu hi nakipatna na tohphat ahitai, ajeh chu miphalouhon na Dan thu apal kehgam tauve.
\p 
\v 127 Tahbeh in nathupeh ho hi sana mantampen sangin kadeijon ahi.
\p 
\v 128 Na thupeh ho hi adihsohkei in, hijeh a chu lamdihlou ho hi kathet ahi.
\s1 Pe
\p 
\v 129 Na Dan semho hi akidang theilheh jengin hijeh a chu kalungthim pumpia kajui ahi!
\p 
\v 130 Na Dan thuhil'a hin vah akilangin hijeh chun milham minjong ahetheijin ahi.
\p 
\v 131 Nathupeh ho kangaichat behseh jeh'in kaki gon chule kakam kah in kangah jinge.
\p 
\v 132 Nangma ngailuho nabolna bangin hung kihei in lang nami khotona neimusah'in.
\p 
\v 133 Nakitepna dungjuijin kalhuh louna dingin neituh'in, thilse eijosah hihbeh'in.
\p 
\v 134 Eisugenthei hoa kon'in neihuhdoh'in, hitiachu nathupehho hoitah a kajuijing theina dingin.
\p 
\v 135 Nasohpa kei ahin namaivah chu hin kilan dohsah'in chutengleh na Dan thu chu neihil in.
\p 
\v 136 Mi hemten na thuhil ajuitah lou jeh un kamit na hin mitlhi twi vadung bangin along'e.
\s1 Tsadhe
\p 
\v 137 O Yahweh Pakai nangma thudihtah nahi, na Dan semho jong adih'e.
\p 
\v 138 Na Dan semho hi nolnabei ahin chuleh tahsanthei mong mong ahi.
\p 
\v 139 Ka galmiten na thupeh hi anahsah loujeh un ka lunghan hi aki khonhel jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 140 Na thutep ho hi kapatep sohkei ahitan adih lheh jengin keiman ka deilheh jenge.
\p 
\v 141 Keima hi hetkhamlou leh notthap ka hivang in nathupeh ho hi ka sumil dehpoi.
\p 
\v 142 Yahweh Pakai nanga hin tonsotna thudih na aum'e, chuleh na thuhil dihtah ho jonghi nolnabei ahi.
\p 
\v 143 Hahsatna le lung khamna in eilonvuh jeng jongleh nathupeh ho hi keidinga kipana tahbeh ahijinge.
\p 
\v 144 Na Dan semho jouse jonghi adihjing jenge, hinna ka neitheina dingin neihet them sah'in.
\s1 Qoph
\p 
\v 145 Kalungthim pumpin kataove O Yahweh Pakai neihouvin, keiman na Dan thu ho chu kanit jingding ahi.
\p 
\v 146 Nangma kahin kouve Yahweh Pakai neihuhdoh'in, na Dan thu ho chu ka juijing theina din.
\p 
\v 147 Khovah masangin matah in kathouvin, nathutep na chun kakinem in panpi kathum e.
\p 
\v 148 Jan khovah'in kahah'in nathutep chu kagel jinge.
\p 
\v 149 Nami ngailutna dihtah a konchun O Yahweh Pakai kataona ngai in lang na Dan thu juina ahin neichoh hing kittan.
\p 
\v 150 Dan neilou miten eihung delkhum un ahi, amaho hi nangma thuhilla kon'in agamla lheh'un ahi.
\p 
\v 151 Ahinlah O Yahweh Pakai nangma naichan naum'inahi, chuleh nangma thupehho jouse adih'in ahi.
\p 
\v 152 Na Dan semho hi tonsot a ding ahije tihi kaneolai a patna kanahetsa ahitai.
\s1 Resh
\p 
\v 153 Kathoh gimna hi venlang neihuhdoh'in, ajeh chu keiman na thuhil ho chu ka sumil khapoi.
\p 
\v 154 Keima langa pangin lang ka chung chang thu nei seipeh'in nakitepna bangin neihuhdoh'in.
\p 
\v 155 Mi phalou hovang ki huhdoh louding ahiuve. Ajeh chu ama hon na Dan thu hi anahsah pouve.
\p 
\v 156 O Yahweh Pakai namihe pina hi anasalheh jenge, na Dan semho hi jui ing kating ka hinkho hi neikile dohsah tan.
\p 
\v 157 Mi tamtah in asugenthei jin eisuboijin ahi, ahinlah na Dan thu juina a kon'in kakiheimang dehpoi.
\p 
\v 158 Hitobanga mikitahlou ho hi ka muting leh ka lungnatpi lhehjin ahi, ajeh chu amaho hin na Dan thu hi anahsah pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 159 Yahweh Pakai ven na thupeh hi ichan gei a ka gelkhoh hitam, na mingailutna longlou jal in ka hinkho hi neilepeh kit in.
\p 
\v 160 Na Dan hung kipatna thuguh chu thutah ahi, na Dan thudihtah ho hi tonsot a dingjing ding ahi.
\s1 Shin
\p 
\v 161 Mi thanei hon dihloutah in eibol seuve, ahinlah keiman nathupeh hi ka lungthim in ginna kanei jinge.
\p 
\v 162 Khat touvin gou nasatah akimudoh bangin nathupeh ahin kakipah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 163 Keiman jou le nal kiti hi kathetnin ahinlah nathupeh ho hi kagelkhoh'e.
\p 
\v 164 Na Dan thu ho hi adihjeh'in nikhat in sagivei thangvah na penge.
\p 
\v 165 Nang ma Dan thu ho gelkhoh na neiho jousen thahatna anei un ahi chuleh kipalna aneipou vin ahi.
\p 
\v 166 Yahweh Pakai nangin neihuhdoh dinghi ka ngaicha lheh jengin ahi, hijeh a chu nathupeh ho hi ka juijing ahi.
\p 
\v 167 Na Dan semho hi kahinjui jinge ajeh chu hiche ho hi deium ka salheh jenge.
\p 
\v 168 Ahi, keiman nathupeh ho leh na Dan semho hi kajui jinge ajeh chu nangin ka kimanchahna jouse nahen ahi.
\s1 Taw
\p 
\v 169 O Yahweh Pakai kahin kou nahi ngai in nangin neitep pehna bangin het them theina lungthim neipen.
\p 
\v 170 Ka taona hi ngai in, nathutep na bangin nei huhdoh tei in.
\p 
\v 171 Kakam a kon'in thangvahna hi hung lengdoh jenghen ajeh chu nangman na Dan thu ho hi neihil themtan ahi.
\p 
\v 172 Kalei in nathupeh ho hi thangvah lan sa hen, ajeh chu nathupeh jouse hi adih'in ahi.
\p 
\v 173 Nei kithopina khutchu hin lhangdoh'in ajeh chu na thupeh ho jui dinga kigotna kanei ahitai.
\p 
\v 174 O Yahweh Pakai nangin neihuhdoh dinghi ka ngaichat jing ahi, ajeh chu nangma thuhil ho hi kakipana ahijinge.
\p 
\v 175 Nangma ka thangvah jing theina dingin nei hing hoi in, chuleh nathupeh ho hi eikithopin pangjing hen.
\p 
\v 176 Kelngoi banga vahmanga kahitai hungin lang neihung holdoh tan ajeh chu nathupeh ho hi keiman kasumil theipoi.
\c 120
\s1 Thudih Lou Seina Kona Huhdohna Dinga Taona
\s1 Jerusalem a Pathen Pathen hou a cheho chung chang a David labol
\p 
\v 1 Lungkham na leh lung gim na kato tengleh Yahweh Pakai kom kalhutjin ahileh Aman kataona asangjin ahi.
\p 
\v 2 O Yahweh Pakaiyin mijoubol ho a konleh milepche ho a kon'in neihuhdoh'in.
\p 
\v 3 Oh lepchena leigui mangcha ho, Pathen Pathen'in nangho ipi na louvin tem? Aman na chunga engbolna ichan gei in apunsahbe dem?
\p 
\v 4 Nangma thalchang hemtah a naki sunding chuleh meihol sapehpoh naki desah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Gamlatah Meshach lah a ka chenchu kadanave, gamla tah Kedar ponbuh a ka chenchu ka thohlel ngeije,
\p 
\v 6 Keima chamna deilah a kachenhi kakhoplheh jengtai,
\p 
\v 7 Keiman chamna kahol in, ahinlah keiman chamna thu kaseipou pouleh ama hon gal bou adeijiu ve.
\c 121
\s1 Aphalouva Kon Yahweh Pakaiyin Nahuhdoh Ding Ahi
\s1 Jerusalem a kon Pahen hou ho dia la kibol
\p 
\v 1 Keima kadah in thinglhanglam kavei, hichea kon a khu eipanpi hung hintem?
\p 
\v 2 Vanle lei sem pa Paka a kon a eipanpi hung ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Aman nangma nakipalsah louding; nachingpa chu ihmu louding ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Tahbeh in Israel chingpa chu itihchan hijongleh ihmu lhulou ding ahilouleh ihmu louding ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai ama tah chu nachingpa ahi! Ama nakom'a ading jingin nahoidohna lim in apang jinge.
\p 
\v 6 Sun leh nisan nasangpeh pontin, janleh lhavah injong nasubeipon te.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakaiyin thilse jousea nahoidohsah in tin nahinkho chingjing nante.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaiyin tu apat tonsot gei in navai kondoh leh nahung vailhun in nachingjing tahen.
\c 122
\s1 Jerusalem'a Chamna Umna Dia David Taona
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai Hou-Inn ah cheuhite tia kakom'a asei u chun keima kakipahlheh jengin ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Vo Jerusalem tuhin keiho nakelkot sung langah kadingtao ve.
\p 
\v 3 Jerusalem hi dettah a kisa khopi ahin apal jonghi detchetna kigenbitna ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai mite Israel phungho jousen hicheahi kintheng bolla ahungnao ahi. Israel te chonna dan dungjui a Yahweh Pakai kom'a thangvahna pedinga ahungnao ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Hichea hin lengte thutanna laltouna ho chu aum'inDavid chilhah ho laltouna ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Jerusalem a cham lenna din taovun, hiche khopi ngailu jouse khangtouhen.
\p 
\v 7 Vo Jerusalem, nakulpi sunga chamleng hen chuleh nakhopi sung khangtou hen.
\p 
\v 8 Ka insung mite leh kagol kapaite khohsahna in keiman Jerusalem ah “Nanga chamna umhen” kati.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai, I-Pathen'u insung khohsah na'in, O Jerusalem nang dinga aphapen chu kahol ahi.
\c 123
\s1 Hepina Mutheina Dinga Taona
\p 
\v 1 Van'a alaltouna a tou O ka Pathen Pathen nangma munomna in kadah in kahinvei.
\p 
\v 2 Sohten amit uva apupao avetjing bangun Yahweh Pakai, I-Pathen'u Pathen khotona ngaichan keihon kahin vejing ui. Hiti hin soh nungah honjong api'u chaloh akivetgeu jingun ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakai ka chung u vah khotona neipeuvin ajeh chu keiho hi vetda changsa ka hiuve.
\p 
\v 4 Ajeh chu keiho hi mi kiletsahho housetna leh mikhoh ho tai tomnan eichupmu ahitai.
\c 124
\s1 Ama Tahsan Ho Yahweh Pakaiyin Ahuhdoh
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai hi eiho langa anapanglou hikhataleh? Israel te jousen velseikit hen.
\p 
\v 2 Min eina delkhum pettah'un Yahweh Pakai hi eiho langa anapanglou hikhataleh,
\p 
\v 3 ama hon alunghan u deojah pum in ahingin eina vallhum tauvinte.
\p 
\v 4 Twi chun einachup uvin tin, twikhanglen chun einalhohmang diu ahitai.
\p 
\v 5 Hitiachu ichung uva twipi kitoltol ding ahiuve.
\p 
\v 6 Igalmiteu eina suhmang sah louva Yahweh Pakai chu thangvahna peuhite.
\p 
\v 7 Eiho thang kampa a kon a vacha ahoidoh banga hoidoh ihiuve. Thangpou chu akivobong tan eiho ihoidoh tauve.
\p 
\v 8 Hitobanga kithopina chu vanle lei sem ah Yahweh Pakai a kon a imu'u ahi.
\c 125
\s1 Pathen Pathen Tahsante Hoidoh Jing Ding Ahi
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai a tahsanna dettah neiho chu Zion mol tobag ahiuve. Amaho chu suhlinghoi hiloudiu a-itih'a detjing ding ahiuve.
\p 
\v 2 Jerusalem mol'in aumkimvel bangin, tuleh tua dingin Yahweh Pakai chu amite kimvel a akisung jinge.
\p 
\v 3 Michonphate gam a chu miphalou te vaihomna leng teng gol in chan aneilou ding ahi. Achuti louleh michonpha ho jengin jong thilse ahinbol maithei ahi.
\p 
\v 4 O Yahweh Pakai miphaho lungthim nangma toh chekhom theiho chu nangin thilpha bolpeh jingin.
\p 
\v 5 Ahinlah O Yahweh Pakai lamdihlouva chete chu thil dihlou bolte toh paidohtha jengin. Israel te lah a cham lenghen!
\c 126
\s1 Pathen Pathen In Asemphat Jal'a Thangvahna
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakaiyin sohchang ho chu Jerusalem a ahinlepuilut kitphatchun, hichu mangtoh abang jengin ahi!
\p 
\v 2 Keiho lungna chim tah a nuinan ka dimset jingun, ki pahtah in la kasauve. Hichun chidang namdang hon aseiyun, “Yahweh Pakaiyin thil loupi kidangtah chu aboldoh peh tauve” atiuve.
\p 
\v 3 Adih'e, Yahweh Pakaiyin thil loupi kidangtah chu eiboldoh pehtauve! Iti kipa um a hitam!
\p 
\v 4 Neldi gam a twilonglut hon athah semkit bangin O Yahweh Pakai kanei kagouhou hin kiledoh sah kittan.
\p 
\v 5 Mitlhi long pum pum a muchi tuten, kipah thanom tah a aga akilodiu ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Kapjing pum a atuding muchi kipoh'a vaikonten, aga hinkipoh puma inmun kipahle thanomtah in hung kileuhen.
\c 127
\s1 Haona Kiti Hi Yahweh Pakaiya Hung Kon Ahi
\s1 Solomon ki pahtah a ala sem
\p 
\v 1 Insa-a hi Yahweh Pakai apan louleh, asahon mohseh a asah'u ahi. Khopi ngah'a hi Yahweh Pakai ajao louleh, khongah ho panna bei a hahkhovah ahiuve.
\p 
\v 2 Jingkah matah a nakipat uva jankhang gei a neh ding an holna a na natoh'u pan nabei ahi, ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin angailut achate hi a-ihmut sung uva hi ijakai agontohpeh ahi bouve.
\p 
\v 3 Veuvin, chatehi Yahweh Pakaiya kon a gou ahin, naobu sunga konna aga kimu jonghi kipa thilpeh ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Khang don laija cha kineiho hi galsatpan akhutna thal changho akichoi tobang ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Thal chang abom dimsetna kipohpa anunnom ahi. Ama chu agalmite toh thutanna munna akimuto teng gal lel hilouhel ding ahi.
\c 128
\s1 Pathen Pathen Gingte Chunga Phattheina Ho
\p 
\v 1 Koi hileh Yahweh Pakai ging geh'a um a Ama lunglhaina lampia kalsongho chu anunnom ahiuve.
\p 
\v 2 Nangin nakhutsoh natohga naneh ding ahin, iti nakipading hitam na hinkho kiledoh ding ahitai.
\p 
\v 3 Na insunga najinu jong lengpi gui ga phatah banga phatthei punna hi ding, ankong phunga an naneh khompi nachate mel-hoitah tah Olive thingbah lhoutah bangdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Veuvin, Yahweh Pakai gingte phatthei achan dingu chu hitobang hi hi ding ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakaiyin Zion a kon'in phatthei nabohjing jinghen, nahinkho lhumkei in Jerusalem machalna mujing jingin.
\p 
\v 6 Natuson gei in jong hin munlang, Israel chungah chamleng hen!
\c 129
\s1 Zion Kidoupite Alekhup Na Dinga Taona
\p 
\v 1 Kakhangdonlai a pat in kagalmiten eihin bolseuvin ahi. Israel pumpin hiche hi velsei uhen.
\p 
\v 2 Kakhangdonlai a pat in kagalmiten eihin bolseuvin ahi, ahinla ama hon khatveicha eijoukha pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Katungtun hi maha adiptauvin, loukhoipan lou akhoi chehlah lahtoh abahsah jengun ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Ahinla Yahweh Pakai chu aphatjeh'in miphalouhon khaova eikan nao eisutlhap peh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Koi hileh Jerusalem hot leh deimoa bol ho jouse chu jumthet in ki nunglekit'u henlang lhuhpiu hen.
\p 
\v 6 Amaho hi panna bei inchung vum a hampa kehtobang, akhan kilhit masanga goplha tobang hiuhen.
\p 
\v 7 Chang-at hon anotthap'u, chuleh chang kanhon adeimou hihen, chuleh hichelang hopa jousen, “Nachung uva Yahweh Pakai phattheiboh umhen keihon Yahweh Pakai mi in phatthei kahinboh uve” tin seihihbeh'u hen.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaiyin phatthei na boh hen, Yahweh Pakai min'in nangma phatthei ka boh uve, chule nangman na lam jot na chun hichi mi ho chun phattheina chu sutang jou pou vin te.
\c 130
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Ngaidamna
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai lunglhahna kotong sunga kon'in nangma panpina kahinthum e.
\p 
\v 2 O Yahweh Pakai kakanahi ngai in, kataona hi neingaipeh'in.
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai kachonset nauhi hoitah a namelchih ding hileh, koiham O Yahweh Pakai ahingdoh ding?
\p 
\v 4 Ahinla Nangin nangma ginje kahetthem theina diuvin ngaidamna neipejiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Keiman Yahweh ka Pakai nangma panpina kinem tah in kangah'e. Henge, keima nangma a ki ngaijing kahi. Keiman athusei katahsan'in hichea kinem a ngahjing kahi.
\p 
\v 6 Keiman Yahweh Pakai chu ka ngahlel ngei e, kho ngahpan khovah ding angalel sangin kangahlel joi.
\p 
\v 7 Vo Israel, Yahweh Pakaiya kinem in, ajeh chu Yahweh Pakai ahin longlou ngailutna umma ahin chuleh ama a hin lhatdamna lhingset in aum'inahi.
\p 
\v 8 Ama tah in Israel chu achonsetna jouse a konna ahuhdoh ding ahi.
\c 131
\s1 David Kineosah Pum'a Yahweh Pakaiya Kingai Jing
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai, kalungthim akiletsah poi; kamit ha dan jong kihi sahna aumpoi. Keima hi thil thupitah in jong kakigel pon keimat phah din jong aloupi behseh e.
\p 
\v 2 Hiche sang chun keima kahina kalung lhaipen lung ol heuvin kaum'inahi. Naosen anu noitwi ngaicha talou banginlung ollin kaum in, naosen lungmonga aum bangin keijong kalhagao lungmong in aum'e.
\p 
\v 3 O Israel tule tonsotnin Yahweh Pakaiyah lungmong'in ummin.
\c 132
\s1 Muntheng Phung Phatthei Channa Dia Taona
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai David hi athohgim na jouse pum in hin geldoh'in.
\p 
\v 2 Aman Yahweh Pakai ah kitepna gimneitah in anase in ahi. Aman Israel Pathen Pathen ah kitepna ananeiyin ahi.
\p 
\v 3 “Keima kain ah cheponge, keima kicholdo ponge,
\p 
\v 4 keiman kamit kicholdo sah ponge ahilouleh kamit imutsah ponge,
\p 
\v 5 Keiman ka Yahweh Pakai dinga inkhat sahna ding mun kamu kahsen, Israel Pathen Pathen a dingin muntheng kamu kahsen!”
\p 
\v 6 Vetan hiche thing kong dinghi Ephrathah a aum'e ti kajaovin Jaar loujao dunga hiche mun hi kana mudoh tauve.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai chenna mun a cheu hitin akengphang bul ah chibai boh'u hite.
\p 
\v 8 O Yahweh Pakai thouvin nacholdona mun a chun luttan nathahat melchihna thingkong chutoh lutthatan.
\p 
\v 9 Nathempuhon chonphatna ponsil chu kisil uhen; nalhacha dihtah hon kipa la sauhen.
\p 
\v 10 Nalhacha David khohsahna jal in, nathao nusa lengpa chu paidoh hih'in.
\p 
\v 11 Yahweh Pakai chu David kom'ah akihahsel in, kitepna nunglah doh kit louhel dingin: “Keiman nachilhah khat nalaltouna a katousah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Nachilhah ten nang toh kakitepna leh ka Dan sem ho leh ka thuhil ho hi anit uva ahileh nalal touna hi chejom peh ding ahi,” ati.
\p 
\v 13 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin Jerusalem hi a inn chenna mun dinga adeilhen ahi.
\p 
\v 14 “Hiche hi tonsot a kacholngah na munding ahi” anati. Keima hiche mun a hi kachending ahi, ajeh chu hiche hi kadeilhen inn chu ahi,
\p 
\v 15 Keiman hiche khopi hi phatthei kaboh ding chuleh ijakai ka suhmang pehding ahi, keiman asunga um vaichate an kapehding,
\p 
\v 16 athemputeu chonphatna pon kasilpeh ding, asoh dihtah hon kipa la asahdiu ahi,
\p 
\v 17 Hiche mun a hi David thaneina khantousah ding, hiche kathaonupa hi kamite dinga thaomeivah hi ding,
\p 
\v 18 chuleh agalmite chu jumna le jachatna pon kasilpeh ding amavang leng loupitah kasosah ding ahi.
\c 133
\s1 Sopi Banga Kipum Khat Phattheina
\p 
\v 1 Veuvin, insungkhat hi kilungkhat tah a achenkhom teng iti phat a pha lunglhai um a hitam?
\p 
\v 2 Hiche hi Aaron chunga thao mantam kisungah aluchanga kon a akhamul lah a longlha a avon mong chan a longlha suhpeh tobang ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Kitohdel a Hermon mol chunga kon a longlha daitwi theng tobang a Zion mol a hung longlha chu ahi. Hichea kon a chu Yahweh Pakaiyin malsomna chu ahin phondoh a hichu tonsot hinkhoa ding ahitai.
\c 134
\s1 Jan'a Khongah Ho Tilkhouna
\p 
\v 1 Oh Yahweh Pakai sohte jousen Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah un, nangho Yahweh Pakaiyinn a jankhovah'a asohkin na tongten.
\p 
\v 2 Nakhut theng'u chu taona in domsang uvin lang Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un.
\p 
\v 3 Van le leiset sempa Pathen Pathen chun, Jerusalem a kon'in phatthei naboh tao hen.
\c 135
\s1 Vahchoina La
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah un! Yahweh Pakai min chu thangvah un! Yahweh Pakai lhacha ten Ama chu thang vah un,
\p 
\v 2 Nangho Yahweh Pakai lhacha na tong, Pathen Pathen, Hou-In sung a natong ten.
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakai chu aphatna jeh'in thangvah'un; amin ngaitah chu vahchoilan domsangun.
\p 
\v 4 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin Jacob chu Ama a dingmong monga alhen ahin, Israel chu atumbeh a amagou dinga agon ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Keiman Yahweh Pakai aletna leh aloupina chu kahen, iPakai u Yahweh hi pathen dang sanga lenjo le loupijo ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakaiyin van le leiset chunga hin, twikanglen thuh sunga hin Aman along lhaina a adeidei abol ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Aman meiho jonghi leiset chunga kon a alentousah ahin, Aman gojuh pet in koljong aphetsah'in, huijong hi athil kholna a kon'in ahin lhadohjin ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Aman Egypt te insunga chun ainson in mihemle ganhing jong apeng masa jouse ana sugam in ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Aman Egypt a chun Pharaoh le amipi jouse douna in datmo umtah thil kidang ho ana tongdoh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Aman namlentah tah ho anavolhun leng thupi tahtah ho jong ana satchap e.
\p 
\v 11 Amor lengpa Sihon, Bashan lengpa Og chuleh Caanan lengho jouse anathat gam in ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Aman agam u chu Ama goulo Israel te gamtum dingin anapen ahi.
\p 
\v 13 O Yahweh Pakai namin hi tonsot a um jing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Ajeh chu Yahweh Pakaiyin amite chunga thutah a vaihom ding asohte chunga khotona anei ding ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Chitin namtinte doilim ho hi sana le dangka maimai mihem in asemthubou ahi.
\p 
\v 16 ama hon kam anei un ima aseithei pouvin, mit anei un ima amuthei pouvin,
\p 
\v 17 kol anei un ima ajathei pouvin nahkui anei un ima anahthei pouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Doilimsemthu ho jouse le hiche tahsanho jouse chu hitobang ngen ahiuve.
\p 
\v 19 Vo Israel Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un! O thempu Aaron chilhahho, Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un,
\p 
\v 20 O Levi te Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un! Nangho Yahweh Pakai ginna neijouse Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un!
\p 
\v 21 Zion'a kon'in Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un ajeh chu Ama Jerusalem'a hin achengin ahi. Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un!
\c 136
\s1 Pathen Pathen Lungsetna Longlou Jeh a Vahchoina
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu aphat na ho jouse jeh in thangvah'un! Ajeh chu ami ngailutna dihtah hi tonsot gei a longlou ahi
\p 
\v 2 Semthu pathen ho, Pathen Pathen chu thangvahna peuvin. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot gei a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Pakai ho Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah na peuvin. Ajeh chu Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot geija longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Ama bou hin thil loupi ki dangtah chu abolji ahi. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot gei a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Thepna giltah a vanho hinsemdoh a Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah na peuvin. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot geija longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Twilah a leiset umsah pa chu thangvahna peuvin. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot gei a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Van'a kon a vah semdohpa chu thangvah'un. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsotna longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Nisan sun a vai ahom in ahi, Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Chuleh lha leh ahsi hon jan ah vai ahom un ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Egypt gam a apeng masapen ho anathagam jeh'in Ama chu thangvahna peuvin. Ama mi ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot na longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Aman Egypt ma kon'in Israel ana puidoh'e, Ami ngailutna chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Aman akhut thahatna leh aban thaneina pum in na atongin ahi. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsotna longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Twipi San sukhen a chu Ama ahi, thangvah na peuvin. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsotna longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Aman Israel chu anapui galkai e, Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsotna longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Aman Pharaoh leh asepaite Twipi Sanlah a ana lehlut in ahi. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Gamthip noi a amite apuigalkai jeh'in thangvah na peuvin, Am ingailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Leng thupitah tahho anajeplhuh jeh'in thangvahna peuvin, Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Aman leng thahat tah tah ho anathat gam in ahi. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Sihon Amor lengpa; Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Og Bashaan lengpa, Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Pathen Pathen'in hiche lengho gamchu agoulo din amite anapen ahi. Ami ngailutna chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 22 Asohte Israel ten gam tumbeh a alodiuva anapeh ahi. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Aman ihatmo nauvah eihin geldohjiu vin ahi. Amibngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 24 Aman igalmihou va kon'in eihuhdoh jiuvin ahi. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 25 Aman hinkho neiho jouse dingin aneh achahdiu apejingin ahi. Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\p 
\v 26 Van Pathen Pathen chu thangvahna peuvin, Ami ngailutna dihtah chu tonsot a longlou ahi.
\c 137
\s1 Babylon Gam'a Sohchang Ho Lung Hemna
\p 
\v 1 Jerusalem kageldoh phatnun Babylon vadungpang a chun katou un kakapgam tauve.
\p 
\v 2 Keihon kasemjang houchu mong thingbah chung dunga chun kakhai un ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Hikom'a chun soh a eihente houchun la sah sahding eigouvin, chuleh eisugenthei houchun kipahtah a la sahsahtei ding eigouvin, “Jerusalem la ho chu khatpen beh neisahpeh'un” atiuve.
\p 
\v 4 Ahinlah keihon hetkhahlou mi gamsunga hi Yahweh Pakai la ho chu iti kasahdiuham?
\p 
\v 5 Vo Jerusalem nangma kasuhmil uleh kakhut jetlam hin semjang pehdan sumil jenghen.
\p 
\v 6 Nangma kageldoh louva, Jerusalem chu kakipana sangpen sang a thupi a kagel lou le, ka leihi kadang chungah behden jenghen.
\p 
\v 7 O Yahweh Pakai Babylon sepaiten Jerusalem alonkhum niuva Edom mite thilbol chu geldoh tei in, “Sumang jengin,” “Toltoh sumat jengun” tin asam un ahi.
\p 
\v 8 O Babylon, nangma nakisu mang ding ahi. Nangin neibol nao bang banga na lethuh penpen chu anunnom ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Nachapangteu puimang a songpi chunga sepgoiho chu nunnom hen!
\c 138
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Lunglhai Jeh a David In Avahchoi
\s1 David lasem
\p 
\v 1 Ka Pathen Pathen kalungthim pumpin nangma thangvah ingkate, pathen dang ho masanga nang vahchoinan la sange.
\p 
\v 2 NaHou-Inn theng lang nga'ing ting nami ngailutna tanglou jehleh nakitahna jeh'in namin vahchoi ing kate, ajeh chu nakitepna hi namin loupinan asuhdet ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Kataopet petleh nangin neidonbut in nangin thahatna neipen neitilkhou vin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Leiset chunga leng jousen nangma nathangvah diu ahi, ajeh chu ama hon nathupeh ajauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 ama hon nathilbol ho jehleh naloupi behseh jeh a nangma thangvah la asahdiu ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Vo Yahweh Pakai nangma na let lheh jeng vangin milham jong nakhohsah thouvin, ahinlah mikiletsah hoa kon'in vang nakikhin gamlan ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Keima lungkhamnan eiumkimvel jeng jongleh nangin kagalmite khutna konna neihoidoh ding ahinai. Nangin nakhut hin lhaang doh 'in natin nabanjetlang thahatna a neihuhdoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaiyin keima hinkhoa athilgon achelhahsah ding ahi, ajeh chu O Yahweh Pakai na mi ngailutna dihtah chu atonsotna longlou ahi. Kachunga na natoh nahinpat hi subulhit tan.
\c 139
\s1 Muntin'a Um Le Ima Jouse Musoh Pathen Pathen
\s1 La lamkaipa henga David lasem
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai nangin kalungthim nakholchil in neihechen sohkeitan ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Nangin katouthimpet hihen, kadindoh pet hijongleh nahei. Gamla tah a kaum jeng vangin nangin kalung gel ngaito jouse nahei.
\p 
\v 3 Kakholjinpet hihen, inna katouthimpet hijongleh nangin neimun ahi, chuleh kabol jouse nahesohkei e.
\p 
\v 4 Yahweh Pakai ka thusei got jonghi kasei masangin nahejitai.
\p 
\v 5 Kamasanga nachen, kanunga jong neijuijin ahi, naphatthei bohna khutchu kaluchungah nangam'in ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Hitobang hetna hi keidingin aki dang val in, chuleh hitobang hetchet dinghi keidingin ahahsaval e.
\p 
\v 7 Nalhagaova kon a iti kajam mang thei dingham? Nanga kon a keima iti kajam mang theiding ham?
\p 
\v 8 Keima van a kaltou jonglehng nangma naum in, mithigam ah lutjong leng nangma naum'e.
\p 
\v 9 Keima jingkah lhaving in lengdoh ingting twikhanglen gallang peh a gacheng jong leng,
\p 
\v 10 hichemun jenga jong chun nakhut in neikai hoi in natin, nathahat na in nei vengbit in nate.
\p 
\v 11 Keiman muthim jah a neisel in tijonglehng chuleh kavel a vahjeng jong muthim sosah jonglehng,
\p 
\v 12 muthimlah a kisel jing jonglehng nanga kon a kakisel mangthei louding ahi. Ajeh chu nang dingin ajing jongchu sun banga vah ding ahi. Muthimleh vah jong nangdingin thakhat ahi bouve.
\p 
\v 13 Nangin ka oisung a thil umjuse jong najopmat mat a kanu naobu sunga neigontoh ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Hitobanga thil kidangtah a neina gontoh jeh'in ka thangvah'e! Na natoh nathil bol danhi datmo umtah ahi ti kalungthim apumpin kahe them e.
\p 
\v 15 Keima jatchombeh a kanu naobu muthimlah a eina kigontoh jeng jongchun nangman neinavesui jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Kapen lhah masang a nangman nei namusa ahitai, nitin ka hinkhoa ka ki manchah na ding dan, phatche dungjui a ana kigongtoh chu nikhatcha jeng jong achelhah masanga na lekhabua ana kigoltohsa ahitai.
\p 
\v 17 O Yahweh Pakai kachung changa nalung gel nathilgon tohsaho chu iti mantama hitam simjou jai ahipoi!
\p 
\v 18 Asim jeng jong keijo chi ahipoi, neldi halsiho sang'in jong atamjoi. Kahung khahdoh gei injong nangin neina umpi jing nalai e!
\p 
\v 19 O ka Pathen Pathen miphalouho hi na suhmang hitavele ong! Tolthat ho kahinkhoa kon'in potdoh'un.
\p 
\v 20 Amaho hin na suminseu ve, nagalmi ho hin namin hi asamseu ve.
\p 
\v 21 O Yahweh Pakai nangma nahotbolte ho hi keiman jong kahot louding ham? Nangma nadouho hi kenjong kathet louding ham?
\p 
\v 22 Ahinai, nangman nathetho hi keiman pumthetna kathet ding ahi, ajeh chu nangma galmi ho chu keima galmi ho ahiuve.
\p 
\v 23 O Yahweh Pakai neikhol chil in kalung neihet peh in; neipatep inlang kahina hi kilang doh sah in.
\p 
\v 24 Kasunga hi nangma douva thilse umnalai am nei nodoh peh inlang tonsot lampi a neipui tan.
\c 140
\s1 Mi Gimsah Hoa Kon Kivenbitna Dinga Taona
\s1 La lamkaipa henga: David lasem
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, miphalou hoa kon'in neihuhdoh in, pumhat-a natong hoa kon'in neihoidohsah'in,
\p 
\v 2 ajeh chu alung sung'uva thilse jeng agong un, beitih um louvin gal abol jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Alei gui-u gul in mi achuh banginamang chauvin, athuseidoh jouseu jong gul-gu tobang ahi.
\p 
\v 4 O Yahweh Pakai, miphalou ho khutna kon hin neihoidoh in, pumhatna natong hoa kon'in neihuhdoh in; ajeh chu kakipal lhuhna din thisle jeng agong un ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Mi kiletsah hon kei matna din thang akam un, khao ajan-doh'un lampi dunga thang ei-kampeh'un ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Keiman Yahweh Pakai kom'a, “Nangma hi ka Pathen Pathen nahi!” O Yahweh Pakai, khotona dinga kataona nei sanpeh tan.
\p 
\v 7 O Yahweh Pakai hatchungnung, athahat pan-a eihuhdoh pa; nangman gal kisat nikhoa nei huhdoh ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai, migilouho adei bangin chesah hih'in, athilse gonhou chu lolhin sahhih'in; achuti louva ahileh kiletsahna dim diu ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Kagal miten kachunga thil phalou tohgon anei jal un, manthah nan lhung uhen.
\p 
\v 10 Meiam kong chu alu chunguvah chuhsah'in, meilah a seplut in; ahilouleh ajamdoh louna diu twiveina kotong'ah lhalut jeng uhen.
\p 
\v 11 Ka gamsung uva hin ajou jouva mihehse ho khantousah hihbeh'in, pumhat'a natong ho achung uva thilse chuhsah'in lang sumang in.
\p 
\v 12 Hinlah suhgentheija umte Yahweh Pakaiyin asumil poi, ti kahen; Aman vaichate thu adih a atanpeh ding ahi, ti kahei.
\p 
\v 13 Tahbeh in mi kitah hon namin athangvah diu, chule michonpha ho na kom'a cheng diu ahi.
\c 141
\s1 Aphalou'a Kon Kivenbitna Dinga Taona
\s1 David lasem
\p 
\v 1 O Yahweh Pakai, nangma kakouve, Panpi ngehna katao hi nei ngaipeh loijin!
\p 
\v 2 Kataona hi nahenga gimnamtui kilhut bangin chule kakhut teni kadopsang hi nilhah lang kilhaina gantha bangin neisanpeh tan.
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai, kakam'a hin kamdal neikoipeh'in. Kakam sung nei vetpeh jingin.
\p 
\v 4 Thilse bolna din kalungthim aselam-a kon'in neihoidah sah in, thil dihlou bolna'a neipansah hih'in. Thil dihlou bol hon aphat chompiu thangset umtah thil hoa chan nei neisah hih'in.
\p 
\v 5 Miphan eiphoh hen hichu ngailutna joh ahi! ama hon eisuhdihna chu damna ahipoi, Miphalou hon thilse abol dounan katao jinge.
\p 
\v 6 Alamkaiteu kol'a akisot lhah tengleh, miphalou hon ka thusei angaidiu chuteng dih ahinsah diu ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Songpi akikhet keh teng tol'a akitakeh bangin, miphalou ho gule chang ho jong vui louva kithe jal ding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 O Yahweh Pakai hatchungnung, panpi ngaijin na henga kataove. Nangma kakiselna kulpi nahi; amaho khut-a thina neitosah hih in.
\p 
\v 9 Kei ona dinga thang akam-uva kon'in neihuhdoh in, thilpha lou jenga chon ho thangkol'a nei o-sah hih in.
\p 
\v 10 Miphalou ho chu amaho thang kam-a chun oh uhen, kijam chap tauhen; keivang nei hoidoh sah'in.
\c 142
\s1 Gim Hesoh Pet-A Kithopina Ngaicha Taona
\s1 Songkoa achen laija, David lasem, le Taona
\p 
\v 1 Keima Yahweh Pakai henga kataovin, Yahweh Pakai henga khotona kathum in ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Keima Yahweh Pakai ang-sunga kakiphin in, kahahsatna jouse jong kaphongdoh'in.
\p 
\v 3 Kalhagao alam vai jitan, hinlah Yahweh Pakai nangbou nahi kachena ding lampi ei-hil ji. Kajotna lam'a chun ei-douten thang eikam peh jiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Keiman mikhat tou hunga eipanpi ding kangaichat lai jin, koiman amitsih jenga jong eive poi! Koimacha eikithopi ding aumpoi, kachunga thilsoh koiman imachan eigelpeh poi.
\p 
\v 5 O Yahweh Pakai, keima na henga kataovin, “Nangma hi kakiselna nahi, kahinkhoa kangaichat pen nang bou nahi,” kati.
\p 
\v 6 Kataona hi nei ngaipeh teijin, ei-kisunem behseh jeng tai! Ei-bolgenthei hoa kon'in neihuhdoh tan, ajeh chu amaho keisang'in ahatval jeng tauve.
\p 
\v 7 Songkul'a kon'in neihuhdoh loijin, chutileh nangma ka thangvah thei ding ahi. Lolhing tah a neibol jeh a kajet le kaveija mikitah dim lha diu ahi.
\c 143
\s1 Huhdohna Ding Le Lampi Ki Gottup Na Dia Taona
\s1 David lasem
\p 
\v 1 Vo Yahweh Pakai, kataona ngaijin. Kangeh hi nei ngaipeh teijin! Nangma kitahna le dihna bangin, neidonbut in.
\p 
\v 2 Nalhacha hi nei patep hih in chule kachung thu jong tan hihbeh in, ajeh chu koima na ang-sunga adih aumpoi.
\p 
\v 3 Ajeh chu kagal miten eihin del peh in, kahing chang in tolgoi nan ineijin, lhan khuh-a athisa umho bangin, kada kacham louvin muthim lah a eiumsah tai.
\p 
\v 4 Hijeh chun keiman kinepna ding kanei tapon, ka lungsung kichatnan adim e.
\p 
\v 5 Keiman khanglui nikho chesa ho kageldoh'in, nakhut tenia natohdohsa thil thupi ho kagel jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Kakhut tenin nahenglam kasang'in kataovin, Gamgo-in sadoh leuva twi angaichat bangin; keiman nangma kangaichan ahi.
\p 
\v 7 O Yahweh Pakai, nei donbut loijin, ajeh chu kahin kho bei pai ding ahitai. Keija kon'in kihei mang hih in, ijeh-inem itileh lhan khuh-a lhalut ho kabah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Jingkah sehleh nalungsetna longlou neijahsah in, ajeh chu keima kingaina nangbou nahi. Kalam lhahna jouse neihil them in, kahin kho hi nangma dia kaphal theng ahi.
\p 
\v 9 O Yahweh Pakai, kagal mitea kon'in neihuhdoh in, nahenga kisel dinga hung jamlut kahi bouve.
\p 
\v 10 Ka Pathen Pathen nahi, nadeilam bolje neihil in, name khotona lhagao chun dettah a pan kalah jingna din neipui jingin.
\p 
\v 11 O Yahweh Pakai, namin loupina dingin kahinkho hinghoi teijin. Ajeh chu nakitahna jal'in kahahsatna'a kon'in nei puidoh tan.
\p 
\v 12 Nami ngailutna longlou chun, kagal mite manthahsan in! Chule nalhacha kahi, eidou ho jouse sumang hel in.
\c 144
\s1 Sochatna Le Haona Dinga Taona
\s1 David lasem
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un Ama chu kasongpi ahi. Aman kakhut teni hi galsatje dan eihil in, chule kakhut jung ho hi galsatna'a manchahje dan eihil ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Ama hi eipanpi phapen leh kakulpi ahin, kahoidohna pal leh eihuhdohpa ahi. Chitin namtin anoijah akunsahji ahi.
\p 
\v 3 O Yahweh Pakai, mihem hi ipi hija hibanga nagel-lut a, mihem chapa jeng jong ipi hija hibanga nakhohsah hitam?
\p 
\v 4 Ajeh chu mihem hi hai khat seh a hing ahibouvin, ahin-nikho jong nisa-lep tobanga mangpai thei ahi bouve.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai vanho hinhong in hung kum lhan, molsang ho hi tham'in lang meikhun len mangsah in.
\p 
\v 6 Kehchang len-dohsah inlang galmite thejalsah in! Nathalchang kap inlang jamsah soh hel in.
\p 
\v 7 Van'a kon'in nakhut hin lhang in, twithuh lah a konleh kagalmite thaneina'a kon'in nei huhdoh in.
\p 
\v 8 Akam'un jou jeng aseijun, thudih kaseije atiuvin akihahsel un, hinlah jou jeng aseijun ahi.
\p 
\v 9 O ka Pathen Pathen, na henga lathah khat sange; selangdah jangsom kibut chu mangchan na vahchoila sange.
\p 
\v 10 Ajeh chu nangman lengho galjona napen! Nalhacha David jong athi nading chemjam'a kon'in nahuhdoh jin ahi.
\p 
\v 11 Neihuhdoh'in! Kagalmite thaneina'a kon'in neihuhdoh'in, akam un jou jeng aseijun; thutah kaseiding ahi tin akihahsel-un, hinlah jou jengseh aseijun ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Kachapa teu akhandon laijun thingphung phatah banginkhanlhit sah in, ka chanuteu jong leng inpi jemhoi dinga kisem khompi hoitah ho bang uhen.
\p 
\v 13 Ka changpang jouseu jong lousoh jouse pum'in dimsoh hen, kaloujaova kagan chateu asang sang'in, sangsom som chan geijin pung hen.
\p 
\v 14 Kagancha teu gai pha hen, veiset le apengsol um hih hel hen! Ka khopi sung jeng uva jong lung gim khoisat beihel hen.
\p 
\v 15 Hitobang thilpha achunga lhung ho kipah uhen! chule a Pathen'u Pathen, Yahweh Pakai hikha nam mite chu kipah cheh'u hen!
\c 145
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Phatna Le Thahatna Jal-a Vahchoina
\s1 David in vahchoila asem
\p 
\v 1 Ka Pathen leh kalengpa Pathen nangma choi at inge, chule itih chan hijongleh nangma thangvah jinging kate.
\p 
\v 2 Niseh a nangma ka thangvah jing ding, itihchan hijongleh nangma kavahchoi ding ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Yahweh Pakai hi athupin, Ama bou thangvah dinga lom ahi; koiman athupina tejou ponte.
\p 
\v 4 Akhang khanga mihem ten Yahweh Pakai natoh apachat jing diu, thil kidangtah tah nabol ho aphonjal diu ahi.
\p 
\v 5 Yahweh Pakai nalal loupina kidang leh nathilbol datmo umtah ho giltah a kagel jing ding ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Nathilbol gimnei ho hi mijouse kam'a kijadoh ding, keiman nathupi na ho ka phondoh ding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Kidangtah a naphatna thusim hi mijousen aseiphong diu, keiman jong nadihna thu hi kipahtah a vahchoila kasah ding ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakai hi milungset them leh hepina'a dim, lunghang vahlou; lungsetna long lou ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakai hi mijouse din aphai, Aman athilsem saho jouse chungah khotona lhingset apen ahi.
\p 
\v 10 O Yahweh Pakai, nasemsa jousen na henga kipathu asei diu, chule nanungjui dihtah jousen nathangvah diu ahi.
\p 
\v 11 ama hon na lenggam loupina asap phong diu, nathahatna atah-lang diu ahi.
\p 
\v 12 ama hon natohdoh thil loupi ho mihem chate aseipeh diu, navaihomna lenggam loupi leh anatsat dan aphondoh peh diu ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Ajeh chu na lenggam hi tonsot lenggam ahin, nangin akhang khanga vai nahop ding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Yahweh Pakaiyin alhuho athoudoh'in apohgih'in adelpha ho aphong dingin ahi. Aseidoh chan a kitah Yahweh Pakai ahin, atohna jousea lungset them ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Mit jousen kinem tah in nangma lam ahin ven, nangman amaho ngaichat dungjuijin aneh diu napejin ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Nangman nakhut namang chan, hinkho neijouse hi agilkel adangchah nau nasuh bulhinpeh jin ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Yahweh Pakai hi atohna jousea kitahnan ajuijin, atohna chan'a ngailutna dim ahi.
\p 
\v 18 Yahweh Pakai henga taote Aman anailut jingin, tahbeh a taote aumpi jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 19 Aman gimna le jana neipumma ngaichatna neiho alolhinsah in, panpi ngaicha'a akanao angaipeh'in ahuhdoh jin ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Yahweh Pakaiyin Ama ngailuho ahuhdoh jin, hinlah miphalou ho vang asumang jin ahi.
\p 
\v 21 Keiman Yahweh Pakai chu ka thangvah jing ding, vannoi leisetna cheng jousen tonsot tonsot in Amin thangvah jing tauhen.
\c 146
\s1 Thil Adih Jenga Abol Jeh a Vahchoina
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai vahchoijun! O kalhagao Yahweh Pakai vahchoi jin!
\p 
\v 2 Kahin laisea Yahweh Pakai kavahchoi ding, hinna hu kanei laisen ka Pathen Pathen vahchoi la sange.
\p 
\v 3 Leng chapa te chunga na tahsan koi hih'in, hichu panpi bei ahi bouve.
\p 
\v 4 Mihem chate hu abei tenglehisetna akilekit-un leivui akisoh jin, hiche nikho lechun athilgon chengseu toh thi thading ahi tauve.
\p 
\v 5 Hinlah apanpi dinga Israel Pathen Pathen neiho, chule Yahweh Pakai, Pathen Pathen a kinepna neiho anunnom ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Aman van le leiset twikhanglen leh asunga um jouse anasemin, Aman imatih chan'a akitepna achepi jing ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Aman suhgentheija umho thudih'in achungthu atanpeh in, chule agilkel te an apen ahi. Yahweh Pakaiyin songkul tangho alhadoh'in, achamlhat sah jin ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Yahweh Pakaiyin mitchoho kho amusah'in, alhu ho aphong dingin, michonpha Yahweh Pakaiyin angailun ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Yahweh Pakaiyin gamdang miho ahuhdoh in, Aman meithaiho leh chaga ho akhoton, amavang miphalou ho thilgon asuhbei peh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Yahweh Pakaiyin tonsotna vai ahomding ahi. O Jerusalem, Ama hi akhang akhanga na Pathen hi ding ahi. Yahweh Pakai vahchoijun!
\c 147
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Tahsan In Chule Ama Jeng Hou-In
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai vahchoijin umhen! I-Pathen'u Pathen vahchoi lasah ding hi iti phat-a pha hitam! Ijeh-inem itileh Ama lungset nan adimn in, vahchoi dia lomtah ahi.
\p 
\v 2 Yahweh Pakaiyin Jerusalem aki ledohsah in, amangtasa Israel te ahin lepui kit in ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Aman lungthimna jong aboldam in, amaha jeng-u jong adamsah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 4 Aman ahsi ho asim toh in, amin cheh in akouvin ahi.
\p 
\v 5 I-Yahweh Pakaiyu hi iti loupi hitam! Athaneina hi akhkonna gei ahi! Athil hetthem theina jong mihem hetphah hoi ahipoi.
\p 
\v 6 Yahweh Pakaiyin mikineosah ho adomsang'in, ahin miphalouho vang toltoh alhobeh'in ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Yahweh Pakai thangvahna la sauvin, semjangto thon Pathen Pathen vahchoila sauvin.
\p 
\v 8 Aman vanho meilom'in akhun, leiset a go ajuh lhahsah in, chule molchunga hampa louhing akedohsah'in ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Aman gamsa ho neh ding apen chule va-ah nou ho apenteng aneh diu apejin ahi.
\p 
\v 10 Aman sakol thahatna leh mihem thahatna'a akison-jiu akipapi poi.
\p 
\v 11 Yahweh Pakai chu Ama ging jing ho leh ami ngailutna longlou chunga kinepna neiho akipa pin ahi.
\p 
\v 12 Vo Jerusalem, Yahweh Pakai loupina vahchoijun! O Zion, na Pathen Pathen vahchoijun.
\p 
\v 13 Ajeh chu Aman nakelkot jol ho alhousah in, chule nakul sunga nachate phatthei aboh in ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Aman nagamgi tin-uva chamna alensah in, chule nagilkel nauvah an twitah in navah uvin ahi.
\p 
\v 15 Vannoi leiset chunga thu-apeh teng jongleh aman gang in ahi.
\p 
\v 16 Aman buhbang jeng jong samul abahsah jin, chule dai-kai jong vutvam kithejal abahsah jin ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Gel-chang jong song kisunglha abahsah jin, adapsah teng jong ama-anga ding jou ding koiham?
\p 
\v 18 Chujou teng Aman thu apen ahileh ajunlha gamji tan, Aman hui chu asol'in ahileh buhbangho chu twijin alongji tai.
\p 
\v 19 Aman Jacob henga thu aseipeh in, Israel kom'a a Dan thupeh ho leh athuhil ho chu ahilchen in ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Hitobang hi namdang ho jah a aseipeh pon, ama hon athuhil jong ahepouvin ahi. Yahweh Pakai vahchoijin umhen!
\c 148
\s1 Thilsem Jousen Yahweh Pakai Vahchoi Hen
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un! Vanhoa kon'in Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un! Vanthamjol-a kon'in Ama chu thangvah'un!
\p 
\v 2 Avantil te jousen thangvah'un! Van sepaite jousen thangvah'un!
\p 
\v 3 Nisa le lha-in ama chu thangvah'un! Aphelhet lhet ahsi hon Ama chu thangvah'un!
\p 
\v 4 Achungsang lam'a um vantham jol'in thangvah'un! Meilom chung sangpeh a um meitwi hon Ama chu thangvah'un!
\p 
\v 5 Thilsemho jousen Yahweh Pakai chu thangvahna peuvin, ajeh chu Aman thu apen ahileh amaho chu ahung kisemdoh jengun ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Aman tonsot geija dinga anagontohsoh ahitai. Ama Dan semchu itih hijongleh ki khokhel louding ahi.
\p 
\v 7 Leisetna kon'in thangvah'un, twikhanglen lailunga thilsemhon thangvah'un,
\p 
\v 8 meileh gel hon, buhbang leh meilom hon thangvah'un, huileh adap asatnin Ama thu chu ngaijun.
\p 
\v 9 Mol leh lhangho, aga nei thingphung ho le Cedar thinghon,
\p 
\v 10 gamsa ho le ganhingho jousen, ganhing neochacha ho le vachahon,
\p 
\v 11 leiset chunga lengho le mipite jousen, leiset chunga vaihom ho leh thutanho jousen,
\p 
\v 12 pasal khangthah ho le numei khangthah hon, tehse ho leh chapanghon,
\p 
\v 13 abonchauvin Yahweh Pakai min thangvah'u hen! Ajeh chu Aminhi aloupi lheh jenge, hiche Amin loupina hi leiset le vanho jouse sanga sangjo ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Aman amite chu ki khat atundohpeh tan ahi, ama dinga kitahna neijouse Aman angailut Israel mipite chu jana apetan ahi. Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen!
\c 149
\s1 Tahsan Chate Jousen Yahweh Pakai Vahchoijun
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'un! Yahweh Pakai vahchoina lathah sauvin. Tahsan chate kikhopna ah avahchoila sauvin.
\p 
\v 2 O Israel nasempa chunga kipah'in, O Jerusalem mipite, na lengpau chungah kipah'un.
\p 
\v 3 Khongpi gintoh semjang saito thon lampum pum'in Aminchu vahchoijun,
\p 
\v 4 Ajeh chu amite chungah akipah'in, mi nun nem te chu jana lallukhuh akhupeh tai.
\p 
\v 5 Pathen Pathen chate chu hitobang jana achanjeh un, jankhovah'in avahchoila sauhen,
\p 
\v 6 Akhut'in chemjam hemtah kichoiyu henlang, akamsunguuvah kipah tah in Pathen Pathen thangvah la sauhen.
\p 
\v 7 Chitin namtin ho chunga aphulah theina diuleh, namtin chunga engbolna apeh theina diuvin,
\p 
\v 8 alengteu thihkhao kola akihen'uva, chuleh alamkaiteu thihkhaova akikan theina diuvin,
\p 
\v 9 achung uva thu kitanna dungjuiya akitohdohna dingin. Hiche hi Pathen Pathen chate chan loupitah achannao chu ahi. Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen!
\c 150
\s1 Yahweh Pakai Vahchoijun
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah na peuvin! Pathen Pathen chu Hou-In'ah thangvah'un, Avan chung thahatna mun nah thangvah'un!
\p 
\v 2 Athilbol thahatna kidangtah jeh'in ama chu thangvah'un, aletna seijoulou jeh'in thangvah'un!
\p 
\v 3 Sumkon gin kithong pum'in vahchoijun, theile mut selangdah saito thon thangvah'un!
\p 
\v 4 Khopi ginleh lam pummin vahchoijun, kuli leh tumging theito thon thangvah'un!
\p 
\v 5 Khong gintoh thon thangvah'un, Khong gin kithong gimneitah chuto thon vahchoi jun,
\p 
\v 6 Haina hu neijousen Yahweh Pakai thangvah na la sauvin! Yahweh Pakai chu thangvah'in umhen! 
